Śivadharmottara
Based on: paśupatimatam śivadharmamahāśāstram paśupatināthadarśanam
bṛhadādhyātmikapariṣada, kāṣṭhamaṇḍapa, Nepal, saṃvat 2055(1998)and
compared with transcript T0075 (T75 ) of IFP, Pondicherry.


 Chapter 1

namo'stu tasmai śakalendudhāriṇe phaṇīndraratnadyutikaṇṭharāgiṇe |
śivamastu sarvajagatāṃ parahitaniratābhavantu bhūtaguṇāḥ |
harāya śubhrābhrakapālamāline vibhinnadaityasphuritaikaśūline || 1.1 |
doṣāḥ prayāntu śāntiṃ sarvatra sukhī bhavantu sakalalokā || \ T75
