te ca śrutāstvayā sarve pṛcchāmi tvāmahantataḥ || 1.5 ||
kiṃ pradhānāḥ śivadharmāḥ śivavākyaṃ ca kīdṛśam |
kiṃ pradhānāśśive dharmāśśivavākyaṃ ca kīdṛśam| \ T75
liṅge'rcitaḥ śivaḥ kena vidhinā samprasīdati || 1.6 ||
vidyādānañca dānānāṃ sarveṣām uttamaṃ kila|
vidyādānaṃ ca sarveṣāṃ dānānām uttamaṃ kila| \ T75
tacca śrutau dvijendrāṇāṃ nānyeṣāṃ samudāhṛtam || 1.7 ||
