tatpuṇyaṃ sarvavarṇānāṃ jāyate kena karmaṇā |
jñeyaṃ katividhaṃ tacca vidyādānam anuttamam || 1.8 ||
kāni puṇyāni kṛtveha gṛhiṇaḥ svargiṇaḥ punaḥ |
