tau gacchataḥ śivasthānaṃ narakan tadviparyayāt || 1.75 ||
% tau gacchataśśivajñānaṃ narakaṃ tadviparyate| \ T75
atha godehasambhūtaṣaḍaṅgavidhinā śivaḥ |
% athavā dehasambhūtaṣṣaḍaṅgavidhinā śivaḥ| \ T75
liṅge sampūjitaḥ śīghraṃ narāṇāṃ samprasīdati || 1.76||
surāsurair mathyamānāt kṣīrodāt sāgarottamāt |
pañcagāvaḥ samutpannāḥ sarvalokasya mātaraḥ || 1.77||
%% p.191
nandā subhadrā surabhiḥ suśīlā sumanāś ca nā |
% nandā bhadrā ca surabhissuśīlā suma . . yā| \ T75
gāvaḥ śivapurāt pañca kṣitiṃ prāptāḥ śivecchayā || 1.78||
% pañcagāvaśśivapurātkṣitiṃ \ T75
sarvalokopakārārthaṃ devānāṃ tarpaṇāya ca |
%% Tp.9
gomātaraḥ sthitā bhūmau snānārcārthaṃ śivasya ca || 1.79||
% snānārthaṃ ca śiva(ra)sya . | \ T75
gomayaṃ rocanā mūtraṃ kṣīraṃ dadhi ghṛtaṃ gavām|
% gomayaṃ recanā mūtraṃ \ T75
ṣaḍaṅgāni pavitrāṇi sarvasiddhikarāṇi ca || 1.80 ||
gomayād utthitaḥ śrīmān bilvavṛkṣaḥ śivapriyaḥ |
% gomayādutthitaṃ śrīmān \ T75
tatrāste padmahastā śrīḥ śrīvṛkṣas tena sa smṛtaḥ || 1.81||
bījāny utpalapadmānāṃ punarjātāni gomayāt |
gorocanā ca māṅgalyā pavitrā sarvasādhikā || 1.82 ||
% gorocanā ca māgalyā pavitrā sarvasiddhidā| \ T75
gor mūtrād guggulur jātaḥ sugandhiḥ priyadarśanaḥ |
% gomūtrādguggulurjātassugandhaḥ priyadarśanaḥ| \ T75
āhāraḥ sarvadevānāṃ śivasya ca viśeṣataḥ || 1.83 ||
yad bījaṃ jagataḥ kiñcit taj jñeyaṃ kṣīrasambhavam |
dadhnaḥ sarvāṇi jātāni māṅgalyāny arthasiddhaye || 1.84||
% māggalyānyarthasiddhaye| \ T75
ghṛtād amṛtam utpannam amarāṇām atipriyam |
% ghṛtādamṛtamṛ(mu)dbhūtam \ T75
tasmād ghṛtena payasā dadhnā ca snāpayec chivam || 1.85||
tadante coṣṇatoyena kaṣāyaiś ca virūkṣayet |
snāpya śītāmbunā paścāl liṅgaṃ rocanam ālabhet || 1.86||
% liṅgaṃ rocanayā lipet| \ T75
pūjayed bilvapatraiś ca padmair nīlotpalair api |
arcayitvā dahed bhaktyā ghṛtayuktaṃ tu guggulum || 1.87||
% arcayitvā va(da)hetpaścādghṛtayuktaṃ ca guggulam| \ T75
pāyasaṃ dadhibhaktaṃ ca ghṛtam adhvā pariplutam |
% ghṛtaṃ dadhnā pariplutam| \ T75
nivedayīta śarvāya bhaktāṃś ca ghṛtapācitān || 1.88 ||
% nivedayecchivāyai tat bhakṣyaṃ ca ghṛtapācitam| \ T75
kṛtvā pradakṣiṇāṃ cānte praṇipatya kṣamāpayet |
% kṛtvā pradakṣiṇaṃ cānte \ T75
%% Tp.10
anena vidhinā devaḥ ṣaḍaṅgena prasīdati || 1.89 ||
ihaloke pare caiva sarvān kāmān prayacchati |
% sarvakāmān prayacchati| \ T75
ṣaḍaṅgavidhinā tasmān nṛpatiḥ pūjayec chivam || 1.90||
śivabhaktaḥ samuttārya kulānām ekaviṃśatim |
svarge sthāpya svayaṃ gacched aiśvaryaṃ padam avyayam || 1.91||
% gacchedaiśvaraṃ paramaṃ padam| \ T75
aśaṭhāḥ sarvabhṛtyāś ca devakārye niyojitāḥ |
% āśritāḥ sarvabhṛtyāśca \ T75
prayānti svāminā sārdhaṃ śrīmacchivapuraṃ mahat || 1.92||
bhuktvā bhogān suvipulān bhṛtyavargasamanvitaḥ|
% buktvā tatrātulān bhogān \ T75
kālāt punarihāyātaḥ pṛthivyām ekarāḍ bhavet|| 1.93||
%% p.192
vṛkṣāḥ puṣpāṅgapatrādair upayuktāḥ śivārcane |
% vṛkṣaḥ puṣpāṅgapatrādaiḥ upayuktāśśivārcane| \ T75
śivagāvaś ca gacchanti rudralokaṃ na saṃśayaḥ|| 1.94||
% śivabhāvācca gacchanti \ T75
pūjitaṃ pūjyamānaṃ vā yaḥ paśyed bhaktitaḥ śivam |
% pūjyataṃ pūjyamānaṃ vā yaḥ paśyecchraddhayā śivam| \ T75
% sopi yāgaphalaṃ kṛtsnaṃ prāpnuyānnātra saṃśayaḥ| \ T75
%% Above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.

śrutvānumodayed yaś ca sarvayāgaphalaṃ labhet|| 1.95||
% śrutvā tu modate puṇyamaiśvaraṃ yassamādhinā| \ T75
% phalaṃ tatsamāpnoti pūjayecchaktitaśśivam| \ T75
% śrutvā tu mumude yastu sa ca yogaphalaṃ labhet| \ T75
%% Above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
arcitaṃ śaṅkaraṃ dṛṣṭvā sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate |
harṣāt praṇamya taṃ bhūmau śivaloke mahīyate|| 1.96||
sampūjyamānaṃ vidhinā yaḥ paśyec chraddhayā śivam |
so'pi yāgaphalaṃ kṛtsnaṃ prāpnuyān nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 1.97||
%% Line 97cd occurs after 95ab of this edition (see above).
śrutvānumodayet puṇyam aiśvaraṃ yaḥ samādhinā |
tatsamaṃ phalam āpnoti śivasya vacanaṃ yathā || 1.98||
% śivasya vacanaṃ tathā| \ T75
%% Tp.11
Yad aśeṣaiḥ śivabhaktair dhyānārcanakṛtan tapaḥ|
% yad aśeṣaiśśive bhaktaiḥ \ T75
Bhaktyānumodayed īśaṃ tat sarvaṃ tvatprasādataḥ|| 1.99||
% bhaktyānumodaneneśaḥ tatsarvaṃ prasīdati| \ T75
śivapuṇyam ahiṃsādyam aśeṣajanasambhavam|
% śivapuṇyamahīṃnādyam \ T75
kālatraye'pi nikhilaṃ yaḥ puṇyam anumodayet || 1.100||
% tacca syādanumodate| \ T75
iti trisandhyamakhilaṃ taṇyāham anumodayet|
% yaḥ puṇyamanumodate| \ T75
asaṃśayamatiḥ śrāddhas tatsamaṃ yaḥ puṇyam āpnuyāt|| 1.101||
% asaṃśayamatiśraddhaṃ \ T75
śivadharmāḥ śivaproktāḥ susūkṣmāḥ sumahāphalāḥ |
% iti dharmāśśivenoktāḥ susūkṣmāssumahatphalāḥ| \ T75
Kīrtitās te samāsena śivārcanavidhiṃ prati || 1.102||
% kīrtitāntena mānena śivārcanavidhiṃ prati| \ T75

\Colo
iti śivadharmottare ṣaḍaṅgavidhirnāma prathamo'dhyāyaḥ|
% iti śrī śivadharmottaraśāstre goṣaḍaṅgavidhirnāma prathamo'dhyāyaḥ| \ T75

%% Chapter 2

%% p.193
%% Tp.12

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivadharmottare
vidyādāno nāma dvitīyo'dhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
% śrīḥ| \ T75
% atha dvitīyodhyāyaḥ| \ T75
atha vidyāvidā deyaṃ vidyādānaṃ śivātmakam|
% atha vidyāvide dātā vidyātmānaṃ śivātmakam| \ T75
tasya dānaṃ mahādānaṃ sarvadānottamottamam|| 2.1||
% tasyādānaṃ mahādānaṃ \ T75
adhyāpayan śanaiḥ śiṣyān śivabhaktān prabodhayet|
% adhyāpya yajanaiḥśśiṣyān \ T75
śivavidyānusāreṇa vidyādānaṃ taducyate|| 2.2||
saṃskṛtaiḥ prākṛtairvākyaiḥ yaḥ śiṣyān anurūpataḥ|
deśabhāṣādyupāyaiśca bodhayet sa guruḥ smṛtaḥ|| 2.3||
yathā śivasya naivāntaḥ sampūrṇasya mahātmanaḥ|
tathā vidyāpradānasya nāntaḥ sarvaguṇātmakaḥ|| 2.4||
% nāntassarvaguṇātmanaḥ| \ T75
śivāṣṭaguṇamaiśvaryavidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|
% śivāṣṭaguṇamaiśvaryaṃ vidyādānādapāpnuyāt| \ T75
iha kīrtiṃ śivāṃ brāhmīṃ prajñāṃ vṛddhiṃ dhanaṃ sukham|| 2.5||
% ihakīrtiṃ śriyaṃ brāhmīṃ prajñāvṛddhiṃ dhanaṃ sukham| \ T75
yo'śuddhamātmanādhītya jñānamadhyāpayecchivam|
% yo śraddhadhānamātmānaṃ jñānamadhyāpayetparam| \ T75
sa yāti narakaṃ ghoraṃ pāpīyān jñānanāśakaḥ|| 2.6||
% pāpīyān jñānaghātakaḥ| \ T75
śivajñānasya kālena vinaṣṭasya pramādataḥ|
ūnātiriktavarṇasya mūḍhairdurlikhitasya ca|| 2.7||
% punāti riktavarṇasya \ T75
pramādādhītapāṭhasya nāśitasyālpabuddhibhiḥ|
% pramādādhītapāṭhasya (sva)siddhāntavirodhi(na) sādhitasyālpabuddhibhiḥ| \ T75
jñānāvalepamānāndhairācāryaiḥ śodhitasya ca|| 2.8||
% jñānāvalepamāpannairācāryairbodhitasya ca| \ T75
vyastaiḥ padair upetasya punaruktasya cārthataḥ|
% vyarthaiḥ padairupetasya \ T75
pūrvottaraviruddhasya svasiddhāntavirodhinaḥ|| 2.9||
%% Tp.13
chandasātīva naṣṭasya śabdārtharahitasya ca|
% chandasātīvahīnasya \ T75
ityevamādibhirdoṣairupetasya kvacit kvacit|| 2.10||
% ityevamādidoṣairupetasya \ T75
yaḥ karoti punaḥ samyak saṃskāraṃ pūrvavadguruḥ|
% yaḥ karoti punastasya \ T75
śivatantrārthaviddhīmān sa vidyāparameśvaraḥ|| 2.11||
% śiva tatrātmaviddhīmān sa vidvān parameśvaraḥ| \ T75
na cāsya puṇyamāhātmyaṃ śakyaṃ vaktuṃ hi kena cit|
% vaktuṃ śakyaṃ hi kena cit| \ T75
yathā śivastathaivāyam asminnityaṃ śivaḥ sthitaḥ|| 2.12||
vidyādānaṃ pravakṣyāmi vratināṃ pustakāśritam|
% dhanināṃ pustakāśritam| \ T75
nīyate dīyate yena vidhinā tatphalaṃ ca yat|| 2.13||
% likhyate dīyate yena vidhinā tatphalaṃ ca yat| \ T75
%% p.194
śivaṃ sampūjya vidhivat tadvidyāṃ pūjayettataḥ|
guruñca pūjayed bhaktyā tulyametat trayaṃ yataḥ|| 2.14||
% guruṃ ca śivavadbhaktyā \ T75
yathā śivastathā vidyā yathā vidyā tathā guruḥ|
śivavidyāgurūṇāñca pūjāyāḥ sadṛśaṃ phalam|| 2.15||
% pūjayāsadṛśaṃ phalam| \ T75
bhūmi(bhā)ge same ramye sarvabādhāvivarjite|
% sarvadoṣavivarjite| \ T75
vidyāmaṇḍalakaṃ kṛtvā gandhagomayavāriṇā|| 2.16||
% vidyāmaṇḍalakaṃ kuryāt \ T75
aṣṭahastaṃ tadardhaṃ vā vṛttaṃ vā caturasrakam|
% caturaśrakam| \ T75
tanmadhye sitacūrṇena likhet padyaṃ suśobhanam|| 2.17||
tadbahirvarṇakaiścitrairnānā śobhāḥ prakalpayet|
% nānā śobhāṃ prakalpayet| \ T75
% pañcavarṇaiśca kusumaiḥ yathāśobhamalaṃkṛtam| \ T75
% sitaṃ vitānachatraṃ vā tadūrdhvamupakalpayet| \ T75
% muktādāmaparikṣiptaṃ kiṃkiṇiravakānvitam| \ T75
%% Above three lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
%% Tp.14
lambanaiḥ sūtradāmaiśca muktāhāraiśca kandukaiḥ|| 2.18||
% lambakairdhvajadāmaiśca muktādāmaissakandukaiḥ| \ T75
vicitrapuṣpasragdāmairghaṇṭācāmarabhūṣitam|
% pavitrapuṣpasrakdāmaiḥ ghaṇṭācāmarabhūṣitaiḥ| \ T75
citravastraparicchannaiścaturbhirdaṇḍakairvṛtam (ghṛtaṃ)|| 2.19||
% vicitravastrasaṃchannaiḥ caturbhiḥ daṇḍakairyutam| \ T75
budbudairardhacandaiśca darpaṇādyupaśobhitam|
% budbudairardhacandraiśca parvaṇānyupaśobhitaiḥ| \ T75
sitapadmasamākīrṇaiścaturbhiḥ kalaśaiḥ śubhaiḥ|| 2.20||
% sitapadmamukhodgāraiḥ caturbhiḥ kalaśaiśśubhaiḥ| \ T75
śobhitaṃ sitamṛtpātrair yavaśālyaṅkurodbhavaiḥ|
% yavaśālyaṃkurodbhalaiḥ| \ T75
vidyāsiṃhāsanaṃ śrīman nāgadantādinirmitam|| 2.21||
suvarṇaratnakhacitaṃ dukūlāstaraṇānvitam|
% suvarṇaratnasicitaṃ(nicitaṃ) \ T75
dattāsanaṃ vā śrīmattaddhemaratnopaśobhitam|| 2.22||
% daṇḍānanaṃ vā śrīmantaṃ \ T75
nāgendradantanicitaṃ raktamandanadārujam|
% nāgendradantasicitaṃ raktacandanadārujam| \ T75
sthāpya puṣpaṃ gṛhasyānte gandhapuṣpaiḥ prapūjya ca|| 2.23||
% srāvyapuṣpagṛhasyāntaṃ gandhapuṣpaissamarcayet| \ T75
lekhyañca likhitañcaiva vinyaset pustakadvayam|
% lekhyaṃ ca likhitaṃ cātra \ T75
rocanācandanādyaiśca puṣpairbhūpaiśca pūjayet|| 2.24||
ghṛtapradīpamālyādyairbhakṣyairvastraiśca śobhanaiḥ|
% dhvajapradīpamālābhiḥ kṣaumavastraiśca pūjitaiḥ| \ T75
% śivavatpūjayedbhaktyā yathāvibhavavistaram| \ T75
%% Above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
kastūryagurukarpūra sicacandana kauśikaiḥ|| 2.25||
% turuṣkagarukarpūraiḥ sitacandanaguggulaiḥ| \ T75
dadyāt pañcavidhaṃ dhūpaṃ samutthāpya punaḥ punaḥ|
% samutkṣipya punaḥ punaḥ| \ T75
tataḥ pradakṣiṇaṃ kṛtvā namet sarvāṅgakairbudhaḥ|| 2.26||
% namet sarvāṅgakaṃ budhaḥ| \ T75
sampūjyaivaṃ śivajñānaṃ guruṃ sampūjayettataḥ|
% sampūjyaiva \ T75
dvitīye tu puṣpagṛhe śrīmadāsanasaṃsthitam|| 2.27||
% divtīye puṣpagrahake śrīmadānanasaṃmitam| \ T75
%% Tp.15
śivavat pūjayed bhaktyā śivajñānaprakāśakam|
tridhā pradakṣiṇīkṛtya daṇḍavat praṇamet kṣitau|| 2.28||
% tridhā pradakṣiṇaṃ kṛtvā \ T75
vijñāpayet samutthāya jānubhyāṃ dharaṇīṅgataḥ|
% jānubhyāṃ dharaṇīṃ tataḥ| \ T75
kṛtāñjalipuṭo bhūtvā praṇipatya punargurum|| 2.29||
%% p.195
bhagavaṃstvatprasādena śāstraṃ sañcārayāmyaham|
% bhagavan tvatprasādena śāstre saṃcarayāmyaham| \ T75
tatheti samanujñātaḥ śāstraṃ puṇyāhamācaret|| 2.30||
% tathaivāstvityanujñātaśśāstrapuṇyamathācaret| \ T75
maṅgalaistūryaghoṣaśca kṛtasvastyayanaḥ śuciḥ|
snātaḥ śuklāmbaradharaḥ stragvī gandhādyalaṅkṛtaḥ|| 2.31||
% snātaśśuklāṃbaradharo gandhamālyaiśca bhūṣitaḥ| \ T75
hemāṅgulīyapāṇiśca kaṭakādyairalaṅkṛtaḥ|
% hemāṅgulīyapāṇistu \ T75
likhet praṇamya deveśaṃ lekhakaḥ ślokapañcakam|| 2.32||
tato vividhabhaktānnapānavyañjanādibhiḥ|
% tato vividhabhakṣyānnapānakavyañjanādibhiḥ| \ T75
bhojayeta guruṃ pūrvaṃ vratinaḥ sadvijānapi|| 2.33||
% bhojayecca guruṃ pūrvaṃ vratinassadvijānapi| \ T75
dīnāndhakṛpaṇānāthabālavṛddhakṛśāturān|
% dīnāndhakṛpaṇānāthān bālavṛddhakṛśāturān| \ T75
mātā pitṛsuhṛdbandhūn naktaṃ sarvaśca dakṣayet|| 2.34||
% mātāpitṛsuhṛdbandhūnetān sarvāṃśca bhojayet| \ T75
kṣamāpya ca guruṃ paścād bhuñjīyād bhṛtyasaṃyutaḥ|
% samāpyaivaṃ guruṃ paścāt \ T75
datvā gaṇabaliṃ rātrau brahmacārī niśi svapet|| 2.35||
apare'hani pūrvāhṇe vidyāmaṇḍalakaṃ budhaḥ|
kṛtvā dvihastamātrantu nānāvarṇakaśobhitam|| 2.36||
% kṛtvā dvihastamātraṃ tu nānāvarṇopaśobhitam| \ T75
yavāṅkuraśarāvādyaiścitrapuṣpairalaṅkṛtam|
% citrakalpairalaṃkṛtam| \ T75
sa dhūpadīpasaṃyuktaṃ vitānaṃ vitatāmbaram|| 2.37||
% svaṃ dhūpādisamāyuktaṃ \ T75
%% Tp.16
śarayantrāsanāsīnaṃ tanmadhye pūjya pustakam|
% śivayantrāsanāsīnaṃ \ T75
evaṃ likhed vācayedvā kṛtvā pūjāṃ dine dine|| 2.38||
caturasraiḥ saumyaśīrṣairnātisthūlainna vā kṛśaiḥ|
% caturaśraissamai śṛṅgaiḥ nātisthūlairna vāṅkuraiḥ| \ T75
sampūrṇāvayavaiḥ snigdhair nātivicchinnasaṃhataiḥ|| 2.39||
mātrānusvārasaṃyogahrasvadīrghādilakṣitaiḥ|
% @hrasvadīrghādilakṣaṇaiḥ| \T75
nandināgarakairvarṇairlekhayecchivapustakam|| 2.40||
%% 40b: last line
sampūrṇaṃ pūrvavidhinā punaḥ pūjāṃ prakalpayet|
% sampūjyet pūrvavidhinā \ T75
śivāgniguruvidyānāṃ sopacārāṃ prayatnavān|| 2.41||
% nopavāsaḥ prayatnataḥ| \ T75
kalpayejjāgaraṃ cātra vāditrairmadhurasvanaiḥ|
% @jāgaraṃ tatra \ T75
gītanṛtyairbahuvidhairākhyātaiśca śivātmakaiḥ|| 2.42||
% @rākhyānaiśca śivātmakaiḥ| \ T75
vedaghoṣaiśca vividhaiḥ prekṣaṇakaiśca śobhanaiḥ|
% prekṣaṇīyaissuśobhanaiḥ| \ T75
kriḍāyantraprayogādyairityevaṃ kṣapayenniśām|| 2.43||
śivavidyāvimānañca kuryāt prātaḥ suśobhanam|
pañcāṇḍakaṃ tribhūmañca dāruvaṃśādinirmitam|| 2.44||
% pañcaṣaṭktṛbhaumaṃ vā guruvaṃśādikaṃ dṛḍham| \ T75
vicitravastrasañchannaṃ sarvaśobhāsamanvitam|
vidyāsanasthaṃ tanmadhye śivajñānasya pustakam|| 2.45||
% vidyāsa(na)naṃ tu tanmadhye . . jñānasya pustakam| \T75
%% p.196
hemaratnacitaṃ divyam athavā dantaśobhitam|
% hemaratnācitaṃ divyam adhivā(pā)daṃtaśobhitam| \ T75
vicitracitrayuktaṃ vā bahirutkīrṇakambike|| 2.46||
% bahirutkīrṇakamlam| \ T75
pārśve carmasamāyuktaṃ dṛḍhasūtranibandhanam|
% pārśvataścatrasaṃyuktaṃ sudṛḍhaṃ sūtrabandhanam| \ T75
sampūjya gandhapuṣpādyaiḥ pūrvoktavidhinā budhaḥ|| 2.47||
%% Tp.17
samutkṣipyānayed bhaktyā tadvimānaṃ śivāśramam|
% samutthāpayedbhaktyā tadvimānaṃ śivāśrame| \ T75
susthitaṃ rathyamukhyena puruṣairvāvalambitam|| 2.48||
% susthiraṃ rathamukhyena puruṣairvāpi balānvitaiḥ| \T75
chatradhvajapatākādayir vimānaisturyanisvanaiḥ|
% vitānaistutya nisvanaiḥ| \ T75
maṅgalairvedaghoṣādyaiḥ sudhūpaiḥ kalaśaiḥ sitaiḥ|| 2.49||
% maṅgalairvedaghoṣairvā na dhūpaiḥ kalaśaiśśubhaiḥ| \ T75
cāraṇairvandibhirvādyaiḥ strīsaṅgītairvibhūṣitam|
% strīsaṃgītairvibhūṣitaiḥ| \ T75
cārucāmarahastābhiścitradaṇḍaiśca darpaṇaiḥ|| 2.50||
% chatradaṇḍaissadarpaṇaiḥ| \ T75
mahatā janasaṃghena purataśca mahīyate|
% purataśca mahīpatiḥ| \ T75
dharmavṛddhai svayaṃ gacchet sarvaśobhāsamanvitaḥ|| 2.51||
athavā hastiyānasthaṃ kṛtvā pustakam ānayet|
rājamārgeṇa mahatā nagarāntaṃ pradakṣiṇam|| 2.52||
% nagarāntaḥ pradakṣiṇam| \ T75
sarvāyatanapūjāñca svadhanaiḥ kārayennṛpaḥ|
daśadikṣu balindatvā nagarasya samantataḥ|| 2.53||
% daśadikṣu baliṃ dadyānnagarasya \ T75
mārge'pi purato gacched balindadyānnirantaram|
% puṣpaṃ datvā nirantaram| \ T75
gandhapuṣpākṣatonmiśramudakañca tadānugam|| 2.54||
% gandhapuṣpākṣatairyuktamudakaṃ candanānugam| \ T75
agrepaścācca gaccheyuḥ sarvāyatanavāsinaḥ|
% gaccheyuryatra taccātra sarvāyatanavāsinaḥ| \ T75
purataḥ śivavidyāyāḥ śivamantrasmarāḥ śubhāḥ|| 2.55||
% purataśśivavidyāyāssmaranto mantramaiśvaram| \ T75
śuklāmbaradharāḥ sarve bhaveyuḥ puravāsinaḥ|
ucchreyeyuḥ patākāśca janāste deśavāsinaḥ|| 2.56||
% vucchrayeyuḥ patākāṃśca janāstaddeśavāsinaḥ| \ T75
gṛhadevāśca sampūjyā kāryaścāpyutsavo gṛhe|
% gṛhadevāṃśca saṃpūjya  \ T75
brāhmaṇān bhojayeyuśca gṛheṣu gṛhamedhinaḥ|| 2.57||
%% Tp.18
annapānairjānapadāyātrāṃ kuryuḥ śivāśrame|
% annapānairjanapadādyātrāṃ kuryācchivāśrame| \ T75
acchedyāstaravaḥ kāryāḥ sarvāṃ hiṃsānnivārayet|| 2.58||
% sarvahiṃsāṃ nivārayet| \ T75
bandhanasthāśca bhoktavyā baddhāḥ krośena śatravaḥ|
% bandhanasthāḥ pramoktavyāḥ vadhyāḥ krodhānnasaṃśayaḥ| \ T75
akālakaumudīṃ kuryād divasadvayamīśvare|| 2.59||
% akālakaumudīṃ kuryāddevasatratamīśvare| \ T75
śivāyatanam āsādya vimānasthantamarghayet|
% vimānasthitamarcayet| \ T75
puṇyāhajayaśabdaiśca mahatā tumulena vā|| 2.60||
% tumulena ca| \ T75
sthāne susaṃskṛte ramye śivasya purataḥ śanaiḥ|
sthāpayitvā guruṃ bhaktyā taṃ praṇamya nivedayet|| 2.61||
% sthāpayedvā guruṃ bhaktyā praṇamya viniveśayet| \ T75
%% p.197
śāntyarthamekamadhyāyaṃ gobrāhmaṇamahībhṛtām|
% śāntyarthameva(na)madhyāyaṃ gobrāhmaṇamahīṃ bhṛtām| \ T75
rāṣṭriyanagarāṇāñca vācayed vācakottamaḥ|| 2.62||
% rāṣṭrāṇāṃ nagarāṇāṃ ca \ T75
chando lakṣaṇatatvajñaḥ satkavirmadhurasvanaḥ|
% satkaviṃ madhurasvaraḥ| \ T75
gāndharvavidvidagdhaśca śreṣṭhaḥ pustakavācakaḥ|| 2.63||
% śraṣṭhaḥ pustakavācakaḥ| \ T75
śāntitoyena rājānaṃ samutthāya gurustataḥ|
% samutthāya guruṃ tataḥ| \ T75
śirasyabhyukṣayedīṣat tatrasthaśca jalantataḥ|| 2.64||
% tatrasthaṃ ca janaṃ tataḥ| \ T75
avadhārya jagacchāntiṃ punarante nṛpasya ca|
% athavāryajagacchāntiṃ \ T75
ācāryabhojanañcātra nṛpaḥ kuryāt sadakṣiṇam|| 2.65||
% nṛpaḥ kuryāt sadakṣiṇām| \ T75
svayamatraiva bhuñjīta sāntaḥpuraparicchadaḥ|
kāryā ca vividhā proktā bhuktavatsu janeṣu ca|| 2.66||
% kāryāśca vividhāḥ prekṣā bhuktavatsu janeṣvapi| \ T75
evaṃ kṛte mahāśāntir nṛpasya nagarasya ca|
% evaṃ kṛte mahāśāntiṃ \ T75
deśasya ca samastasya jāyate nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 2.67||
% rāṣṭrasya ca samantasya jāyate nātra saṃśayaḥ| \ T75
%% Tp.19
ītayaśca praśāmyanti na ca mārī pravartate|
% arātayaḥ praṇaśyanti na ca māri \ T75
śāmyanti sarvaghorāṇi praśamanti bhayāni ca|| 2.68||
unmūlyante grahāḥ sarve praṇaśyanti ca śatravaḥ|
% grahāstuṣyanti sarve'pi \ T75
upasargāḥ pralīyante na durbhikṣabhayaṃ bhavet|| 2.69||
% u(vu)pasargāḥ pralipyante \ T75
vināyakāśca naśyanti saubhāgyaṃ paramaṃ bhavet|
% vidhāyakāśca naśyanti \ T75
rājyavṛddhiśca vipulā nityañca vijayī nṛpaḥ|| 2.70||
% nityaṃ ca vijayaṃ nṛpaḥ| \ T75
vardhate putrapautraiśca matirdharme pravartate|
vidyādānaprasādena nṛpasya ca janasya ca|| 2.71||
anena vidhinā rājā yaḥ śivajñānapustakam|
% vidyādānaprasādena + anenavidhinā rājā + yaśśivajñānapustakam| \ T75
dadyāt tadabhiyuktāya vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.72||
yo vā'nyaḥ puruṣaḥ kaścichraddhāvittānusārataḥ|
% śrddhāvittasamanvitaḥ| \ T75
kuryād vidhimimaṃ strī vā vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.73||
% kuryā . . .  vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet| \ T75
daridraścānusāreṇa vittaśāṭhyavivarjitaḥ|
% daridraścārthasāreṇa \ T75
kṛtvā vidhimimaṃ bhaktyā vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.74||
yasya yāvad bhaved vittaṃ sa tasyehānusārataḥ|
% sa tasyaihānusārataḥ| \ T75
aśāṭhyena acaretpuṇyam āḍhyatulyaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.75||
% adhya(sya)tulyaphalaṃ labhet| \ T75
yāvadakṣarasaṃkhyānaṃ śivajñānasya pustake|
% yāvadakṣarasaṃkhyānāṃ \ T75
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi dātā śivapure vaset|| 2.76||
% tāvatkālasahasrāṇi tathā \ T75
daśa pūrvān samuddhṛtya daśaṃ vaṃśyāśca paścimān|
% daśavaṃśyāṃśca paścimām| \ T75
mātāpitṛdharmapatnīḥ svarge sthāpya śivaṃ vrajet|| 2.77||
% mātāpitṛṛn dharmapatnīn  . . . . śivaṃ vrajet| \ T75
%% p.198
sāntaḥ puraparivāraḥ sarvabhṛtyasamanvitaḥ|
% nāntaḥ puraḥ parīvāraḥ \ T75
%% Tp.20
rājā śivapuraṅgacched vidyādānaprabhāvataḥ|| 2.78||
% divyaṃ śivapuraṃ \ T75
vimānayānaiḥ śrīmadbhiḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaḥ|
manoramyairasaṃkhyānaiḥ krīḍate kālamakṣayam|| 2.79||
% manojavairasaṃkhyātaiḥ \ T75
paramāṣṭaguṇaiśvaryairupetaḥ sarvataḥ prabhuḥ|
% satataṃ prabhuḥ| \ T75
sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇātmā dvitīya iva śaṅkaraḥ|| 2.80||
yathāmarāṇāṃ sarveṣāṃ paramaḥ parameśvaraḥ|
tathaiva sarvadānānāṃ vidyādānaṃ paraṃ smṛtam|| 2.81||
anenaiva vidhānena yaḥ śivaṃ jñānapustakam|
kusumagṛhake sthāpya pūjayīta śivāśrame|| 2.82||
% kusumāgārakaṃ sthāpya pūjayeta \ T75
āṣāḍhyāṃ pūrṇimāsyāṃ tu dīpamālāvibodhanaiḥ|
% dīpamālyāvabodhanaiḥ| \ T75
vaiśākhyāñcāpi sampūjya vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.83||
yaḥ śrīmatpustakam ālekhya vinivedayet|
% yaśśrīmatpustakavaraṃ navalekhyaṃ nivedayet| \ T75
śivajñānābhiyuktāya tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 2.84||
yāvat tatpatrasaṃkhyānaṃ mañcaketīvaśobhanam|
% @patrasaṃkhyānāṃ sañcayetīvaśobhate| \ T75
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|| 2.85||
% rudraloke mahīyate| \ T75
yatpatraṃ yantrasūtrādyaṃ maṣībhājanalekhanī|
% yaḥ patrayantrasūtrādyaiḥ maṣibhājanalekhane| \ T75
śarayantrāsanābhyaṅga śayyāsadbhaktavetanam|| 2.86||
% śarayantrāsanādyaṅgaṃ śayyāṃ tadbhaktavetanam| \ T75
ityevamādi yaccānyat tadartham upayujyate|
yadvā tadvā mahatsūkṣmaṃ vidhānena tu yadbhavet|| 2.87||
% yadvā tadvā ma . tsūkṣmaṃ vinā yena na bhavet| \ T75
tadekamapi vidyāṅgaṃ śraddhāvittānusārataḥ|
%% Tp.21
nivedya sa mahābhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate|| 2.88||
pustakāstaraṇaṃ datvā dadvastraśca pramāṇataḥ|
% sadvastraṃ vā pramāṇataḥ| \ T75
tadvāsanavitānaṃ vā śivaloke mahīyate|| 2.89||
% tadvāsasaṃ vitānaṃ vā \ T75
yāvattadvastratantūnāṃ parisaṃkhyā samantataḥ|
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi mahābhogānavāpnuyāt|| 2.90||
% mahābhogamavāpnuyāt| \ T75
śivajñānābhiyuktāya bhaktācchādan dadāti yaḥ|
% bhaktyācchādyaṃ dadāti yaḥ| \ T75
āsamāpteravicchinnaṃ vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.91||
upānacchatrakaupīnaṃ śayyāprāvaraṇāsanam|
% upānacchatrakaupīnaśayyā@ \ T75
pādasnehāñjanābhyaṅgaṃ snānabhojanabheṣajam|| 2.92||
% pādapūjāṃjanābhyaṃgasnāna@ \ T75
yatimātropakaraṇaṃ maṭhasammārjanāñjanam|
% maṭhasaṃmārjanādikam| \ T75
dīpāgnitoyapuṣpādyaṃ śivapustakavācanam|| 2.93||
% śivapustakavācinām| \ T75
%% p.199
yaḥ kuryādetadakhilaṃ śivajñānaratātmakam|
% yaḥ kuryādetamakhilaṃ śivajñānaratātmanām| \ T75
pañcānāṃ pañcavarṣāṇi vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.94||
triḥsaptakulamuttārya sthāpayedvaiṣṇave pure|| daiśvare|
% trisaptakulamuttārya sthāpayedvaiṣṇave pure| \ T75
te'tra tadvipulairbhogaiḥ krīḍantyācandratārakam|| 2.95||
% tatra tadvipulairbhogaiḥ krīḍatyācandratārakam| \ T75
kalatraputrasadbhṛtyairyuktaḥ śivapure naraḥ|
% kalatrabhṛtyasadbhṛtyaiḥ \ T75
akṣayaṃ modate kālaṃ vimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|| 2.96||
vidyāmaṇḍalakaṃ vṛttaṃ yadi vā caturastrakam|
% yadi vā caturaśrakam| \ T75
dvihastamadhikaṃ vāpi kṛtvā sadgomayāmbhasā|| 2.97||
% kṛtvā gomayavāriṇā| \ T75
%% Tp.22
sitaraktādibhiścūrṇaiḥ samantādupaśobhitam|
sitapadmayutaṃ madhye dadvitānavibhūṣitam|| 2.98||
vicitrakusumākīrṇaṃ pradīpākṣatasaṃyutam|
sampūjyaivaṃ śivajñānaṃ śraddhayā vācayīta yaḥ|| 2.99||
% śraddhayā vācayettataḥ| \ T75
ādyantaṃ tatkramātsarvam ekarūpaṃ śanaiḥ śanaiḥ|
% ādyaṃ tataḥ kramātsarvam \ T75
sarvalokapakārārtham ātmanaśca samṛddhaye|| 2.100||
% ātmanaḥ puṇyavṛdhaye| \ T75
tatsamāptau śivaṃ vidyām ācāryañca prapūjayet|
% kalpayedbhojanaṃ paścātsarveṣāṃ śivayoginām| \ T75
% ya evaṃ bhaktitaḥ kuryācchivajñānasya vācakam| \ T75
% mūlena kārayedvāpi vidyādānaṃ phalaṃ labhet| \ T75
% api ślokaṃ tadardhaṃ vā śivajñānasya yaḥ paṭhet| \ T75
%% Above 4 lines are missing in the printed edition, form Nepal.
vācayeccintayedvāpi lekhayellipayīta vā|| 2.101||
% likhedvā lekhayeta vā| \ T75
śṛṇuyādekacittaśca tadarthañca vicārayet|
janebhyaḥ śrāvayedyaśca tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 2.102||
yaḥ pradadyānmahīpūrṇāṃ sarvayatnaistu yatphalam|
% triḥ pradāya mahīṃ pūrṇāṃ \ T75
ślokārdhaṃ śivajñānasya pāṭhanat phalamāpnuyāt|| 2.103||
% ślokārdhamīśvarajñānādyatphalaṃ tadavāpnuyāt| \ T75
yaḥ śrīparṇīsamudbhūtanimnakhātaṃ susañcayam|
% yaśśāmaṇīsamudbhūtaṃ nimnabhūtaṃ susaṃcayam| \ T75
dadyāt sampuṭakaṃ kṛtvā carmaṇā vāpi nirmitam|| 2.104||
% dadyātsaṃkaṭakaṃ bhaktyā \ T75
śivajñānābhiyuktāya tadadhyayanadetunā|
% tadadhyāyanahetunā| \ T75
suślakṣṇaphalakaṃ vāpi vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.105||
% svarṇākṣaphalakāṃ vāpi vidyādānaphalaṃ labhet| \ T75
%% Tp.23
mahāvimānaiḥ śrīmadbhiḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaiḥ|
kriḍate paramaṃ kālaṃ rudraloke vyavasthitaḥ|| 2.106||
tataḥ kālāt kṣitiṃ prāpya rājā bhavati dhārmikaḥ|
surūpaḥ daddvijo vāpi sarvavidyārthapāragaḥ|| 2.107||
% svarūpātsadvijo vāpi \ T75
yaḥ sauvarṇaṃ susampūrṇaṃ sarvaratnopaśobhitam|
sapidhānaṃ samañjūṣaṃ vidyākoṣasamāśrayam|| 2.108||
% . . . . . . vidyādānasamāśrayam| \ T75
kārayedvāpi raupyeṇa tāmreṇa caturasrakam|
% kārayedvāpi kāvyeṇa(kāṃsyena) tāmereṇa caturaśrakam| \ T75
kāṃsyārakūṭalauhairvā dāruvaṃśādinirmitam|| 2.109||
% kāṃsyārakūṭalohairvā  \ T75
%% p.200
tatkaṣāyānuraktena carmaṇābhinavena ca|
% satkaṣāyānuraktena \ T75
antarbahiśca mathayedvidyāvāsagṛhaṃ navam|| 2.110||
% antarbahiśca dṛḍhaye  . . . . sagṛhaṃ navam| \ T75
sarvāśmakaṭakopetaṃ dṛdhasūtranibandhanam|
% na(sa) dvārakaṭakopetaṃ \ T75
kuryāttālakasaṃyuktaṃ vidyāratnakaraṇḍakam|| 2.111||
% vidyārakṣakaraṇḍakam| \ T75
evaṃ vittānusāreṇa kārayitvānurūpataḥ|
% kārayitvā su(nu)rūpataḥ| \ T75
prakṣyālya gandhatoyena vidyāvāsagṛhasya daḥ|| 2.112||
% vidyā . . . śagṛhaṃ varam| \ T75
kṛtvā vastravaraṃ divyamntaḥpuṣpaṃ gṛhānvitam|
% kṛtvā ca sadgṛhaṃ divyamantapuṣpagṛhānvitam| \ T75
vidyāsiṃhāsanaṃ tatra sampūjya vidhivad budhaḥ|| 2.113||
% vidhipatpūjayettataḥ| \ T75
tasmin puṇyāhaśabdena vidyākoṣagṛhanyaset|
% vidyākośaṃ gṛhaṃ nyaset| \ T75
tataścandanakarpūrau kuḍmumādaiḥ pralepayet|| 2.114||
% tataḥ candanakarpūrakuṅkumādyaiḥ pralepayet| \ T75
antarvastrayutaṃ dhūpaṃ satpuṣpairabhipūjayet|
% antaryaṃtrayutaṃ dhūpya sapuṣpairapi pūjayet| \ T75
tato vāditranirghoṣairvidyākoṣaṃ prapūjayet|| 2.115||
%% Tp.24
tataḥ sampūjayed vidyāṃ mahāvibhavavistaraiḥ|
% yathāvibhavavistaraiḥ| \ T75
kṛtvā pradakṣiṇañcānte namatsarvāṅgikaṃ budhaḥ|| 2.116||
% nametsarvāṅgikaṃ naraḥ| \ T75
vidyākoṣagṛhasyāpi vidyāyatanamuttamam|
bhavet suśobhanantasya cāṣṭahastapramāṇataḥ|| 2.117||
% bhavet suśobhanaṃ ramyam aṣṭahastapramāṇataḥ| \ T75
śileṣṭakāmṛṇmayaṃ vā saddārukṛtameva vā|
kapāṭārgalasaṃyuktaṃ prākārāsanaśobhitam|| 2.118||
% kavāṭāṭṭālasaṃyuktaṃ prākārāmaśobhitam| \ T75
patākādhvajasaṃyuktaṃ sadvitānasuśobhanam|
% vitānadhvajasaṃyuktaṃ sadvitānavibhūṣitam| \ T75
ghaṇṭācāmarasaṃyukta kiṅkiṇīravakānvitam|| 2.119||
% ghaṇṭācāmarasaṃyuktaṃ \ T75
candanāgurugandhādyairanuliptaṃ samantataḥ|
nityaṃ sugandhakairdhūpaiḥ puṣpaiścaivādhivāsayet|| 2.120||
% nityaṃ sugandhakarpuraiḥ puṣpaiścāpyadhivāsayet| \ T75
tatra taṃ tūryaghoṣeṇa maṅgalairvividhairapi|
% tatra sūktasughoṣeṇa \ T75
ānīya sthāpayedbhaktyā vidyāratnakaraṇḍakam|| 2.121||
tataḥ sugandhapuṣpādyaiḥ śivavat pratipūjayet|
śivavidyāṃ sadākālaṃ trisandhyamupacārataḥ|| 2.122||
tataḥ samāgatān sarvān bhojayecchivayoginaḥ|
dīnāndhakṛpaṇādyāṃśca dakṣayitvā kṣamāpayet|| 2.123||
% dīnāndhakṛpaṇādīṃśca \ T75
evaṃ yaḥ śivavidyāyāḥ kuryādāyatanaṃ śubham|
sa muktaḥ pātakaiḥ sarvairvidyādānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.124||
kulaikaviṃśaduttārya sabhṛtyaparibāritaḥ|
% kulaikaviṃśamuttārya sadbhṛparivāri(pāli)taḥ| \ T75
prāpyāṣṭaguṇamaiśvaryaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 2.125||
%% p.201
%% Tp.25
yastatra jñānamāsādya viṣayān viṣavat tyajet|
sa prāpnoti parāṃ muktiṃ rāgī bhogānavāpnuyāt|| 2.126||
% sa prāpnoti paraṃ muktiṃ bhogī \ T75
sṛṣṭyantare punaḥ prāpte pṛthivyāmekarāḍ bhavet|
sarvaiśvaryaguṇopetaḥ sarvajñānārthapāragaḥ|| 2.127||
% sarvajñānasya pāragaḥ| \ T75
yaḥ kārayenmahāramyaṃ suvedīsaṃsthitapuram|
% suvediṃ susthitaṃ puram| \ T75
pañcabhaumaṃ tribhaumaṃ vā śivajñānaratātmanām|| 2.128||
guhāpravarakairyuktaṃ maitrasthānasamanvitam|
% guhyāpagargakairyuktaḥ maitrasthānasamanvitaḥ| \ T75
vāstuvidyāvibhaktañca prākāraparivāritam|| 2.129||
% prākārapariśobhitam| \ T75
tasya vedī dvihastoccā paryantastambhasaṃyutam|
% paryantastaṃbhasaṃyutā| \ T75
pakveṣṭakāparicchannā tatsurambhastramantaram|| 2.130||
% pakveṣṭikāparicchannaṃ tatsuramyaṃ samantataḥ| \ T75
savīdhyāḥ purataḥ kāryaṃ diśyāgneyāṃ mahānasam|
% sucitraṃ purataḥ kuryāddeśāgneyryāṃ mahāsa(na)nam| \ T75
dhūmanirgamanopetaṃ pūrvataḥ satramaṇḍapam|| 2.131||
% pūrvatastatramaṇḍapam| \ T75
gandhapuṣpagṛhaṃ kāryam aiśānyāṃ paṭasaṃyuta|
% paṭasaṃyutam| \ T75
bhāṇḍāgāraṃ ca kauberyāṃ koṣṭhāgārañca vāyavye|| 2.132||
udakāśrayañca vāruṇyāṃ vātāyanasamanvitam|
samitkuśendhanasthānam āyudhānāñca nairṛte|| 2.133||
abhyāgatālayaṃ ramyaṃ śayyāsanasapādukam|
% śayyāsanasamanvitam| \ T75
toyāgnidīpasadbhṛtyairyuktaṃ dakṣiṇato bhavet|| 2.134||
% yo yāgnidīpasa(na)cchatrairyuktaṃ \ T75
gṛhāntarāṇi sarvāṇi jalajaiḥ kadalīgṛhaiḥ|
% sadajaiḥ kadalīgṛhaiḥ| \ T75
pañcavarṇaiśca kusumaiḥ śobhitāni prakalpayet|| 2.135||
%% Tp.26
prākārāntarbahirdadyāt pañcahastapramāṇataḥ|
% prākāraṃ tadbahiḥ kuryāt \ T75
prākārācca bahiḥ kuryāt sarvadikṣu samantataḥ|| 2.136||
divyaṃ śivāśramārāmaṃ nānāpuṣpopaśobhitam|
sarvarttukaguṇopetaṃ nānāvṛkṣasamanvitam|| 2.137||
% bahuvṛkṣajalānvitam| \ T75
priyaṅguśirīṣāśokapuñjīvakarañjakaiḥ|
% priyaṅguśāriṣāśokapatrajīvakariṣṭi(ṣṭa)kaiḥ| \ T75
punnāganāgabakulaiḥ pāṭalābilvacampakaiḥ|| 2.138||
% pāṭalī bilvacampakaiḥ| \ T75
śvetamandāravijayairjātītagarakuñjakaiḥ|
% jātityagarukuñjakaiḥ| \ T75
suvarṇaśvetayūthībhirbāṇāmrātakuruṇṭakaiḥ|| 2.139||
% suvarṇaiśśetayūthibhiḥ bāṇālatākuraṃ bakaiḥ| \ T75
karavīrakarṇikārair nānāvarṇairanekaśaḥ|
% karavīraiḥ karṇikāraiḥ \ T75
sthānavinyāsaracitaissanmārgādhārasaṃyutaiḥ|| 2.140||
% saṃmārgādhānasaṃyutaiḥ| \ T75
puṣpairbahuvidhairyuktaṃ digvidikṣu jalānvitam|
% vṛkṣairbahuvidhairyuktaṃ \ T75
sitaraktārkakusumair nīlaraktotpalairyutam|| 2.141||
%% p.202
latāvitānagṛhakaiḥ kvacikvacidavasthitaiḥ|
% vicitraiścadavasthitaiḥ| \ T75
kadalīstambhaṣaṇḍaiśca dāḍimādyairvirājitam|| 2.142||
iti kṛtvā bahistasya prākāraṃ kalpayenmahat|
kapāṭagopuropetaṃ parikhāvaṃśasaṃyutam|| 2.143||
% kavāṭagopuropeta parighātarusaṃyutam| \ T75
tṛtīyāñca parādūrdhvaṃ vidyāvyākhyānamaṇḍapam| 
% tṛtīyācca \ T75
gavākṣanirgamopetaṃ vicitraṃ parikalpayet|| 2.144||
parārdhaṃ pañcamaṅkāryaṃ śivasya vaḍa(bala)bhīgṛham|
% purācca paścimaṃ kāryaṃ śivasya valabhīgṛham| \ T75
ṣaḍḍhastamaṣṭhapaṭṭaṃ vā cārupaṭṭavinirmitam|| 2.145||
% ṣaḍantamaṣṭadīrghaṃ ca dvārapaṭṭavinirmitam| \ T75
%% Tp.27
tatra mṛddāruśailaṃ vā sthāpayedvidhivacchivam|
sarvavidyāvidhātāraṃ sarvajñaṃ lakulīśvaram|| 2.146||
vṛtaṃ śiṣaiḥ praśiṣyaiśca vyākhyānodyatapāṇikam|
% prata . . śirṣaiśca guṇibhiḥ \ T75
padmāsanasthaṃ suśvetaṃ prasannavadanaṃ śubham|| 2.147||
% prasannavadanaṃ gurum| \ T75
evaṃ śivāśramaṃ kṛtvā bhaktyā vittānusārataḥ|
tatpratiṣṭhāntataḥ kuryāt pūjāsaṃskāralakṣaṇam|| 2.148||
% tatra tiṣṭhāṃ tataḥ kuryāt \ T75
vidyādānoktavibhavaiḥ śobhāṃ kṛtvā tathāgrataḥ|
% śobhāṃ kṛtvā maṭhāgrataḥ| \ T75
pañcabhiḥ pañcagavyena sthāpyaiśānyāṃ śivāṅkramāt|| 2.149||
% pañcamṛtpañcagavyena snāpyeśānyāṃ \ T75
snāpayed gandhatoyādyaiḥ snānavastreṇa saṃyutam|
% snāpya vastreṇa chādayet| \ T75
tūryaghoṣaistamānīya sthāpayet puṣpamaṇḍape|| 2.150||
% tūryaghoṣaissamānīya \ T75
tataścandanapuṣpādyaiḥ pūjayitvā'dhivāsayet|
japtvā pañcavidhaṃ stotraṃ śivaṃ vijñāpayet tataḥ|| 2.151||
adyādhivāsanaṃ deva śvaḥ pratiṣṭhāvidhistava|
% adyādhivāsitaṃ devaṃ śvapratiṣṭhāvidhi punaḥ| \ T75
bhaktānāmupakampāyai sannidhyam upakalpayeḥ|| 2.152||
% bhaktānāmanukampārthaṃ śāntyarthamula(ta)kalpayet| \ T75
prātaḥ snāpya punardevaṃ pūjayitvā prakalpayet|
% pūjayitvā praveśayet| \ T75
pavitraiḥ sthāpayed vedyāṃ pādādārabhya pañcabhiḥ|| 2.153||
tataḥ sugandhagandhādyairnityaṃ bhāvyaṃ sugandhibhiḥ|
% nityaṃ bhaktyā śivālayam| \ T75
śivaśca pūjayet puṣpaiḥ snānaṃ varjyaṃ sugandhibhiḥ|| 2.153||
saśiṣyastaṃ praṇamyeśaṃ gururvyākhyāṃ pravartayet|
prāṅmukhodaṅmukho vāpi puṇyāhārthaṃ śivāgrataḥ|| 2.154||
%% Above 3 lines, 153cd - 154cd, are missing in T75.
tataḥ sampūjayedbhaktyā yajamānaḥ svayaṃ gurum|
% śivaṃ ca pūjayedbhaktyā yajamānassvayaṃ gurum| \ T75
dakṣiṇābhirvicitrābhirbhojanādyaiśca pūrvavat|| 2.155||
% pūjayet| \ T75
nivedayet tataḥ sthānaṃ sarveṣāṃ śivayoginām|
%% Tp.28
sarvopakaraṇapetaṃ praṇipatya punaḥ punaḥ|| 2.156||
evaṃ yaḥ kārayedādyaḥ śrīmacchivapuraṃ mahat|
%% p.203
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate|| 2.157||
sagotraṃ triṃśakopetaḥ sabhṛtyaparivāritaḥ|
% sagotraṃ \ conj; sa gotraṃ \ ed
% svagotraṃ śatakopetassadbhṛtyaparicārataḥ| \ T75
putramitrādisaṃyuktaḥ sāntaḥ puraparicchadaḥ|| 2.158||
suvicitrairmahāyānairasaṃkhyaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ|
% sarvagāmikaiḥ| \ T75
śivavat krīḍate bhogairaṇimādiguṇānvitaḥ|| 2.159||
% śivavaktrodite śambhoraṇimādiguṇairyutaḥ| \ T75
tataḥ kālena mahatā vidyādānaprabhāvataḥ|
jñānayogaṃ samāsādya tatraiva parimucyate|| 2.160||
% tatraiva sa vimucyate| \ T75
sthapatiḥ sthāpakā vṛkṣā valīvardāḥ sukarmiṇaḥ|
% sthapatiḥ sthāpako vṛkṣāt | \ T75
yānti rudrapuraṃ sarve tadadhyakṣāśca ye narāḥ|| 2.161||
% yānti rudrapuraṃ sarve tada . . . . ye narāḥ| \ T75
ye cāpi vṛttibhṛtakāḥ śivāyatanakarmaṇā|
% ye cāpi bhṛtyā bhṛtakāḥ \ T75
te'pi yānti mṛtāḥ svargā śivakarmānubhāvataḥ|| 2.162||
% svargaṃ śivadharmānusārataḥ| \ T75
śivadāsatvamāpannā naranārīnapuṃsakāḥ|
% śivadāsatvamāpannāḥ \ T75
te'pi tannāmasaṃyogādyānti rudrapuraṃ mahat|| 2.163||
dattāḥ krītāḥ praviṣṭāśca daṇḍopannā balāhṛtāḥ|
% dattāṃ krītāḥ praviṣṭaśca daṇḍotpannā baloddhṛtāḥ| \ T75
vijñeyā rudragaṇikāḥ śivāyatanayogataḥ|| 2.164||
% śivāyatanayoṣitaḥ| \ T75
%% p.204
yā rudragaṇikotpannā putrapautrādisarvataḥ|
% yā rudragaṇikotpannāt . . . . . disaṃtataḥ| \ T75
sāpi yāti mṛtā svargaṃ māturevānubhāvataḥ|| 2.165||
śivāyatanaparyante mriyante ye'pi jantavaḥ|
%% Tp.29
te'pi yānti śivaṃ lokaṃ kiṃ punastatsamāśritāḥ|| 2.166||
atyalpamapi yaḥ kuryādatiramyaiḥ śivāśramam|
dvirekavasatimātraṃ so'pi yāti śivaṃ puram|| 2.167||
% vitastihastamātraṃ vā so'pi yānti \ T75
kṛtvā sukuṭṭimāṃ bhūmim īśvarāyatanāgrataḥ|
tatra maṇḍalakaṃ kuryāt suvṛttaṃ gomayāmbhasā|| 2.168||
% kuryāt vṛttaṃ vā caturaśrakam| \ T75
sūtreṇa sumitaṅkṛtvā nānāvarṇakaśobhitam|
% sūtreṇa sammitaṃ kṛtvā \ T75
vicitrakusumākīrṇaṃ madhye paṅkajaśobhitam|| 2.169||
% vicitrakusutkīrṇaṃ \ T75
pradīpākṣatasaṃyuktam udakaṃ bhrāmya pāṇinā|
% udakaṃ grāhya pāṇinā| \ T75
mūrdhnā praṇamya medinyāṃ śivāya vinivedayet|| 2.170||
yaḥ kuryāt sakṛdapyevaṃ śivamaṇḍalakannaraḥ|
sa sarvakāmasaṃyuktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate|| 2.171||
% sa sarvakāmaiḥ saṃyuktaḥ \ T75
kālāt punarihāyātaḥ śrīmān arthapatirbhavet|
jñānavān rūpavān bhogī supriyaḥ sudvijaḥ sukhī|| 2.172||
% jñānavan rogahīnaśca supriyassaddvijassukhī| \ T75
vidyāmaṇḍalakaṃ kṛtvā vidyāvyākhyānamaṇḍape|
tatrābhyarcya śivajñānaṃ tadvyākhyāṃ śṛṇuyāttataḥ|| 2.173||
% vyākhyānaṃ śṛṇuyāttataḥ| \ T75
śivamaṇḍalakādyena vidhinātīva śobhanam|
gurumaṇḍalakaṃ kṛtvā śivaloke mahīyate|| 2.174||
śivavidyāgurūṇāñca kṛtvā maṇḍalakaṃ trayam|
yaḥ śṛṇoti śivajñānaṃ tasya vidyāprasīdati|| 2.175||
anena vidhinā jñānaṃ yaḥ śṛṇoti pravakti ca|
% yaḥ pravartiśśṛṇoti vā| \ T75
%% Tp.30
sa samprāpya śriyaṃ saukhyaṃ dehānte muktimāpnuyāt|| 2.176||
% sa saṃprāpya śivaṃ saukhyaṃ \ T75
ārogyaśālāṃ yaḥ kuryānmahāvaidyapuraskṛtām|
sarvopakaroṇopetāṃ tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 2.177||
dharmārthakāmamokṣāṇāmārogyaṃ sādhanaṃ yataḥ|
tasmādārogyadānena dattaṃ syāttaccatuṣṭayam|| 2.178||
apyekamārtaṃ vidvāṃsaṃ susthīkṛtya prayatnataḥ|
prāpnoti sumahatpuṇyamanantaṃ kṣayavarjitam|| 2.179||
%% p.205
jñānayogarataṃ śāntaṃ rogārtaṃ śivayoginam|
yaḥ karoti naraḥ svasthaṃ sarvadānaphalaṃ labhet|| 2.180||
brahmaviṣṇusurāḥ sarve vyādhayaḥ svajanā nṛpāḥ|
% svadārā nṛjanā nṛpāḥ| \ T75
yogasyaite mahāvighnā vyādhayastena yoginām|| 2.181||
brahmakṣatraviśaḥ śūdrān rogārtān yān prayatnataḥ|
% brahmakṣatraviśaśśūdrāḥ rāgārtān pālayatyataḥ| \ T75
yatpuṇyamahadāpnoti na tatsarvairmahāmakhaiḥ|| 2.182||
ākāśasya yathā nāntaḥ surairapyupalabhyate|
% āśāyasya yathā nā(sā)ntassurairapyupalabhyate| \ T75
tadvādārogyadānasya nāntaḥ saṃvidyate tathā|| 2.183||
% tadvadārogyadānasya nāntassaṃpadyate tathā| \ T75
puṇyamānena mahatā gatvā śivapurannaraḥ|
% śivapuraṃ naraḥ| \ T75
modate vividhairbhogairvimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|| 2.184||
ekaviṃśakulapetaḥ sabhṛtyaparivāritaḥ|
% evaṃ śivaguṇopetaḥ sadbhṛtyaparivāritaḥ| \ T75
āste śivapure tāvadyāvadābhūtasamplavam|| 2.185||
tatastakkarmaśeṣeṇa samprāpte pralaye tathā|
% tatastaddharmaśeṣeṇa \ T75
%% Tp.31
jñānamutpadyate tasya rudrebhyaḥ parivāritaḥ|| 2.186||
% rudrebhyaḥ pratipāditam| \ T75
jñānād viraktaḥ saṃsāre śivadhyānamupāśritaḥ|
% śivajñānaṃ samāśritaḥ| \ T75
svadehaṃ tṛṇavat tyaktvā sarvaduḥkhāntamāpnuyāt|| 2.187||
% sadehaṃ tṛṇavattyaktvā \ T75
samastaduḥkhanirmuktaḥ śuddhaḥ svātmavyavasthitaḥ|
% śuddhasvātmanyavasthitaḥ| \ T75
sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇaśca mukta ityabhidhīyate|| 2.188||
tasmād bhogāpavargārthaṃ rogārtaṃ samupācaret|
% rogārthaṃ sa(na)mupācaret| \ T75
viśeṣeṇa ca yogīndramātmanā ca dhanena ca|| 2.189||
rogiṇo nodvijet prājñastanmalānāśca sarvataḥ|
% rogīṇāṃ tyajetprājñastanmūlānāṃ ca sarvataḥ| \ T75
sampaśyed guruvannityamevaṃ dharmaḥ pravartate|| 2.189||
yo'nugṛhītamātmānaṃ manyamāno dine dine|
upasarpati rogārtaṃ tīrṇastena bhavārṇavaḥ|| 2.190||
% upasarpeta rogārtaṃ \ T75
% tasmātsarvaprayatnena vidyādānaṃ samācaret| \ T75
%% Above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
evametadbahuvidhaṃ vidyādānaṃ prakīrtitam|
sarveṣāmeva varṇānāṃ vidhinānena tadbhavet|| 2.191||

\Colo
iti śrīśivadharmottare vidyādāno nāma dvitīyo'dhyāyaḥ|
% iti śrīśivadharmottare śāstre vidyādānaphalaṃ nāma dvitīyodhyāyaḥ| \ T75
% śrīsāmbasadāśivārpaṇamastu | \ T75

%% Chapter 3

%% p.206
%% Tp.32

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivadharmottare
jñānayogo nāma tṛtīyo'dhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
% (śrīḥ|) \ T75
% (|atha tṛtīyodhyāyaḥ|) \ T75
% |śubhamastu| \ T75
atha ye satataṃ bhaktā bhavanti śivayoginām|
% atha ye satataṃ bhaktyā \ T75
te vindanti mahābhogānante yogañca śāṅkaram|| 3.1||
bhogayogārthibhistasmāt sampūjyāḥ śivayoginaḥ|
pratiśrayānnapānena śayyāvastrātsanādibhi|| 3.2||
yaḥ sthānagātraśuśrūṣāṃ prakuryācchivayoginām|
% yannāma gātraśiśrūṣā \ T75
daridraḥ satataṃ bhaktyā tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 3.3||
% daridrassatataṃ bhaktastasya \ T75
sūryatejaḥ pratīkāśairvimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ|
% sarvagāmikaiḥ| \ T75
mṛtaḥ śivapuraṃ gacchet trisaptakulasaṃyutaḥ|| 3.5||
tatra divyairmahābhogaiḥ strīsahasrairmanoramaiḥ|
kalpakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ sevyamānaḥ sa tiṣṭhati|| 3.6||
tadante viṣṇubhavane tāvatkālaṃ vaset punaḥ|
vaiṣṇavairvividhairbhogaiḥ strīsahasraiśca pūjitaḥ|| 3.7||
% strisahasraissamanvitaḥ| \ T75
viṣṇulokād brahmalokaṃ samprāpya krīḍate punaḥ|
% viṣṇulokāccyuto brāhmyāṃ saṃprāpya (ca) vasetpunaḥ| \ T75
bhogaiḥ suvipulaiḥ sūkṣmaistāvatkālamanuttamaiḥ|| 3.8||
% bhogaistu vividhaissūkṣmaiḥ \ T75
prajāpatīndragandharvayakṣalokeṣvanukramāt|
% prajāpatyendragāndharva yakṣalokeṣvanukramāt| \ T75
bhogānnānāvidhān bhuktvā pṛthivyāṃ jāyate kramāt|| 3.9||
kule mahati viprāṇāṃ prajñāśīlaguṇānvitaḥ|
%% Tp.33
tataḥ sa pūrvabhāvena yogīndrān paryupāsate|| 3.10||
% tatassaṃpūrṇabhāvena yogīndraṃ paryupāsati| \ T75
tatsamparkācchivajñānaṃ prāpya yogaṃ niṣevate|
yogād viraktaḥ saṃsārāt prāpnoti paramaṃ padam|| 3.11||
% yo dviraktassaṃsārāt| \ T75
iti yaḥ kurute bhaktiṃ satataṃ śivayoginām|
sa dvitīye tṛtīye vā dehe yogamavāpnuyāt|| 3.12||
atha pūjādikāryādyair bhedairbahuvidhaiḥ sthitaḥ|
% bhedairbahuvidhaistataḥ| \ T75
karmayogaḥ samākhyātastapaścāndrāyaṇādikaḥ|| 3.13||
% karmayajñassamākhyātastapaścāndrāyaṇadikam| \ T75
svādhyāyaśca japaḥ proktaḥ śivamantraśca sa dvidhā|
% śivamantrasya tattridhā| \ T75
dhyānayajñaḥ samākhyātaḥ śivacintā muhurmuhuḥ|| 3.14||
adhyāpanamadhyayanaṃ vyākhyā śravaṇacintanam|
% adhyāpanaṃ hi taddhyānaṃ \ T75
iti pañcaprakāro'yaṃ jñānayajñaḥ prakīrtitaḥ|| 3.15||
%% p.207
uttarottaravaiśiṣṭyaṃ sarveṣāṃ parikīrtitam|
% uttarottarataśśreṣṭhaṃ \ T75
pañcānāmapi yajñānāṃ dhyānayajño vimuktidaḥ|| 3.16||
% jñānayajño vimuktidaḥ| \ T75
nāsti jñānaṃ vinā dhyānaṃ nāsti jñānamayoginaḥ|
% nāsti jñānamayoginām| \ T75
jñānadhyānañca yasyāsti tīrṇastena bhavārṇavaḥ|| 3.17||
jñānaṃ prasannamekāgram aśeṣopādhivarjitam|
yogābhyāsena satataṃ viraktasyopajāyate|| 3.18||
śrutañcitāmayaṃ jñānaṃ vikalpabahulaṃ yataḥ|
% śruticintāmayajñānaṃ vikalpabahuśaṃ yataḥ| \ T75
tasmāttadaprasanntvāccañcalanna vimuktidam|| 3.19||
śrutād vivardhate prajñā prajñātaścintayet punaḥ|
% śrutvāpi vardhayejjñānaṃ prājñāstaccintayet punaḥ| \ T75
%% Tp.34
vimalantat prasannañca cintyamānaṃ bhavecchanaiḥ|| 3.20||
ārambhakālaḥ śravaṇaṃ kriyākālaśca cintaram|
% āraṃbhakāle śravaṇaṃ kriyākāle vicintanam| \ T75
cintayā bhāvanā tasya niṣṭhā kāle prasannatā|| 3.21||
% niścayādbhāvanaṃ tasya niṣṭhākāle prasannataḥ| \ T75
jñānaṃ vikalpabahulaṃ rāgādyaiḥ kaluṣīkṛtam|
% jñānaṃ vikalpabahuśaṃ \ T75
nājñānamalaśuddhyarthaṃ kaluṣodakavad bhavet|| 3.22||
% ajñānamalaśudhyarthaṃ \ T75
niḥsāram atikaṣṭaṃ ca bhavaṃ bhāvayataḥ śanaiḥ|
ambhasīva śaratkāle tatprasannaṃ kramād bhavet|| 3.23||
% ambhovacca śaratkāle \ T75
yadā prasannamekāgraṃ stimitodadhivat sthitam|
% sthitimodadhisaṃsthitam| \ T75
tadā jñānamiti proktam ajñānamiti cetarat|| 3.24||
% ajñānamitaratpunaḥ| \ T75
iti prasannaṃ yajjñānaṃ bhāvanāmayamuttamam|
rāgādyairaparāmṛṣṭaṃ tadvijñeyaṃ vimuktidam|| 3.25||
ajñānapāśabaddhatvādamuktaḥ puruṣāḥ smṛtaḥ|
% ajñānapāśabandhatvādamuktaḥ \ T75
tasmājjñānena muktiḥ syādajñānāsya parikṣayāt|| 3.26||
saṃsārabījamajñānaṃ saṃsārajñaḥ pumān yataḥ|
% saṃsārabandhamajñānaṃ saṃsāryajñaḥ pumāṃsmṛtaḥ| \ T75
jñāttasya nivṛttiḥ syāt prakāśāttamaso yathā|| 3.27||
ajñāne sati rogādyā dharmādharmau ca tadvaśau|
% ajñānena tirāgādyā dharmādharmau ca tadvaśaḥ| \ T75
dharmādharmavaśāt puṃsaḥ śarīramupajāyate|| 3.28||
% puṃsāṃ śarīramupajāyate| \ T75
śarīre sati saṃkleśaiḥ sarvaiḥ saṃyujyate yataḥ|
% sā yujyate yataḥ| \ T75
tataḥ kleśaprahāṇārthaṃ punardehanna kāmayet|| 3.29||
jagatastattvasambodhādajñānaṃ vinivartate|
%% Tp.35
ajñānavinivṛttau ca rāgādīnāmasambhavaḥ|| 3.30||
rāgādyupaśamātpuṃsaḥ puṇyapāparikṣayaḥ|
% rāgādyupaśamātpuṃsāṃ puṇyapāpa(pa)rikṣayaḥ| \ T75
tatkṣayācca śarīreṇa na punaḥ samprayujyate|| 3.31||
%% p.208
aśarīraśca saṃkleśaiḥ sarvaireva na bādhyate|
% sarvadaiva na bādhyate| \ T75
kleśamuktaḥ prasannatvānmukta ityabhidhīyate|| 3.32||
% prasannātmā mukta ityabhibhīyate| \ T75
tasmādajñānamūlāni sarvaduḥkhāni dehinām|
jñānena ca tadajñānannivarteta na karmabhiḥ|| 3.33||
% jñāne sahitadajñānaṃ nivarteta sakarmabhiḥ| \ T75
nāsti jñānādṛte puṃsāṃ puṇyapāpaparikṣayaḥ|
mokṣārthī puruṣastasmājjñānameva sadābhyaset|| 3.34||
mārjyamānaḥ sadā yadvad darpaṇo nirmalo bhavet|
% mārjyamāṇaḥ sadā \ T75
jñānābhyāsāttathā puṃsāṃ buddhirbhavati nirmalā|| 3.35||
% jñānābhyāsāttadā puṃsāṃ buddhirbhavati nirmalaḥ| \ T75
jñānāmṛtaraso yena sakṛdāsvādito bhavet|
sa sarvakāryāṇyutsṛjya tatraiva paridhāvati|| 3.35||
sa sarvakāryāṇi . . . . . paridhāvati| \ T75
jñānāmṛtarasaḥ prāyastena nāsvādito bhavet|
yenānyatrābhiramate tadvihāyaiva durmatiḥ|| 3.36||
% yenānyatraiva ramate tadvihāya sudurmatiḥ| \ T75
jñānāmṛtena tṛptasya kṛtakṛtyasya yoginaḥ|
naivāsti kiñcit kartavyam asti cenna sa tattvavit|| 3.37||
% asti cenna natakvacit| \ T75
lokadvaye'pi kartavyaṃ kiñcittasya na vidyate|
% kiñcidanyanna vidyate| \ T75
ihaiva sa vimuktaḥ syāt sampūrṇapriyadarśanaḥ|| 3.38||
% sampūrṇassamadarśanaḥ| \ T75
nāsti jñānātparaṃ kiñcit pavitraṃ pāpanāśanam|
%% Tp.36
tat sadābhyāsayogena śanairātmani vindati|| 3.39||
% vratāni dānāni tapāṃsi yajñās sanyāsatīrthāśramadharmayogāḥ| \ T75
% svargīyametatsukhamadhuvaṃca jñānaṃ dhruvaṃ śāntikaraṃ mahārtham|| \ T75
%% Above two lines are missing in the printed edition, form Nepal.
yajñena devānāpnoti taporbhirbrahmaṇaḥ padam|
% yajñairdevatvamāpnoti \ T75
dānena vividhān bhogān jñānānmokṣamavāpnuyāt|| 3.40||
dharmarajjvā vrajedūrdhvaṃ pāparajjvā vrajatyadhdaḥ|
% vrajetya(da)dhaḥ| \ T75
dvayaṃ jñānāsinā chitvā videhaḥ śāntimṛcchati|| 3.41||
jñānināṃ yadyadharmeṇa bhaved bandhaḥ śubhena vā|
huhuta muktiḥ kathanteṣāṃ nibaddhānāṃ śubhāśubhaiḥ|| 3.42||
% dhruvamuktiḥ kathaṃ teṣāṃ \ T75
nahi dehabhṛtā śakyaṃ karma tyaktuṃ śubhāśubham|
gacchatastiṣṭhato vāpi tadavaśyaṃ bhavedyataḥ|| 3.43||
adharmavinivṛttau ca bhavetpuṇyamakurvataḥ|
% adharmavinivṛtyaiva \ T75
dharmatyāgādadharmaśca sa tiṣṭhenniścalaḥ katham|| 3.44||
% na teṣāṃ niścalaḥ katham| \ T75
tasmājjñānāsinā tūrṇam aśeṣaṅkarmabandhanam|
% tasmājjñānaṃ vinā tūrṇam \ T75
kāmākāmakṛtaṃ chitvā śuddhaḥ svātmani tiṣṭhati|| 3.45||
% śuddhasvātmani tiṣṭhati| \ T75
yathā vahnirmahān dīptaḥ śuṣkamārdrañca nirdehet|
% yathā vahnimahādīptā \ T75
tathā śubhāśubhaṃ karma jñānāgnir dahati kṣaṇāt || 3.46||
%% p.209
padmapatraṃ yathā toyaiḥ svakairapi na lipyate|
% toyaistasthairapi na lipyate| \ T75
śabdādiviṣayāmbhobhis tadvajjñānī ca lipyate|| 3.47||
% stadvajjñānaṃ na lipyate| \ T75
yadvanmantrabalopetaḥ krīḍan sarpairna daśyate|
% yadvā mantrabalopetaḥ krīḍan sarpairna daṃśyate| \ T75
%% Tp.37
krīḍanna daśyate jñānī tadvadindriyapannagaiḥ|| 3.48||
% krīḍannavivya(lipya)te \ T75
mantrauṣadhibalairyadvajjīryate bhakṣitaṃ viṣam|
% mantrauṣadhibalairyadvadbhakṣitaṃ jīryate viṣam| \ T75
tadvatpāpāni karmāṇi jīryante jñānināṃ kṣaṇāt|| 3.49||
% tadvatsarvāṇi pāpāni jīryante jñāninaḥ kṣaṇāt| \ T75
nāsti jñānasamaṃ tīrthaṃ nāsti jñānasamantapaḥ|
nāsti jñānasamo yajñastasmājjñānaṃ samabhyaset|| 3.50||
% sadābhyaset| \ T75
yathā jñānaṃ tathā dhyānaṃ jñānadhyānaṃ samaṃ smṛtam|
jñānadhyānarataḥ saukhyaṃ punarmokṣañca vindati|| 3.51||
% munirmokṣaṃ ca vindati| \ T75
jñānādaiśvaryamatulam aiśvaryātsaukhyamuttamam|
% aiśvaryātsa . . . muttamam| \ T75
jñānena tatparityajya vitanurmokṣamāpnuyāt|| 3.52||
% tanumuktimavāpnuyāt| \ T75
sarveṣāmeva yajñānāṃ jñānayajñaḥ paraḥ smṛtaḥ|
% jñānadhyānaṃ paraṃ smṛtam| \ T75
nityaṃ śuddhaḥ prasannaśca sarvadoṣavivarjitaḥ|| 3.53||
% nityaśuddhaḥ prasannaśca  \ T75
śuklakṛṣṇaparaḥ sūkṣmaḥ suviśuddhaḥ samādhijaḥ|
śuklakṛṣṇaḥ pa(va)rassukṣmaḥ \ T75
jñānayajñaḥ paro jñeyaḥ sthūlo'śuddhaśca karmiṇām|| 3.54||
% jñānayajñaḥ paro yajñaḥ sthūlo śuddhaśca karmaṇām| \ T75
viśuddhaḥ sādhanaiḥ sūkṣmairdhyānayajñaḥ prasādhyate|
% viśuddhaissādhanaiḥ \ T75
yasmāttasmādviśuddho'yamapavargaphalapradaḥ|| 3.55||
antarbahiryogopacāreṇa yaḥ pūjayati śaṅkaram|
% antaryāgopacāreṇa \ T75
dhyānayajñena satataṃ sa yāti paramāṅgatim|| 3.56||
% dhyānamajñānasatataṃ \ T75
puṣpairyamaniyamārthairātmakaikādaśabhiḥ pariḥ|
% puṣpaidyandaissaniyamairātmaikādaśabhiḥ paraiḥ| \ T75
daśadikṣu tathā madhye yajeta parameśvaram|| 3.57||
karmayajñāttapoyajño viśiṣṭo daśabhirguṇaiḥ|
%% Tp38
japayajñastapoyajñājjapaḥ śataguṇādhikaḥ|| 3.58||
% japayajñastapoyajñaḥ jñeyaśśataguṇādhikaḥ| \ T75
jñānadhyānātmakaḥ sūkṣmaḥ śivayogamahāmakhaḥ|
% śivayogamahāmakhaḥ(ghaḥ)| \ T75
variṣṭaḥ sarvayajñānāmasaṃkhyātairmahāguṇaiḥ|| 3.59||
% variṣṭhaḥ \ T75
pūjayā vipulaṃ rājyam agnikāyeṇa sampadaḥ|
japena pāpaśuddhiḥ syājjñānadhyāne na mucyate|| 3.60||
% japena pāpasaṃśuddhirjñānadhyānena mucyate| \ T75
% [mārjyamāṇassadā yadvaddarpaṇo nirmalo bhavet| \ T75
% jñānabhyāsāttathā puṃsāṃ buddhirbhavati nirmalaḥ||] \ T75
prakṣīṇāśeṣapāpasya jñānadhyāne bhavenmatiḥ|
% prakṣīṇāśeṣadoṣasya \ T75
pāpāpahatabuddhīnāntadvārttāpi sudurlabhā|| 3.61||
% pāpopahatabuddhīnāṃ \ T75
dhanuṣāṃ koṭibhiryogaḥ samantāt parirakṣyatekṣati|
% samantātparirakṣyate| \ T75
sahasraiḥ ṣaṣṭibhirgaṅgā dharmatīrthāni cārdhataḥ|| 3.62||
% dharmajñetraṃ tadardha(rtha)taḥ| \ T75
% dharmakṣetraṃ \ ed
%% p.210
tīrthāni toyapūrṇāni devāḥ pāṣāṇamṛṇmayāḥ|
yogino na prapadyante svātmapratyayakāriṇaḥ|| 3.63||
agnau kriyāvatāṃ devā divi devā manīṣiṇām|
pratimāsvaprabuddhānāṃ yogināmātmani sthitāḥ|| 3.64||
śivamātmani paśyanti pratimāsu na yoginaḥ|
ajñānāmbhāvanārthāya pratimā parikalpitā|| 3.65||
%% Above two verses 64 & 65 are missing in T75.
ātmatthaṃ yaḥ śivaṃ tyaktvā bahiḥsthaṃ yajate śivam|
% ātmasthaṃ yaśśivaṃ tyaktvā bahiṣṭhaṃ \ T75
haste piṇḍaṃ samutsṛjya lihet kūrparamātmanaḥ|| 3.66||
% hastasthaṃ piṇḍamutsṛjya vihetkorparamātmātmanaḥ| \ T75
sarvatrāvasthitaṃ ye tu na prapaśyanti śaṅkaram|
% sarvatrāvasthitaṃ śāntaṃ \ T75
jñānacakṣurvihīnatvādandhāḥ sūryaṃ yathoditam|| 3.67||
% @vihīnatvādandhaḥ \ T75
yaḥ paśyt sarvagaṃ śāntaṃ tasyātmasthaḥ śivaḥ sadā|
% yaḥ paśyat \ T75
ātmasthaṃ ye na paśyanti tīrthe mārganti te śivam|| 3.68||
ātmasthaṃ tīrthamutsṛjya bahistīrthāni yo japet|
% yo vrajet| \ T75
%% Tp.39
karasthaṃ sa mahāratnaṃ tyaktvā kācaṃ hi mārgati|| 3.69||
jñānadhyānarataiḥ śāntairyadyastyevaṃ (sasto) yaṃ niṣevitam|
% śāntairyadyattoyaṃ niṣevitam| \ T75
pāpaśuddhyartham ajñānāt tattīrthaṃ na tu yoginām|| 3.70||
% pāpaśudhyarthamajñānāṃ \ T75
divasaṃ divasārdhaṃ vā yatra tiṣṭhatti yoginām|
% yatra tiṣṭhanti yoginaḥ| \ T75
unmaṅgalyaṃ pavitraṃ tattattīrthaṃ tattapodhanam|| 3.71||
% tanmāṅgalyaṃ pavitraṃ ca \ T75
jijñāsurapi yogasya yāṃ gatiṃ labhate muniḥ|
na tāṃ gatimavāpnoti sarvairapi mahāmakhaiḥ|| 3.72||
satyamāgamavārtāyām apratyakṣe ca tatphale|
adhyeyam aiśvaraṃ jñānaṃ alpakleśaṃ mahāphalam|| 3.73||
% adhyeyamīśvarajñānam \ T75
yadi kleśena mahatā bhavet puṇyaṃ mahāphalam|
% mahāphalam| \ T75
syānmahāratnavāhibhyaḥ phalaṃ pāṣāṇavāhinām|| 3.74||
pāṣāṇaśatasāhasraṃ yaḥ skandhenābhivāñchati|
% yasskandhe voḍhumicchati| \ T75
voḍhuṃ śramavināśaṃ vā naiva tatphalamāpnuyāt|| 3.75||
% śramameti vināśaṃ vā so buddhistadvihanniva| \ T75
aṅguṣṭhodaramātrepi sukhaṃ saṃvāhya yatphalam|
% aṅguṣṭhodamātraṃ tu viśiṣṭaḥ padmarāṭ maṇiḥ| \ T75
na tatphalamavāpnoti hitaṃ pāṣāṇavāhinaḥ|| 3.76||
% prāptastu sukhasaṃvāhyo mahatorthasya nāthakaḥ| \ T75
evaṃ hi kaṣṭāni tapāṃsi yajñān kleśātmakānalpaphalapradāśca|
santyajya sarvān śivayogamekaṃ dhyāyetparaṃ muktikaraṃ viśuddham|| 3.77||
% dhyāyetparaṃ muktikaraṃ praśāntam| \ T75
jñānayogaḥ pradhānatvādantaraṅgo vimuktidaḥ|
%% Tp.40
bahiraṅgapradhānaṃ yajñādyaṃ bhogasādhanam|| 3.78||
% bahiraṅgo pradhānatvādyajñādyaṃ \ T75
%% p.211
yathehāntaścarā rājñāṃ priyā śambhorna karmiṇaḥ|
% yaddehāntaścarārājñāṃ priyāssyuḥ na bahiścarāḥ| \ T75
tathāntardhyāna niratāḥ priyāḥ śambhorna karmiṇaḥ|| 3.79||
% tathāntadhyānaniratāḥ \ T75
bahiḥ karmakarā yadvannātīva phalabhāginaḥ|
% bahiḥ karmakarāyadvā nātīva phalabhoginaḥ| \ T75
dṛṣṭvā narendrabhavane tadvadatrāpi karmiṇaḥ|| 3.80||
% dṛṣṭā narendrabhavane tadvattatrāpi \ T75
yathāntaḥpuracāreṇa naraḥ strīṣu prasīdati|
tathāntardhyānavidhinā prasīdati maheśvaraḥ|| 3.81||
yathāntardantināṃ dantāḥ sukhino na bahiḥ sthitāḥ|
% yathāntardantino dantāḥ \ T75
tathāntarghyānaniratāḥ saphalā na bahiḥ sthitāḥ|| 3.82||
% tathāntardhyānaniratāssaphalāni bahisthitāḥ| \ T75
atyalpi yathā dīpaḥ sumahannāśayettamaḥ|
% samahaṃ nāśayaṃ tamaḥ| \ T75
yogābhyāsastathalpo'pi mahāpāpaṃ vināśayet|| 3.83||
ardhayāmaṃ muhūrtaṃ vā dhyāyataḥ paramaṃ śivam|
dhyāyataṃ parameśvaram| \ T75
yadbhavet sumahatpuṇyam antastasya na vidyate|| 3.84||
yadyantarā vipadyeta jñānayogārthamudyataḥ|
% yadyantarepi \ T75
śraddhayā gurubhaktyā rudralokaṃ sa gacchati|| 3.85||
% śraddhayā gurubhaktyā ca \ T75
anubhūya sukhaṃ tatra kulanāthena yoginām|
% kule jāyeta yoginām| \ T75
jñānayogaṃ tataḥ prāpya saṃsārādvinivartate|| 3.86||
% saṃsāramativartate| \ T75
mṛdumadhyādhimātratvācchraddhā puṃsāṃ tridhā sthitā|
% mṛdurmadhyottamā caiva śraddhā puṃsāṃ tridhā smṛtāḥ| \ T75
janmatrayād dhruvaṃ jñānaṃ mandaśraddho'pi vindati|| 3.87||
% janma tridhā dhruvaṃ jñānaṃ mantaśśraddhopi vi+ddhati(vindati)| \ T75
tasmāt svargiyamutsṛjya karmayogamanuttamam|
% tasmātsvargaṃ samutsṛjya karmayogam aśāśvatam| \ T75
%% Tp.41
dhyāyannityaṃ viśuddhañca jñānayogamanuttamam|| 3.88||
% dhyāye nityaṃ viśuddhaṃ ca \ T75
ityetajjñānayogasya mahābhāgyamudāhṛtam|
% ityevaṃ jñānayogasya \ T75
tadabhyāsaratānāñca munīnāṃ śāntacetasām|| 3.89||
% tadābhyāsaratānāṃ ca \ T75

\Colo
iti śivadharmottare jñānayogo nāma tṛtīyo'dhyāyaḥ|
% iti śrīśivadharmottare pañcamahāyajñaguṇādhyāyo nāma tṛtīyodhyāyaḥ| \ T75
% iti śrīsāmbasadāśivārpaṇamastu| \ T75

%% Chapter 4

%% p.212
%% Tp.42
atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre
śivadharmottare satpātrapradānannāma caturtho'dhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
% śrīḥ
% atha caturtho'dhyāyaḥ|
% śubhamastu| śivāya gurave namaḥ |
athaikabhavikaṃ dānaṃ karmayogaratātmanām|
śatajanma bhaveddānaṃ taponiṣṭhapratiṣṭhitam|| 4.1||
% śatajanmabhavaṃ dānaṃ taponiṣṭhe pratiṣṭhitam| \ T75
japayajñābhiyuktebhyaḥ sahasrabhavikaṃ smṛtam|
āhūbhūtaḥ samplavasthāpi pradānaṃ śivayoginām|| 4.2||
% ābhūtasaṃpavasthāyī \ T75
atyalpamapi yaddattaṃ śivajñānārthavedinām|
% atyalpamapi yo dattaṃ \ T75
tanmahāpralayaṃ yāvad dāturbhogāya kalpate|| 4.3||
% anubhogāya kalpate| \ T75
na dānamalpaṃ bahu vā kiñcid asti vijānataḥ |
% sadānamalpaṃ bahu vā \ T75
deśakālavidhiśraddhāpātrayuktantadakṣayam|| 4.4||
% deśakālavitaśrāddha pātrayuktaṃ tadakṣayam| \ T75
pātre deśe ca kāle ca vidhinā śraddhayā c a yat|
% deśa kāle ca pātre ca \ T75
dattaṃ hutaṃ kṛtaṃ ceṣṭaṃ tadanantaphalaṃ bhavet|| 4.5||
% dattaṃ kṛtaṃ hutaṃ cedattadanantaphalaṃ bhavet| \ T75
tilārdhamātrakeṇāpi yatpramāṇena dīyate|
% līlārthamatrakeṇāpi yatpramāṇena dīyate| \ T75
satpātre śraddhayā kiñcit tadbhavet sarvakāmikam|| 4.6||
% tatpātre śraddhayā kiñcit tadbhavet sarvakāli .| \ T75
yaddhautaṃ jñānasalilaiḥ śīlabhasmapramārjitam|
% yaddātaṃ \ T75
tatpātraṃ sarvapātrāṇām uttamaṃ sārvakāmikam|| 4.7||
jñānoḍupena yaḥ puṃsāṃ trātā saṃsārasāgarāt|
% trāti saṃsārasāgarāt| \ T75
ajñānāṃ pālanāt trāṇāt tatpātraṃ paramaṃ smṛtam|| 4.8||
% ajñānapatanāttrāṇāt pātraṃ tat paramaṃ smṛtam| \ T75
jñānaplavabalopetastrāti pāpamahārṇavāt|
% jñānaplavabalopetaḥ pātraṃ pāpamahārṇavāt| \ T75
%% Tp.43
nājñānastārayedavyaṃ kiṃ śilā tārecchilām|| 4.9||
% nājñā vitārayedajñaṃ kiṃ śilāṃ \ T75
dvijānāṃ vedaviduṣāṃ koṭiṃ sambhojya yat phalam|
% kohi saṃbodhya yatphalam| \ T75
bhikṣāmātrapradānena tatphalaṃ śivayoginām|| 4.10||
% tatphalaṃ śivayogine| \ T75
śivayogī gṛhe yasya bhikṣāṃ gṛhṇāti saṃskṛtām|
% bhikṣāṃ gṛhṇāti satkṛtam| \ T75
kulam uttārayet tasya narakārṇavasaṃsthitam|| 4.11||
yajñāgnihomatīrtheṣu yatphalaṃ parikīrtitam|
yoginām annadānena tatsamagraphalaṃ labhet|| 4.12||
jñānine śāntacittāya śivadhyānaratāya ca |
śraddhayānnaṃ sakṛd datvā sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate || 4.13||
ekaṃ munivaraṃ śāntam īśvararpitamānasam|
% īśvarārpitamānasam| \ T75
bhojayitvā sakṛd bhaktyā sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt|| 4.14||
%% p.213
dhyāyamānaḥ śivaṃ yogī bhuṅkte'nnaṃ satataṃ yataḥ|
tataḥ sākṣāc chivenaiva tadbhuktam aśanaṃ bhavet|| 4.15||
pitṛn uddiśya yaḥ śrāddhaṃ bhojayec chivayoginam |
% trayanuddiśya ya śrāddhe \ T75
sa gacched īśvarasthānam evaviṃśakulānvitaḥ|| 4.16||
% sa gacchedaiśvaraṃ sthānam ekaviśatkulānvitaḥ| \ T75
śivāya sarvapākāgraṃ nivedyāgnau ca homayet|
% śivāya sarvapāpā(ni) pranivedyāgau ca homayet| \ T75
kalpayecca gurorbhāgam ityeṣa satataṃ vidhiḥ|| 4.17||
% ityayaṃ satataṃ vidhiḥ| \ T75
śivāgniguruviprebhyaḥ sarvapākāgramanvaham|
% yo nivedya svayaṃ bhuṅkte sarudro nātra saṃśayaḥ| \ T75
%% Above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
yonivedyātmanā bhuṅkte sa bhuṅkte kilviṣaṃ naraḥ|| 4.18||
% anivedya ca yo bhuṅkte \ T75
%% Tp.44
kṛṣivṛdhyādivāṇijyakrodhāsatyārjanadibhiḥ|
% kṛṣivārdhuṣyavāṇijya krodhāsatyorjanādibhiḥ| \ T75
puṃsāṃ pāpāni vardhante sūnādoṣaiśca pañcabhiḥ|| 4.19||
sammārjanāñjanantoyam agnikaṇḍanapeṣaṇī|
% agnikuṇḍakapoṣaṇam| \ T75
sūnāḥ pañcagṛhasthānānnityaṃ pāpābhivṛddhaye|| 4.20||
śivāgnigurupūjābhiḥ pāpairetairna lipyate|
% nityaṃ pāpaiḥ na lipyate| \ T75
anyaiśca pātakairghoraistasmāt sampujayet trayam|| 4.21||
% annaiśca \ T75
śivāgnigurunaivedye yāvatsikthāni saṃkhyayā|
% śivāgnigurunaivedyaṃ yāvatsiddhāni saṃkhyayā| \ T75
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi dātā śivapure vaset|| 4.22||
% tadā śivapure vaset| \ T75
ghṛtasūpayutaiḥ sikthaiḥ puṇyaṃ daśaguṇottaram|
% ghṛtāplutayutaissiddhaiḥ puṇyaṃ daśaguṇottaram| \ T75
avadatsa yutairjñeyaṃ puṇyaṃ śataguṇottaram|| 4.23||
% upadaṃśayutairjñeyaṃ puṇyaṃ śataguṇādhikam| \ T75
ṣaṣṭikodananaivedyaiḥ sahasraguṇitaṃ phalam|
sugandhaśālinaivedyarvijñeyamayutādhikam|| 4.24||
% sugandhiśālinaivedyai \ T75
raktaśālyannanaivedyaḥ phalaṃ syānniyutādhikam|
% mātuluṃgakalalyāmrapanasādyaiśubhairnavaiḥ| \ T75
kalamaiḥ śālinaivedyairdaśalakṣadhikaṃ phalam|| 4.25||
% kalamāśālinaivedyairbhavennakṣādhikaṃ phalam| \ T75
evaṃ śāliviśeṣeṇa phalaṃ syāduttarottaram|
sadvyañjanayujāṃ bhūyastatpuṇyamabhivardhate|| 4.26||
% savyañjanayutaṃ \ T75
vyañjanāni vicitrāṇi svādūni surabhīṇi ca|
koṭiphalādhikānyāhuḥ snigdhāni madhurāṇi ca|| 4.27||
% koṭikoṭiphalānyāhuḥ \ T75
kṣīrabhaktena naivedyaṃ daśakoṭiguṇādhikam|
% kṣīradhuna naivedyaḥ daśabhuṅkte guṇādhikam| \ T75
%% Tp.45
pānakānāṃ sugandhānāṃ phalaṃ tulyaṃ rasālayā|| 4.28||
% rasālayoḥ| \ T75
tathā phalaviśeṣaiśca svādubhiḥ sadṛśaṃ phalam|
% svādubhissadaśabhissadṛśaṃ phalam| \ T75
guḍakhaṇḍakṛtairbhakṣyai ghṛtena paripācitaiḥ|| 4.29||
% gu.lakhaṇḍakṛtaiścāpi \ T75
koṭisahasraguṇitaṃ geyaṃ puṇyaṃ sugandhibhiḥ|
% koṭisāhasraguṇitaṃ \ T75
% nānāprakārairvividhaiḥ gṛtena paripācitaiḥ| \ T75
%% Above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
dadhiśarkarayā yuktaṃ tatpuṇyaṃ syāddaśādhikam|| 4.30||
%% p.214
rasālāṃ sughanāṃ sītāṃ karpūrasurabhīkṛtām|
% śītāṃ (śīlāṃ) karpūrasurabhīkṛtām|| \ T75
nivedya puṇyamāpnoti koṭikoṭiguṇādhikam|| 4.31||
%% Above 3 lines 30cd - 31cd occurs in-between 28ab & cd in T75.
gṛtāśanena vijñeyaṃ rasālātulitaṃ phalam|
% māṣatulyaphalaṃ budhaiḥ| \ T75
śarkarākhaṇḍayuktena rasālābhyadhikaṃ phalam|| 4.32||
% māṣādapyadhikaṃ phalam| \ T75
yathā yathā hi svādūni snigdhāni surabhīṇi ca|
% surabhīṇī ca| \ T75
bhaktyannapānamātrāṇi tatphalāni tathā tathā|| 4.33||
% bhikṣānnapānaśoṣyāṇi tatphalāni yathā tathā| \ T75
yadvā yadvā śivāyānnaṃ liṅgāni gurumūrtaye|
% liṅgāne gurumūrtaye| \ T75
bhaktyā nivedya bhuñjānaḥ phalamakṣayamāpnuyāt|| 4.34||
evaṃ yaḥ kurute śrāddhaṃ bhaktitaḥ śivayoginām|
sa pitṛn sarvapāpebhyaḥ samuddhṛtya divannayet|| 4.35||
% sa pitrān sarvapāpebhyaḥ samuddhṛtya śivaṃ nayet| \ T75
gaṅgāsnānasamaṃ puṇyaṃ darśanaṃ śivayoginām|
sarvatīrthābhiṣeka ca tatsambhāṣaṇam uttamam|| 4.36||
% sarvatīrthābhiṣekācca \ T75
mucyate sarvapāpebhyaḥ praṇamya śivayoginam|
%% Tp.46
śuśrūṣayitvā bhaktyā tu śivaloke mahīyate|| 4.37||
% śiśrūṣayuktyā ta. bhaktyā  \ T75
yugavat pūjitāstena brahmaviṣṇumaheśvarāḥ|
% yugapatpūjitāste \ T75
pitaraḥ sarvadevāśca yo'rcayeccivayiginam|| 4.38||
% mātarassarvadevāśca \ T75
tuṣyanti pitaras tasya suvṛṣycaiva ca karṣakāḥ|
% suvṛṣṭeriva karṣakaḥ| \ T75
yaḥ śrāddhe pūjayed bhaktyā viśeṣāc chivayogina || 4.39||
% yaḥ śrāddhe bhojayedbhaktyā \ T75
api naḥ sa kule kaścijjanayet putramīhaśam|
% āpīnasakule kaścit janayet putramīdṛśam| \ T75
yaḥ sampūjya śivaṃ śrāddhe bhojayecchivayoginam|| 4.40||
nṛtyanti pitarastuṣṭā gāyanti ca pitāmahāḥ|
adya naḥ putraḥ pautro vā yogivdraṃ bhojayiṣyati|| 4.41||
% adya naḥ putrapātro vā yogīndraṃ  \ T75
śivayoginamāyāntaṃ dṛṣṭaiva gṛhasaṃsthitam|
% gṛhasaṃsthitāḥ| \ T75
krīḍantyoṣadhayaḥ sarvā yāsyāmaḥ svargamakṣayam|| 4.42||
% kriḍantyoṣadhayaḥ sarvāḥ \ T75
anugrahāya lokānāṃ śraddhāyāśca parikṣaṇe|
% śraddhāyāśca parīkṣaye| \ T75
carantyatithirūpeṇa devā yogī ca bhūtale|| 4.43||
% devo yogācca bhūtale| \ T75
tasmādatithimāyāntam anugacchet kṛtāñjaliḥ|
% adhigacchet kṛtāñjaliḥ| \ T75
svāgatāsanapādyārghasnānānna śayanādibhiḥ|| 4.44||
% svāgatāsanapādyārghyāstānnāranāśayanādibhiḥ| \ T75
rūpānvitaṃ virūpaṃ vā malinaṃ malināmbaram|
% kṛpānvitaṃ virūpaṃ hi \ T75
yogīndrāśaṅkayā nityam atithinna vicārayet|| 4.45||
śivayogiśarīre tu nityaṃ sannihitaḥ śivaḥ|
% śivayogiśarīreṣu nityaṃ \ T75
yogīndraṃ pūjayet tasmāt sa sākṣāt pūjitaḥ śivaḥ|| 4.46||
% tasmāt sākṣāt sampūjayecchivaḥ| \ T75
% p.215
yoginaṃ ye dviṣantyajñāḥ sarvapāpavyavasthitāḥ|
% ye yogīndraṃ dviṣantyajjñāḥ sarvapāpeṣvanukramāt| \ T75
%% Tp.47
adhomukhordhvapādāste patanti narakāgniṣu|| 4.47||
% pacyante narakāgniṣu| \ T75
kṛmibhirbhinnavadanās tāpyamānāśca vahninā|
% kramabhirbhinnavadanā tapyamānācca vahninā| \ T75
prapīḍyante vadhairghorairyāvadacandratārakam|| 4.48||
ye śivajñānaniratān pradviṣanti manāgapi|
% ye śivajñānanirataṃ pradviyanti manāgapi| \ T75
paścād bāhukabaddhāste nīyante yamasādanam|| 4.49||
tatrāgnitaptaiḥ sandaṃśaiḥ prapīḍyoraśca pādataḥ|
% tatrāgnitaptasandaṃśaiḥ pravīdo ravi vādayoḥ(rapi pādayoḥ)| | T75
teṣām utpāṭyate jihvā śataśo'tha sahasraśaḥ|| 4.50||
% teṣām utpādyate jihvā \ T75
vikatthante mahātmānaṃ ye mūḍhāḥ śivayoginam|
% vikatthyante \ T75
te yānti śrotṛbhiḥ sārdhaṃ narakeṣu na saṃśayaḥ|| 4.51||
% te yānti śrotribhissārdhaṃ narakaṃ naiva saṃśayaḥ| \ T75
ye cāpavādaṃ śṛṇvanti vimūḍhāḥ śivayoginām|
% vimūḍhāśivayoginaḥ| \ T75
te viśeṣeṇa pacyante narakeṣvāmahīkṣayāt|| 4.52||
% te viśeṣeṇa vadhyante \ T75
sati śrotari vaktā syād apavādasya yoginām|
% sa ti śrotari vaktā syād avamānasya yoginaḥ| \ T75
tasmācchrotā tu pāpīyāṃstaddaṇḍaḥ sumahānataḥ|| 4.53||
% tasmācchrotātrapāpīyāṃ nādadātyumahātmanaḥ| \ T75
vaktā śrotā'numantā ca prayoktā dūṣaṇasya ca|
etaiḥ saṃyujyate pañca pañcaite nārakāḥ smṛtāḥ|| 4.54||
% eteṣāṃ yastu samparkaḥ \ T75
iti yogīndrapātrasya mahābhāgyam udāhṛtam|
pūjāpavādaṃ viṣayam apātraṃ śṛṇutādhunā|| 4.55||
% pūjyāpavādaviṣayamasya(sva) pātraṃ śṛṇutādhunā| \ T75
ajñānapaṅkanirmagnam ātmatrāṇavivarjitam|
% ātmatrāṇavivarjitaḥ| \ T75
apuṇyagiriṇākrāntam apātraṃ guṇavarjitam|| 4.56||
% apuṇyagiriṇākāntam \ T75
āmapātre raso yadvannaśyate tacca bhājanam|
% yadvā naśyate saha bhājanam| \ T75
%% Tp.48
dānam ajñe tathā nyasta saha pātreṇa naśyati|| 4.57||
% dānadujñe yathāsvastaṃ sahapātreṇa naśyati| \ T75
sadbījamuṣare yadvadvā pitaṃ niṣphalaṃ bhavet|
% sadbījamūṣake yadvā dustannikhilatāṃ vrajet| \ T75
dānaṃ tadvad pātreṣu vinyastaṃ niṣphalaṃ bhavet|| 4.58||
bhasmanīva hutaṃ havyaṃ yathā hotuḥ suniṣphalam|
% tasminniva hutaṃ havyaṃ \ T75
jñānāgnirahite pātre tathā dānam anarthakam|| 4.59||
% jñānāgnirahito vipro . . . ghādānaṃ nirarthakam| \ T75
yathā ṣaṇḍho'phalaḥ strīṣu yathā gaur gavi cāṣphalā|
% yathā ṣaṇḍo narastrīṣu puṃgavena vinā ca gauḥ| \ T75
mānavasya tathā janma jñānahīnasya niṣphalam|| 4.60||
% brāhmaṇasya tathā janma \ T75
lohoḍupena prataran nimajjatyaudake yathā|
% lobhoḍupena pacaraṃ(pradaraṃ) nimajjatyudake yathā| \ T75
tathā dātā grahītā ca patatyajñastathālpadhīḥ|| 4.61||
% patatyandhe tamasyadhaḥ| \ T75
kāruṇyāt sarvabhūtebhyaḥ śraddhayā yatpradīyate|
% kā . . . . rvabhūtebhyaḥ \ T75
dānaṃ tadapi vijñeyaṃ sarvakāmikamuttamam|| 4.62||
%% p.216
dīnāndhakṛpaṇānāthabālavṛddhakṛśāturān|
% @bālavṛddhakṛśāturāḥ| \ T75
etān anukampayāmītyarthī gṛhṇāti nispṛhaḥ|| 4.63||
% etenukaṃpyāssatataṃ nārthaṃ gṛhṇīta nispṛhaḥ| \ T75
adatvā jñāninaḥ pātraṃ nispṛhatvānna te'rthinaḥ|
% arhatyajñāninaḥ pātram aspṛhatvānna terthinaḥ| \ T75
alpikāpi hi tatpūjā paryāptā hyātmanaḥ phalam|| 4.64||
% alpikā vihitā pūjā paryāptaṃ karmiṇaḥ phalam| \ T75
na hi svārthasamuddiśya pratigṛhṇvanti sādhavaḥ|
% putraṃ hanti hi sādhavaḥ| \ T75
dātur evopakārāya yasmād gṛhṛnti[yasmād gṛhṇanti] nispṛhāḥ|| 4.65||
% dāturevopakārāya gṛhṇanti munayo manāt| \ T75
daridraḥ sādhubhiryatnāt prārthanīyo'nukampayā|
adānādasya dāridrān dānādaiśvaryam āpnuyāt|| 4.66||
% adānādanyadāridrya \ T75
dāturevopakārāya vadatyarthī dadasva me|
% vadatyarthī tadasya me| \ T75
%% Tp.49
yasmāddātā prayātyūrdhvam adhastiṣṭhet pratigrahāta|| 4.67||
% ayantiṣṭhetpratigrahī| \ T75
dehītyeva vadannarthī janaṃ bodhayatīva saḥ|
% dehītyevaṃ buvatyarthī janaṃ bādhayatīva saḥ| \ T75
yadidaṃ kaṣṭam arthitvaṃ prāgadānaphalaṃ hi tat|| 4.68||
% prāgadānaphalaṃ mahat| \ T75
bodhayanti na yāvatte dehīti kṛpaṇāñjanāḥ|
% bodhayanti na yācante dehīti kṛpaṇā janāḥ| \ T75
avastheyam adānasya mā bhūdevaṃ bhavānapi|| 4.69||
kalyāṇamitram āyāntam arthinaṃ ko na pūjayet|
dānāt svargam avāpnoti ko'nya bandhurihārthinaḥ|| 4.70||
% konya bandhorivārthinaḥ| \ T75
ihāmutra phalenāpi dātāram anuyojayan|
% ihamantraphalaissopi dātāramanu yo vrajet| \ T75
āyātyarthī gṛhandātuṃ kastanna pratipūjayet|| 4.71||
% ādhatyatyugrahaṃ dātuḥ \ T75
nārthinaḥ syuḥ katha pūjyāpacamānā dine dine|
% kathaṃ pūjā yācamānā dine dine| \ T75
ye balādapyanicchantaṃ yojayanti naraṃ śriyā|| 4.72||
% ye balādasya niścittaṃ \ T75
ahanyahani mārgantaṃ ko na manyadguruṃ yathā|
% ko na(sa) manyedguruṃ yathā| \ T75
mārjanaṃ darpaṇasyeva yaḥ karoti dine dine|| 4.73||
karamuttānakaṃ kṛtvā dānaṃ gṛhṇāti yo dvijaḥ|
dānādūrdhvagatistena dātu darśayatīva saḥ|| 4.74||
% dānādūrdhvagatiṃ tasya dāturdarśayatīva saḥ| \ T75
ekena tiṣṭhatyadhastadanyenopiri tiṣṭhati|
% ekena tiṣṭhatādastā(ntā)danyonyaṃ paritiṣṭhatā| \ T75
dātṛyācakayorbhedaḥ karābhyāmeva sūcitaḥ|| 4.75||
% karābhyāmeva nocitaḥ| \ T75
yaḥ prāptam arthinaṃ dīnaṃ tyaktvā pātramudīkṣate|
% tyaktvā pātram upekṣati| \ T75
sa vaṇigdharmayuktatvānna dātā paramārthataḥ|| 4.76||
% sa vaṇisthurmaktatvānāṃ dātā paramārthinaḥ| \ T75
yadyarthino narā na syur dānakarma kathaṃ bhavet|
% dāturdama kathaṃ bhavet| \ T75
%% Tp.50
satsvarthiṣu bhaveddānaṃ sa hi dāne ca tatphalam|| 4.77||
% natvarthiṣu bhaveddānaṃ na ca \ T75
yadi stabdhāḥ śaṭhā dīnā na syurapriyavādinaḥ|
kva nu dānaṃ dayā kṣāntirbhāvyate sādhubhistadā|| 4.78||
% kṣātraṃ dānaṃ tathā tathā kṣānta bhāryā tenādhu bhinndhā| \ T75
%% p.217
yadi nāma na deyaṃ syāt samprāptāyārthine gṛhe|
% yadi nāmani deyaṃ syāt samprāptāyārthine gṛham| \ T75
kiṃ vākyānyapi naṣṭāni priyāṇyanugatāni ca|| 4.79||
% kiṃ vākyasya vinaṣṭāni \ T75
pratyutthānābhigamanaṃ svāgataṃ svāsanaṃ priyam|
% abhyutthānābhigamanaṃ svāgataṃ cāsanaṃ priyam| \ T75
pādodakam anuvrajyā svargasopānapustakam|| 4.80||
% svargasopānasaptakam| \ T75
vittaṃ cittānusāreṇa kadā kasya bhaviṣyati|
% kadā kasyā bhaviṣyati| \ T75
grāsādardhamapi grāsaṃ yuktaṃ dātuṃ sadārthinām|| 4.81||
% dātuṃ yuktaṃ sadārthine| \ T75
dānaṃ priyavinirmuktaṃ naṣṭam āhur manīṣiṇaḥ|
% naṣṭamāhurvipaścitaḥ| \ T75
tasmāt sakṛtpradātavyam anantaphalamicchatā|| 4.82||
% tasmātsatkṛtya dātavyaṃ nareṇa phalamicchatā| \ T75
pratyākhyānam api śreyaḥ priyānunayapeśalam|
% pratyābhyāsamapi śreyaḥ priyāsu nayu peśalam| \ T75
na tu dānam asatkāra pāruṣyamalinīkṛtam|| 4.83||
% sa tu dānamasatkāra pāruṣyaṃ puruṣīkṛtam| \ T75
varaṃ na dattamarthibhyaḥ sakrodhenāntarātmanā|
% saṃkruddhetenāntarātmanā| \ T75
na taddhanaṃ na ca prītirna dharmaḥ priyavarjitaḥ|| 4.84||
% da . . śca na ca prīti sa dharmapriyavarjitaḥ| \ T75
dānaṃ vratāni niyamo yajñā dhyanaṃ hutaṃ tapaḥ|
% dānaṃ vratādi niyamaḥ yajñaṃ \ T75
yatnenāpi kṛtaṃ sarvaṃ krodhanasya vṛthā bhaveta|| 4.85||
% krodhinastadvṛthā bhavet| \ T75
yaḥ śraddhayārcitaṃ dadyāt pratigṛhṇāti cārcitaḥ|
% yaśśraddhayā sthitaṃ dadyāt pratigṛhṇāti vārthinaḥ| \ T75
tāvubhau gacchataḥ svargaṃ narakaṃ tadviparyayāt|| 4.86||
% narakaṃ tadviparyaye| \ T75
audāryaṃ svāgataṃ maitrīm anukampāmamatsaram|
% udāryāt sagatiḥ  . . maiśca manukaṃpā mahatsarā| \ T75
%% Tp.51
guṇānāvahate pañca dāturdānaṃ mahāphalam|| 4.87||
% guṇaṃ nu(su) vahate pañca \ T75
vārāṇasī kurukṣetraṃ prayāgaḥ puṣkarāṇi ca|
gaṅgā samudratīrañca naimiṣāmarakaṇṭakāḥ|| 4.88||
% naimīśāraṇyamaṣṭamam| \ T75
śrīparvato mānasañca gokarṇo vedaparvataḥ|
% śrīparvataṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ gokarṇaṃ vedaparvatam| \ T75
ityādyāḥ kīrtitā deśāḥ surasiddhaniṣevitāḥ|| 4.89||
% ityādikīrtitā deśāssyurasiddhaniṣevitāḥ| \ T75
sarve śivāśramāḥ puṇyāḥ sarvā nadyaḥ saparvatāḥ|
% sarvanadyāssaparvatāḥ| \ T75
gosiddharṣinivāsāśca deśāḥ puṇyāḥ prakīrtitāḥ|| 4.90||
% gosiddhāmunivāsaṃ ca puṇyadeśāḥ prakīrtitāḥ| \ T75
śivāyatanasaṃsthānāṃ yad alpam api dīyate|
% śivāyatanasaṃsthāne \ T75
tadanantaphalaṃ jñeyaṃ śivakṣetrānubhāvataḥ|| 4.91||
% śivakṣetrānubhāvitaḥ| \ T75
grahaṇañ candrasūryābhyāṃ dakṣiṇāyanam uttaram|
% uttarāyaṇadakṣiṇam| \ T75
viṣuvatsavyatīpātaṃ ṣaḍaśītimukhaṃ tathā|| 4.92||
% viṣuvaṃ saṃvyatīpātaṃ \ T75
dinakṣayāṇi saṃkrāntirjñeyaṃ viṣṇupadaṃ punaḥ|
% dinaścidrāṇi nākrānte jñeyaṃ \ T75
iti kālaḥ samākhyātaḥ puṃsāṃ puṇyavivardhanaḥ|| 4.93||
% iti kālāḥ samākhyātā puṃsāṃ puṇyavivardhitāḥ| \ T75
bhaktirbhāvaḥ parā prītiḥ śivadharmaikatānatā |
% śivadharmaikatāṃ gatā| \ T75
pratipattir iti jñeyaṃ śraddhāparyāyapañcakam|| 4.94||
% jñeyā śraddhāharyāya vañcakam| \ T75
%% p.218
śraddhāmātraṃ ca jananī jñānasya sukṛtasya ca|
% śraddhā māteva jananī jñānasya kṛtasya ca| \ T75
tasmācchraddhāṃ samutpādya deyamakṣayamicchatā|| 4.95||
yaddānaṃ śraddhayā pātre vidhivat pratipādanam|
% vidhivatpratipāditam| \ T75
tadanantaphalaṃ jñeyam api bālāgramātrakam|| 4.96||
% api pālāgramātrakam| \ T75
ārteṣu dīneṣu guṇānviteṣu yacchaddhayāsvalpamapi pradattam|
% tīrtheṣu dīneṣu \ T75
%% Tp.52
tatsarvakāmān samupaiti loke śraddhaiva dānaṃ pravadanti tajjñāḥ|| 4.97||
% śraddheva dānaṃ pravadanti tajñāḥ| \ T75
śraddhāpradhānaṃ vijñeyaṃ satpātrādicatuṣṭayam|
% satpātrāṇi catuṣṭayam| \ T75
śraddhātaḥ kīrtitā tasmānnāśraddhātaḥ phalaṃ bhavet|| 4.98||
% śraddhā te kīrtitā tasmānn āśraddhātaḥ phalaṃ labhet| \ T75

\ colo
iti śivadharmottare satpātrapradānaścaturtho'dhyāyaḥ|
% satpātraguṇaṃ nāma caturtho'dhyāyaḥ| \ T75
% śrīsāmbasadāśivāya parabrahmaṇe namaḥ| \ T75


%% Chapter 5

%% p.219
%% Tp.53

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre
śivadharmottare śivapuradharmagatirnāma pañcamo'dhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāyaḥ|
%% (atha) pañcamo'dhyāyaḥ|| \ T75
atha dharmāḥ śivenoktāḥ śivadharmāgamottare|
% śivadharmāgamottame| \ T75
jñeyā bahuvidhās te ca karmayogopabhedataḥ|| 5.1||
% karmayogapraprabhedataḥ| \ T75
hiṃsādoṣavinirmuktāḥ kleśāyāsavivarjitāḥ|
% haṃsā doṣavinirmuktāḥ kleśāyānavivarjitāḥ| \ T75
dharmā bhūtahitāḥ śuddhāḥ susūkṣmāḥ sumahāphalāḥ|| 5.2||
% sarvabhūtahitāśśuddhāssusūkṣmāssumahatphalāḥ| \ T75
anantaśāvāvalitāḥ śivamūle ca saṃsthitāḥ|
% anantaśākhākavitāḥ śivamūlaikasaṃśritā| \ T75
sarve sarvaguṇopetāḥ śivadharmāḥ sanātanāḥ|| 5.3||
tārayanty aśivādyamād dhāryante śivabhāvitaiḥ|
% yājayanti śivaṃ yasmād \ T75
śivadharmāḥ smṛtās tasmāt saṃsārārṇavatāraṇāḥ|| 5.4||
athāhiṃsā kṣamā satyaṃ hrīḥ śraddhendriyasaṃyamaḥ|
% hrīṃ śraddhendriyanigrahaḥ| \ T75
dānam ijyā japo dhyānaṃ daśakaṃ dharmasādhanam || 5.5||
% daśakaṃ dharmalakṣaṇam| \ T75
asamastaiḥ samastair vā śivadharmair anuṣṭhitaiḥ|
% atha vyastaissamastairvā \ T75
śivaikasthānasamprāptair gatiścaikaiva kirtitā|| 5.6||
% śivekasthānasamprāptiḥ gatirekaiva kīrtitā| \ T75
yathā bhūḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ sthānaṃ sādhāraṇaṃ smṛtā|
% sthānaṃ sādhāraṇaṃ smṛtam| \ T75
tathā tacchivabhaktānāṃ tulyaṃ śivapuraṃ smṛtam|| 5.7||
% bhogāssā(nnā)tiśayāssmṛtāḥ| \ T75
yatheha sarvabhūtānāṃ bhogāḥ sādhāraṇāḥ smṛtāḥ|
%% Above line is missing in T75.
nānāpuṇyaviśeṣeṇa bhogāḥ śivapure tathā|| 5.8||
% bhogāḥ śivapure . thā| \ T75
śubhāśubhaphalañ cātra bhujyate karma dehibhiḥ|
% bhajante sarvadehinaḥ| \ T75
śivadharmasya caikasya phalan tatropabhujyate|| 5.9||
yāpādṛgbhavetpuṇyaṃ śraddhāmātraviśeṣaṇam|
% yasya yāvadbhavetpuṇyaṃ śraddhāpātraviśeṣataḥ| \ T75
%% Tp.54
bhogās tādṛgvidhāstasya jñeyāḥ sātiśayāḥ pure|| 5.10||
% bhogāntā dṛgvidhāṃ tatra jñeyāssātiśayāstathā| \ T75
sthānaprāptiphale tulye bhogāḥ sātiśayāḥ sthitāḥ|
% sthānaprāptiparā tulyā \ T75
kuryāt puṇyaṃ mahat tasmān mahābhogajigīṣayā|| 5.11||
sarvādhipatyamevaikaṃ tatra nāsti purottame|
% sarvādhipatyamekaikaṃ \ T75
svātmabhogādhipatyaṃ syācchivaḥ sarvajagatpatiḥ|| 5.12||
kecit tatraiva mucyante jñānayogaratā narāḥ|
% @mucyante \ T75
āvartante punaś cānye saṃsāre bhogatatparāḥ || 5.13||
% vartante punaścānye \ T75
tasmād vimokṣam anvicched bhogāsaktiṃ vivarjayet |
% tasmāt parokṣamanvicchan bhogānsaktiṃ vivarjayet| \ T75
viraktaḥ śāntacittātmā śivajñānam avāpnuyāt || 5.14||
%% p.220
ye cānyāsaktahṛdayā yajantīśaṃ prasaṅgataḥ |
% ye cānye saktahṛdayā \ T75
teṣām api dadātīśa sthānaṃ bhāvānurūpataḥ || 5.15||
% sthānamātm ānurūpataḥ| \ T75
tatrārcayanti ye rudraṃ sakṛd ucchiṣṭakarmaṇā |
% tato(nnā)rcayanti ye rudraṃ sakṛducchiddiṣṭakalmaṣam| \ T75
teṣāṃ piśācalokeṣu bhogānīśaḥ prayacchati|| 5.16||
% bhogān śa prayacchati| \ T75
dvirarcayanti ye rudraṃ krurāḥ saṃkuddhalocanāḥ|
% dvirarthayanti ye rudraṃ krūrāssaṃkruddhalocanāḥ| \ T75
rakṣoloke śivas teṣāṃ mahābhogān prayacchati|| 5.17||
% mahībhogān prayacchati| \ T75
trirarcayanti ye rudraṃ madyamāṃsāturā narāḥ|
yakṣaloke śivasteṣāṃ divyān bhogān prayacchati|| 5.18||
% yakṣo loke \ T75
ye gītanṛtyaṃ kurvanti triścaturvā yadṛcchayā|
% ye nu . . . . ptagītaṃ kurvanti tricaturvā yadṛcchayā| \ T75
śivāgratas tu te yānti gandharvabhavanan narāḥ || 5.19||
% śivāgratastaṃ te yānti gāndharvaṃ bhuvanaṃ narāḥ| \ T75
loke khyātiṃ samuddhiśya pañcārcayati yaḥ śivam|
% lokā khyātiṃ samuddiśya \ T75
%% Tp.55
tasyendrabhavane rudraḥ kāmān divyān prayacchati|| 5.20||
% ta . . ndra bhavane \ T75
kāmāśaktena cittena yaḥ ṣaḍarcayate śivam|
% ṣaḍarcayati yaśśivam| \ T75
prājāpatye śivas tasya loke bhogān prayacchati || 5.21||
% somaloke śivastasya kāmān divyān prayacchati| \ T75
dāridryamuktihetutvāt saptārcayaty upoṣitaḥ|
% saptārcayanti ye rudraṃ gandhapuṣpādibhiḥ kramāt| \ T75
somaloke śivenaiva divyair bhogai ramanti (te) ca|| 5.22||
% prājāpatye śivastasya loke bhogān prayacchati| \ T75
% aṣṭārcayanti gāyatryā śivaṃ ye vedatatparāḥ| \ T75
% sadbhāvataśśivasteṣāṃ brahmalokaṃ prayacchati| \ T75
% na vārcayanti ye rudramekatvaṃ samupāśritāḥ| \ T75
% te yānti viṣṇubhavanaṃ divyairbhogaissamāśritāḥ| \ T75
%% Above 4 lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
jñeyaṃ viṣṇupurādūrdhvaṃ divyaṃ śivapuraṃ mahat|
tadbhogāsthānamatulaṃ karmaratātmanām|| 5.23||
% karmayogaratātmanām| \ T75
aprameyaguṇairdivyairvimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|
% sārvagāmikaiḥ| \ T75
asaṃkhyaistatpuraṃ vyāptaṃ sarvaprāṇyupakārakaiḥ|| 5.24||
sahasrabhaumavistīrṇaḥ sūryakoṭisamaprabhaḥ|
% sahasrabhaumavistīrṇaiḥ sūryakoṭisamaprabhaiḥ| \ T75
rudraloka iti proktaścāśeṣaguṇasaṃyuta|| 5.25||
% rudralokamiva proktamaśeṣaguṇasaṃyutam| \ T75
sarveṣāṃ śivabhaktānāṃ tatparaṃ parikīrtitam|
% tatpuraṃ parikīrtitam| \ T75
rudrakṣetramṛtānāñ ca jaṅgamasthāvarātmanām|| 5.26||
% rudrakṣetremṛtānāṃ ca \ T75
apyekadivasaṃ bhaktyā yaḥ pūjayati śaṅkaram|
% apyekadevasaṃbhaktyā \ T75
so'pi yāti śivasthānaṃ kiṃ punarbahuśo'rcayeta|| 5.27||
% so'pi yāti paraṃ sthānaṃ  . . . . . rcanāt| \ T75
tasmādīśe sadā bhaktiṃ bhāvayedātmanātmani|
%% Tp.56
tanmāhātmyavicāreṇa bhavarogavirāgataḥ|| 5.28||
% tasmādātmavicāreṇa bhavadoṣavirāgataḥ| \ T75
evaṃ śivānubhāvena nikṛṣṭenāpi karmaṇā |
naraiḥ sthānāny avāpyante deśe bhāvānurūpataḥ || 5.29||
% karmabhāvānurūpataḥ| \ T75
ity etad aparaṃ proktaṃ śrīmacchivapuraṃ mahat|
dehināṃ karmaniṣṭhānāṃ punarāvartakaṃ smṛtam|| 5.30||
%% p.221
ūrdhvaṃ śivapurāj jñeyaṃ sthānatrayam anuttamam|
nityaṃ paraṃ viśuddhañ ca skandomāśaṅkarātmakam || 5.31||
skandaṃ śaktidharaṃ śāntaṃ ṣaṇmukhaṃ śikhivāhanam|
taptacāmīkaraprakhyaṃ triśikhaṃ bālarūpiṇam || 5.32||
prabhābhir bhāṣitaṃ devaṃ sarvalokānukampakam |
% prabhābhirbhāsitaṃ \ T75
dhyāyamānaḥ prasannātmā guhasthānam avāpnuyāt || 5.33||
% dhyāyansadā prasannātmā \ T75
kanyārūpām umāṃ śāntāṃ sūryakoṭisamaprabhām|
dhyāyamānaḥ sadā bhaktyā devyāḥ sthānam avāpnuyāt|| 5.34||
śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśaṃ jaṭāmakuṭadhāriṇam|
% jaṭāmakuṭaśobhitam| \ T75
tryakṣaṃ caturbhujaṃ śāntam akṣamālādharaṃ haram|| 5.35||
% akṣamūlādharaṃ haram| \ T75
varadābhayahastañca triśūlāsaktapāṇikam|
% triśūlāsaktapāṇinam| \ T75
dhyāyamānaḥ śivaṃ nityaṃ śivasthānam avāpnuyāt|| 5.36||
% tatsāyujyam avāpnuyāt| \ T75
ye samprāptāḥ śivasthānaṃ jñānayogaratā narāḥ|
% ye saṃprāptāḥ paraṃ sthānaṃ \ T75
na teṣāṃ punarāvṛttir ghore saṃsārasāgare|| 5.39||
sarvajñāḥ sarvagāḥ śuddhāḥ paripūrṇā maheśvarāḥ |
%% Tp.57
śivatulyabalāḥ siddhāḥ paraṃ śivapuraṃ gatāḥ || 5.40||
% śivatulyabalopetāḥ \ T75
yogaṃ pravedayiṣyāmi pṛthagadhyāyasammitam|
% yogaṃ prabodhayiṣyāmi pṛthagadhyāyasaṃsthitam| \ T75
upariṣṭācca lokānāṃ svarūpaṃ cāpyanukramāt|| 5.41||
tatrāṣṭaguṇam aiśvaryaṃ pārthivaṃ piśitāśinām |
tatsāyujyagatānāñ ca narāṇāṃ tatsamaṃ smṛtam|| 5.42||
rakṣas su ṣoḍaśakalaṃ pārthivāñ ca taddvidhā|
% rākṣasaṃ ṣoḍaśaguṇaṃ pārthivaṃ cāpi tadvidhā| \ T75
etacca niravaśeṣaṃ yakṣeṣv anyac ca taijasam|| 5.43||
% etā naraviśeṣaṃ hi yakṣeṣvanyasya taijasam| \ T75
gandharvāṇañca vāyavyaṃ yākṣañca sakalaṃ smṛtam|
% yakṣāṇāṃ sakalaṃ smṛtam| \ T75
pāñcabhautikamindrasya catvāriṃśadguṇaṃ mahat|| 5.44||
somasya mānasaṃ divyaṃ yaccādhaḥ pāñcabhautikam|
% somapānarasaṃ divyaṃ yaccādaṃ \ T75
saumyaṃ prājāpatisthānam ahaṃkāraguṇānvitam|| 5.45||
% saumyātprajāpatiṃ nāma ahaṃkāraguṇādhikam| \ T75
catuṣṣaṣṭiguṇaṃ brāhmaṃ bauddhamaiśvaryamuttamam|
% catuṣṣaṣṭiguṇaṃ brāhmyaṃ bhodhyamaiśvaryamuttamam| \ T75
viṣṇoḥ pradhānikaṃ sūkṣmam aiśvaryam uttamam|| 5.46||
% viṣoḥ pradāni sūkṣmamaiśvaraṃ brahmaṇaḥ param| \ T75
śrīmacchivapure nityamaiśvaryaṃ sārvakāmikam|
% śrīmacchivapuraṃ divyamaiśvaryaṃ sarvagāmikam| \ T75
śivena śivabhaktānāṃ kalpitaṃ vaiṣṇavāt param|| 5.47||
skandasya bhagavatyāśca vaiṣṇavāt paramaṃ mahat|
sūkṣmamavyaktikaṃ divyamaiśvaryaṃ sārvakāmikam|| 5.48||
%% Above verse 48 is missing in T75.
%% p.222
anantaguṇamaiśvaryaṃ śivasyātmagataṃ mahat|
ādimadhyāntarahitaṃ viśuddhaṃ tatvalakṣaṇam|| 5.49||
sarvābhibhāṣakaṃ sūkṣmamanupamyaṃ parātparam|
% sarvābhibhāvakaṃ sūkṣmamanupamyam anāmayam| \ T75
susampūrṇaṃ jagaddhetuḥ paśupāśavimokṣaṇam|| 5.50||
% susampūrṇaṃ jagaddhetuṃ \ T75
yo yāṃ saṃsthānamanuprāptastasya bhogāstadātmakāḥ|
% etatsthānamanuproktaṃ tasya bhogāstadātmakāḥ| \ T75
aiśvaryaṃ tatpramāṇañca bhavedīśaprasādataḥ|| 5.51||
% aiśvaryaṃ tatsamānaṃ ca \ T75
%% Tp.58
tārārūpavimānānābhimā dṛśyanti koṭayaḥ|
% tārārūpā vimānānāṃ dṛśyante saptakoṭayaḥ| \ T75
aṣṭāviṃśatirevordhvaṃ sudīptāḥ suhṛdātmanām|| 5.52||
% saṃdīptāssukṛtātmanām| \ T75
ye kurvanti namaskāramīśvarāya kvacit kvacit|
samparkāt kautukāllobhāt tadvimānaṃ labhanti te|| 5.53||
% tadvimānaṃ vahanti te| \ T75
nāmasaṅkīrtanādvāpi prasaṅgena śivasya yaḥ|
% nāmasaṃkīrtanaṃ vāpi prasaṅgena śivasya ca| \ T75
kuryādvāpi namaskrāraṃ tattasyāpi phalaṃ labhet|| 5.54||
% kuryādvā taṃ namaskāraṃ na tasya viphalaṃ bhavet| \ T75
ityetā gatayaḥ proktā mahatyaḥ śivakarmaṇām|
% ityevaṃ gatayaḥ \ T75
atyalpālpatareṇāpi puṃsāmīśānabhāvataḥ|| 5.55||

\ colo
iti śivadharmottare śivadharmagatirnāma pañcamo'dhyāyaḥ|
% śivasaṃgatyaḥ pañcamodhyāyaḥ| \ T75
% śrīsāṃbasadāśivārparabrahmaṇe namaḥ| \ T75

%% Chapter 6
%% Tp.59
%% p.223

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivadharmottare ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
% śrīḥ \ T75
% atha ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ| \ T75
athādhaḥ patanāt puṃsāmadharmaḥ parikīrtitaḥ|
narakādau mahāghore pāpānāṃ yātanāḥ smṛtāḥ|| 6.1||
% narakābdau mahāghore patanātpāpamucyate| \ T75
adharmabhedā vijñeyāścittavṛttiprabhedataḥ|
sthūlāḥ sūkṣmāḥ susūkṣmāśca koṭibhedairanekadhā|| 6.2||
% sthūlasūkṣmāsusūkṣmāśca \ T75
tatra ye pāpanicayāḥ sthūlā narakahetavaḥ|
te samāsena kathyante manovākkāyasādhanāḥ|| 6.3||
% te samāsena kathyante pā(vā)jmanaḥ kāyasādhanam| \ T75
parastrīparasaṅkalpaścetaso'niṣṭacintanam|
% @ścetanāniṣṭhacintanam| \ T75
akāvyārbhiniveśaśca caturdhā karma mānasam|| 6.4||
% akāryābhiniveśaśca \ T75
anibaddhapralāpitvam asatyañca apriyañca yat|
% anibandhapralāpitvam \ T75
parāpavādaḥ paiśunyaṃ caturdhā karma vācikam|| 6.5||
% parāpavādapaiśunyaṃ \ T75
abhakṣyabhakṣaṇaṃ hiṃsā mithyākāmanivedanam|
% mithyākāmanyasevanam| \ T75
parasvānāmupādānaṃ caturdhā karma kāyikam|| 6.6||
ityetad dvādaśavidhaṃ karma proktaṃ trisādhanam|
% ityevaṃ trividhaṃ proktaṃ karmatritayanādinam| \ T75
asya bhedān punarvakṣye yeṣāṃ phalamanuttaram|| 6.7||
% yeṣāṃ phalamanantakam| \ T75
ye dviṣanti mahādevaṃ saṃsārārṇavatāranam|
sumahāpātakopetāste yānti narakāgniṣu || 6.8||
% sumahatpātakopetāste yānti narakāntikam| \ T75
dūṣayanti śivajñānaṃ ye sarvārthaprasādhakam |
% dūṣayantaśśivajñānaṃ ye sarvārthaprasādhanam| \ T75
sumahat pātakaṃ teṣāṃ nirayārṇavagāminām|| 6.9||
%% Tp.60
ye śivajñānavaktāraṃ vidviṣanti gurunnarāḥ|
% śivajñānasya vaktāraṃ nindanti ca guruṃ narāḥ| \ T75
sumahāpātakopetāste yānti narakārṇavam|| 6.10||
% sumahatpātakopetāste yānti nirayārṇavam| \ T75
śivanindā gurunindā śivajñānasya dūṣaṇam|
% śivanindā gurornindā \ T75
devadravyāpaharaṇaṃ gurudravyavināśanam|| 6.11||
% devadravyāpahāriṇaṃ \ T75
haranti ye ca sammuḍhāḥ śivajñānasya pustakam|
% haranti yena saṃmūḍhāśśivajñānasya pustakam| \ T75
sumahāpātakānyāhuranantāni phalāni ca|| 6.12||
% sumahatpātakopetā anantāni phalāni ṣaṭ| \ T75
nābhinandanti ye dṛṣṭvā śivapūjāṃ prakalpitām|
na namantyarcitaṃ dṛṣṭvā pūjitaṃ na stuvanti ca|| 6.13||
yatheṣṭaceṣṭā niḥśaṅkāḥ santiṣṭhanti ramanti ca|
upacāravinirmuktāḥ śivāgnigurusannidhau|| 6.14||
%% p.224
sthānasaṃskārapūjāñca ye na kurvanti parvasu|
% sthānasaṃsārapū . . ñca \ T75
śivavidyāgurūṇāñca karmayogavyavasthitāḥ|| 6.15||
% karmayogepyavasthitāḥ| \ T75
ye tyajanti śivācāraṃ śivabhaktān dviṣanti ca|
śivanindāsamānyeva mahānti pātakāni hi|| 6.16||
% śivanindāsamāhyete mahāntaḥ pātakottamāḥ| \ T75
asampūjya śivajñānaṃ ye'dhīyante likhanti|
% ye dhiyante likhanti ca| \ T75
anyāyataḥ prayacchanti śṛṇvantyuccārayanti ca|| 6.17||
% anyāyataśca pṛcchanti \ T75
vikrīyanti ca lobhena kujñānaniyamena ca|
% kuñjānaḥ niyamena ca| \ T75
asaṃskṛtapradeśeṣu yatheṣṭaṃ sthāpayanti ca|| 6.18||
% asaṃskatapradeśeṣu \ T75
śivajñānakathākṣepaṃ yaḥ kṛtvā'nyat prabhāṣate|
% śivajñānarathākṣepaṃ \ T75
nādhīyīta samarthaśca yaḥ pramādaṃ karoti ca|| 6.19||
% sādhīyante samarthassan \ T75
%% Tp.61
aśuciścāśucau sthāne yaḥ pravakti śṛṇoti ca|
% acintāścāśucisthāne yaśśṛṇoti pravarti ca| \ T75
iti sarvaṃ samāsena jñānanindāsamaṃ smṛtam|| 6.20||
gurupūjām akṛtvyaiva yaḥ śāstraṃ śrotumicchati|
na karoti ca śuśrūṣām ājñāṃ bhaktiśca bhāvataḥ|| 6.21||
% ājñāṃ bhaktiṃ ca bhāvataḥ| \ T75
nābhinandati tadvākyam uttarañca prayacchati|
% nābhinandanti \ T75
gurukarmaṇi śāṭhyañca tadupekṣāṃ karoti ca|| 6.22||
guruṃ śāntam aśaktaṃ vā videśaprasthitantathā|
% gurumāptamaśaktaṃ vā \ T75
aribhiḥ paribhūtaṃ vā yaḥ santyajati pāpakṛt|| 6.23||
tadbhāryāputramitreṣu yaścāvajñāṃ karoti ca|
ityetat pātakaṃ jñeyaṃ gurunindāsamaṃ mahat|| 6.24||
% gurunindāsamaṃ bhavet| \ T75
brahmaghnaśca surāpaśca steyī ca gurutalpagaḥ|
mahāpātakinastvete tatsaṃsargī ca pañcamaḥ|| 6.25||
% mahāpātakasatsyete tatsaṃyogī ca pañcamaḥ| \ T75
krodhād dveṣād bhayāllobhād brāhmaṇasya vadecca yaḥ|
% krodhāllobhādbhayādveṣāt \ T75
marmāntikaṃ mahādoṣaṃ brahmaghnaḥ sa prakīrtitaḥ|| 6.26||
% mamāntikaṃ mahādoṣaṃ brahmahā \ T75
brāhmaṇaṃ yaḥ samāhūya yācyamānaṃ sakiñcanam|
% yācamānamakiṃcanam| \ T75
paścānnāstīti ca brūyāt sa vai brahmaṇaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 6.27||
% brahmahatyā sa ca smṛtaḥ| \ T75
yaśca vidyābhimānena udvejayati sa dvijam|
% yaścāvi(pi)dyājamānena yastarjayati dvijam| \ T75
udāsīnaṃ sabhāmadhye brahmahā sa prakīrtitaḥ|| 6.28||
mithyā guṇaiḥ svamātmānaṃ nayatyutkarṣaṇaṃ balāt|
% mithyāguṇaiḥ \ T75
gurūṇāñca viruddho yaḥ sa vai brahmaṇaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 6.29||
% gurūṇāṃ ca viruddhassyāt brahmātya . sa ca smṛtaḥ| \ T75
%% Tp.62
kṣutṛṭsantaptadehānāṃ dvijānāṃ bhoktumicchatām|
% kṣuttṛṣṇātaptadehānāṃ \ T75
yaḥ samācarate vighnaṃ tamāhurbrahmaghātakam|| 6.30||
%% p.225
piśunaḥ sarvalokānāṃ randhrānveṣaṇatatparaḥ|
udvegajananaḥ krūraḥ sa vai brahmaṇaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 6.31||
% udvegajanakaḥ krūraḥ sa ca vai brahmaghātakaḥ| \ T75
gavāṃ tṛṣābhibhūtānāṃ jalārthamupasarpatām|
% gacchantīnāṃ jalāśayam| \ T75
yaḥ samācarate vighnaṃ tamāhurbrahmaghātakam|| 6.32||
paradoṣaṃ parijñāya nṛpakarṇe japetu yaḥ|
% paradoṣān parijñāya nṛpakarṇe japeta yāḥ| \ T75
pāpīyān piśunaḥ kṣudraḥ sarvai brahmahaṇaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 6.33||
% pāpīyān piśunaḥ kṣudro brahmātparicati smṛtaḥ| \ T75
%% Above two lines of T75 occurs in between verse 30 and 31 of this edition.
devadvijagatāṃ bhūmiṃ parvabhuktāṃ harettu yaḥ|
% pūrvadattāṃ hareta yaḥ| \ T75
praṇaṣṭāmapi kālena tamāhurbrahmaghātakam|| 6.34||
% pranaṣṭhāmapi kālena \ T75
dvijavṛtyāpaharaṇe nyāyataḥ samupārjatam|
% dvijavittāpaharaṇaṃ nyāyena samupārjitam| \ T75
brahmahatyāsamaṃ jñeyaṃ pātakaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 6.35||
adhīsa yaḥ śivajñānaṃ parityajati mūḍhadhīḥ|
% adhitsa yaśśivajñānaṃ \ T75
surāpānasamaṃ jñeyaṃ tasya pātakamulvaṇam|| 6.36||
% surāpānasamaṃ jñeyaṃ tatpātakamuttamam| \ T75
agnihotraparityāgī pañcayajñīyakarmaṇām|
% agnihotraparityāgaḥ pañcayajñādhikarmaṇām| \ T75
mātāpitṛparityāgī kūṭasākṣī sukṛdvadhaḥ|| 6.37||
% mātāpitroḥ parityāgaḥ kūṭasākṣyaṃ suhṛdvadhaḥ| \ T75
apriyaḥ śivabhaktānām abhakṣyasya ca bhakṣaṇaḥ|
% apriyaṃ śivabhaktānām abhakṣyasya ca bhakṣaṇam| \ T75
vane niraparādhānāṃ prāṇināñca nipātanam|| 6.38||
% prāṇināṃ copaghātakam| \ T75
gavālaye vane cāgniṃ pure grāme ca dīpayet|
% gavāṃ mārge vane cāgniṃ puraṃ grāmaṃ pradīpayet| \ T75
iti pāpāni ghorāṇi surāpānasamāni ca|| 6.39||
% surāpānasamāni ti[samānīti]| \ T75
dīnasarvasvaharaṇaṃ narastrīgajavājinām|
gobhūratnatratānāmauṣadhīnāṃ rasasya ca|| 6.40||
% gobhūmiratnaraupyāṇāmoṣadhīnāṃ rasasya ca| \ T75
candanāgurukarpūrakastūrīpaṭavāsasām|
% candanāgurukastūrīkarpūrapaṭṭavāsasām| \ T75
hastanyāsāpaharaṇaṃ rakmasteyasamaṃ smṛtam|| 6.41||
% vāsasyānāvaharaṇaṃ rakmasteyasamasmṛtaḥ| \ T75
kanyānāṃ varayogyānāmadānaṃ sadṛśe vare|
putramitrakalatreṣu gamanaṃ bhaginīṣu ca|| 6.42||
kumārīsāhasaṃ ghoram antyajastrīniṣevanam|
svavarṇāyāñca gamanaṃ gurutalpasamaṃ smṛtam|| 6.43||
% svavarṇāyāśca gamanaṃ \ T75
mahāpātakatulyāni pāpānyuktāni tāni ca|
% pāpānyuktāni yāni tu| \ T75
tāni pātakasaṃjñāni tadbhūtānyupapātakam|| 6.44||
% tadūnānyupapātakam| \ T75
dvijāyārthaṃ pratijñāya na prayacchati yaḥ punaḥ|
na ca smārayate viprastulyaṃ tadupapātakam|| 6.45||
% na ca smarayate vipraḥ tulyaṃ tadupapātakaiḥ| \ T75
dvijadravyāpaharaṇaṃ maryādāyā vyatikramaḥ|
% dvijadravyāpaharaṇiaḥ ma . . . dāyāvyatikramaḥ| \ T75
atimāno'tikopaśca dambhikatvaṃ kṛtaghnatā|| 6.46||
% atimānāti kaupe ca ḍāṃbhīkatvaṃ \ T75
%% p.226
atyantaviṣayāsaktiḥ kārpaṇyaṃ śāṭhyamatsaram|
% atyantaviṣayāsaktaḥ kārpaṇyaṃ śāṭhyamatsare| \ T75
paradārābhigamanaṃ sādhvīkanyāpradūṣaṇam|| 6.47||
% sādhukanyābhidūṣaṇam| \ T75
parivittiḥ parivettā yayā ca parividyate|
% yayā ca parivedyate| \ T75
tayordānañca kanyāyāstayoreva ca yācanam|| 6.48||
putramitrakalatrāṇām adoṣe svāminastathā|
% prabhave svāminastathā| \ T75
sahāyānāṃ parityāgaḥ sādhubandhutapasvinām|| 6.49||
% kāryāṇāñca parityāgaḥ svāmibandhutapasvinām| \ T75
%% Tp.64
gavāṃ kṣatriyavaiśyānāṃ strīśūdrāṇāṃ ca ghātane|
% strīśūdrāṇāṃ vighātakam| \ T75
śivāśramatarūpāñ ca puṣpāśamavināśanam|| 6.50||
% śivāśramatarūṇāñca puṣparāmāvināśanam| \ T75
yaḥ pīḍamāśramasthānām ācaredalpikāmapi|
% yaḥ . . dāmāśramasthānām ācaredalpikāmapi| \ T75
tadbhṛtyaparivargasya paśudhānyadhanasya ca|| 6.51||
% tadbhṛtyā parivārasya \ T75
kupyadhānyapaśusteyam ayācyānāñca yācatam|
% laupyadhenupaśurde(rje)yā mayā jñānaṃ ca yājanaḥ| \ T75
yajñārāmataḍāgānāṃ dārāpatyasya vikrayaḥ|| 6.52||
tīrthayātropavāsānāṃ vratāyatanakarmaṇām|
strīdhanānyupajīvanti strībhiratyantanirjitāḥ|| 6.53||
% strībhiratyantakīrtitāḥ| \ T75
arakṣaṇañca nārīṇāṃ madyapastrīniṣevanam|
% madhyamastrīniṣevaṇam| \ T75
ṛṇānāmapradānañca dhānyavṛddhyupasevanam|| 6.54||
% ṛṣīṇāmapradānaṃ ca \ T75
ninditācca dhanādānamavaśyānāñca vikrayaḥ|
% ninditānaṃdanādānamapaṇyānāṃ ca vikrayam| \ T75
viṣamāraṇamantrāṇāṃ prayoge mūlakarmaṇām|| 6.55||
% viṣamāraṇayantrāṇāṃ \ T75
uccāṭanābhicāraśca garavidveṣaṇakriyā|
jvihākāmopabhogārthaṃ yasyārambhaḥ svakarmasu|| 6.56||
% yadyārambhasya karmasu| \ T75
mūlyenādhyāpayedyastu mūlyenāpyadhīyate ca yaḥ|
vrātyatā vratasantyāgaḥ sarvakarmaniṣevaṇam|| 6.57||
% sarvāhāraniṣevaṇam| \ T75
asacchāstrābhigamanaṃ śuṣkatarkāvalambanam|
devāgnisādhusādhvīnāṃ nindā gobrāhmaṇasya ca|| 6.58||
% devāgnigurusādhvīnā \ T75
pratyakṣaṃ vā parokṣaṃ vā rājñāṃ maṇḍalināmapi|
kutsnaṃ pitṛdevejyāsvakarmatyāginaśca ye|| 6.59||
% utpannapitṛdevejyāsvakarmatyāgināṃ tathā| \ T75
%% Tp.65
% duśśīlā nāstikāḥ pāpā sadā sacchūnyavādinaḥ| \ T75
% duśśīlā nāstikā pāpāḥ sadasacchūnyavādinaḥ| \ NK28
% sarvakāle divācāpsu viyonau paśuyoniṣu| \ T75
% paśuyonuṣu \ ed
% rajasvalāsu yonau ca maithunaṃ yassamācaret| \ T75
% strīmitraputrasamprīterāśāyāścedakāśca ye| \ T75
%% Above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
% at least NK28 has those [Kengo 20211203]
janasyāpriyavaktāraḥ krūrāḥ samayabhedinaḥ|
% jananyāpriyavaktāraḥ krūrassamayabhedinaḥ| \ T75
bhettā taḍāgavaprāṇāṃ saṃkramāṇāṃ rathasya ca|| 6.60||
ekapaṅktisthitānāñca pākabhedaṃ karoti yaḥ|
ityetaiḥ strīnarāḥ pāpair upapātakinaḥ smṛtāḥ|| 6.61||
%% Above 3 lines 60cd-61cd are missing in T75.
yuktās tadbhūtakiaḥ kṣadaiḥ pāpaiḥ pāpakarāḥ smṛtāḥ|
% yuktāstadūnakaiḥ kṣudraiḥ pāpaiḥ pāpanarāssmṛtāḥ| \ T75
ye gobrāhmaṇakanyānāṃ svāmimitratapasvinām|| 6.62||
% yo gobrāhmaṇakanyānāṃ \ T75
%% p.227
antaraṃ yāntyakāryeṣu smṛtā nārakā narāḥ|
% antarā yānti kāryeṣu te smṛtā narakāssmṛtāḥ| \ T75
parastriyābhitaptasya ye paraduvyasūcakāḥ|| 6.63||
% paradravyahitavyante ye paradravyasūcikāḥ| \ T75
paravyāpāraniratāḥ parastrī paradūṣakāḥ|
% dravyāpahāraniratāḥ \ T75
dvijāya duḥkhaṃ kuryāt prahāramugdiracca yaḥ|| 6.64||
% duḥkhaṃ dvijānāṃ yaḥ kuryāt praharedūrdhvato hi yaḥ| \ T75
yaḥ sevate dvijaḥ śūdraṃ surāmāghrāti kāmataḥ|
% yassevate dvijāśśūdraṃ surāṃca pāti kāmataḥ| \ T75
%% surāṃcā pāti \ ed
ye pāpābhiratāḥ krūrāḥ ye ca hiṃsāpriyā narāḥ|| 6.65||
% ye pi hiṃsāpriyā narāḥ| \ T75
pravyarthāṃ ye ca kurvanti dānayajñādikāṃ kriyām|
% bhṛ(vṛ)tyarthaṃ ye ca kurvante dānayajñādikā kriyāḥ| \ T75
goṣṭhāgnijalarathyāsu tarucchāyānageṣu ca|| 6.66||
tyajanti ye purīṣādīn ārāmāyataneṣu ca|
% ye tyajanti purīṣādyān \ T75
madyamāṃsaratā nityaṃ gītavādyaratā narāḥ|| 6.67||
% madyapānaratā nityaṃ \ T75
kelikīlābhujaṅgāśca randhrānveṣaṇatatparāḥ|
% kelīśilābhujaṅgāśca \ T75
vaṃśeṣṭakāśilākāṣṭhai sva(kha)bhraiḥ śaṅkubhireva vā|| 6.68||
% vaṃśeṣṭakāśilākāṭhairaśṛṅgaiśśaṅkubhireva ca| \ T75
ye mārgamuparundhanti parasminno haranti ca|
% parasīmaṃ haranti ca| \ T75
%% Tp.66
kūṭaśāsanakartāraḥ kuṭakarmakriyāratāḥ|| 6.69||
% kuṭaśālanakartāraḥ kuṭakarmaratā narāḥ| \ T75
kūṭayuddhāḥ kuśāstrāṇi kūṭasaṃvyavahāriṇaḥ|
% kūṭayuddhāśca vastrāṇi \ T75
dhanuṣaḥ śalyaśastrāṇāṃ yaḥ kartā yaśca vikrayī|| 6.70||
% dhanuṣāṃ śalyaśastrāṇāṃ yaḥ kartā yacca vikriyā| \ T75
nirdayo'tīva nṛtyeṣu paśūnāṃ damakāśca ye|
% nirdayotivaṣovyeṣu paśūnāṃ damakaiśca ye| \ T75
mithyā pravadato vācamākarṇayati yaḥ śaniaḥ|| 6.71||
% mithyāpravadato(lo)pāśca mākarṇayati yaśaśanaiḥ| \ T75
svāmimitragurudrohī māyāvī capalaḥ śathaḥ|
% māyāvī ca paraśśathaḥ| \ T75
ye bhāryāputramitrāṇi bālavṛddhakṛśāturān|| 6.72||
bhṛtyān atithibandhūśca tyaktvā'śnanti bubhukṣitān|
% bhṛtyān atithibandhūnśca tyaktvā śāntibubhukṣitān| \ T75
yaḥ svayaṃ mṛṣṭamaśnāti viprāyānyat prayacchati|| 6.73||
vṛthāpākaḥ sa vijñeyo brahmavādiṣu garhitaḥ|
% vṛthāpākī sa vijñeyo \ T75
niyamān svayamadāya ye tyajanti jitendriyāḥ|| 6.74||
pravakṣyā(vrajyā) vasitā ye ca rahasyānāñca bhedakāḥ|
% pravṛjyārasikā ye ca \ T75
ye tāḍayanti gāścaiva trāsayatni muhurmuhuḥ|| 6.75||
% ye lobhayanti gāścaiva śivaṃ te ca muhurmuhuḥ| \ T75
durbalān na ca puṣṇanti praṇaṣṭān nānviṣanti ca|
% durbalānyeva puṣṇanti praṇaṣṭāṃśca dviṣanti ca| \ T75
pīḍayantyatibhāreṇa sakṣatān vāhayanti ca|| 6.76||
% asakṛdvāhayanti ca| \ T75
sārddhayāmācca parata abhukte ye ca bhuñjate|
% sārthayāmācca varatāḥ saṃyukto yena bhuñjate| \ T75
ye bhagnakṣatarogārtān gorūpāṃśca kṣudhāturān|| 6.77||
% ye bhagnānakṣirogārthaṃ tān svagopān kṣudhāturān| \ T75
na pālayanti te goghnā nārakāḥ pāpinaḥ smṛtāḥ|
% na pālayanti yā?naste goghnā nārakā smṛtāḥ| \ T75
vṛṣaṇāṃ vṛṣaṇau ye ca pāpiṣṭhā gālayanti ca|| 6.78||
% vṛṣāṇaṃ vṛṣaṇāya ca pāpiṣṭhā nāśayanti ca| \ T75
%% p.228
vāhayanti ca gāṃ vandhyāṃ mahārārakiṇo narāḥ|
% vāhayanti ca gāṃ vandyāmahānārakiṇo narāḥ| \ T75
%% Tp.67
āśāvāsamanuprāptān kṣuttṛṣṇāśramapīḍitān|| 6.79||
% adṛ(dva)śa . . . samanuprāptān kṣutṛṣṇāśramakarśitān| \ T75
ye'tirthāścāvamanyante te vai nirayagāminaḥ|
% yetithīnavamanyante te vai \ T75
anāthaṃ vikalaṃ dīnaṃ bālavṛddhākṛśāturān|| 6.80||
% anāthānvikalān dīnān \ T75
nānukampanti ye mūḍhāste yānti nirayārṇavam|
ajāviko māhiṣakaḥ sāmudrī vṛṣalīpatiḥ|| 6.81||
% māhiṣīkassāmudro vṛṣalīpatiḥ| \ T75
śūdaviṭkṣatravṛttiśca nārakī syād dvijādhamaḥ|
% śūdraviṭkṣatravṛttiśca nārakīsyādvijottamaḥ| \ T75
śilpinaḥ kārukā vaśyā hemakārā nṛpādhvajā|| 6.82||
% śilpinaḥ kāravo vaidyā hemakāranṛpadhvajāḥ| \ T75
bhṛtakāḥ śāṭhyasaṃyuktāstathāntyā nārakāḥ smṛtāḥ|
% bhūtakāśśāṭhyasaṃyuktāste narā narakāssmṛtāḥ| \ T75
yaścocitamatikramya svacchāyā bāhyektaram|| 6.83||
% yaścocitamanutkṛtya svecchayaiva haretkaram| \ T75
narakeṣu sa pacyeta yaśca daṇḍarucirnṛpaḥ|
% daṇḍarucī nṛpaḥ| \ T75
utkocikairadhikṛtaistaskaraiśca prapīḍyate|| 6.84||
% utkośakairadhikṛtaistaskaraiśca \ T75
yasya rājñaḥ prajā rāṣṭre pacyate narakeṣu saḥ|
ye dvijāḥ pratigṛhṇānti nṛpasyānyāyavartinaḥ|| 6.85||
% nṛpasyānyāyavartinaḥ| \ T75
prayānti te'pi ghoreṣu narakeṣu na saṃśayaḥ|
pāradārikacaurāṇāṃ yatpāpaṃ pārthivasya tat|| 6.86||
% paradārikacorāṇāṃ \ T75
bhavedarakṣataḥ sarvaṃ ghoraṃ tasya pratigrahāt|
% bhavedarakṣatastasya pāpāyaiva pratigrahāḥ| \ T75
acauraṃ cauravat paśyeccaurān vā'caurarūpiṇaḥ|| 6.87||
% acoraṃ coravatpaśye coraṃ vā corarūpiṇam| \ T75
avicarya nṛpastasmād ghātayannarakaṃ vrajet|
% avivārya nṛpastasmāt \ T75
ghṛtatailānnapānāni madhumāṃsasurāsavam|| 6.88||
% madhumāṃsasurāsavaḥ| \ T75
guḍekṣukṣīraśākāni dadhimūlaphalāni ca|
% gavekṣukṣīraśākāni dadhimūlaphalāni ca| \ T75
%% Tp.68
tṛṇakāṣṭhapatrapuṣpamauṣadhaṃ kāṃsyabhājanam|| 6.89||
% tṛṇakāṣṭhaṃ puṣpavastrmauṣadhāsavabhājanam| \ T75
upānachatraśakaṭā yetayetmāsanaṃ gṛham|
% upānachatraśakaṭamāsanaṃ śayanaṃ mṛduḥ| \ T75
tāmrasīsatrapuktāṃsya śaṅkhādyañca jalodbhavam|| 6.90||
% tāmrasīsaṃ trapūkāṃsyaṃ \ T75
vārkṣyaṃ vā vaiṇavādyaṃ vā gṛheṣu puṣkarāṇi ca|
% vārkṣaṃ vā vaiṇavaṃ vādyaṃ grahopakaraṇāni ca| \ T75
ūrṇākarpāsakauśeyabhaṅgapaṭṭodbhavāni ca|| 6.91||
% vaurṇa kārpāsa kauśeya bhaṇṭapaṭṭodbhavāni ca| \ T75
sthūlasūkṣmāṇi vastrāṇi ye lobhena haranti ca|
evamādīni cānyāni dravyāṇi vividhāni ca|| 6.92||
%% Above line 92ab is missing in T75.
narakeṣu dhruvaṃ gacched apahṛtyālpakāny api|
% apahṛtya svalpakāni ca| \ T75
yadvā tadvā paradravyamapi sarṣapamātrakam|| 6.93||
apahṛtya naro yāti naraknnātra saṃśayaḥ|
evamādyair naraḥ pāpair vyākrāntaiḥ samanantaram|| 6.94||
% pāpaiḥ utkrāntaissamanantaram| \ T75
%% p.229
śrarīraṃ yātanārthīyaṃ pūrvākāramavāpnuyāt|
% śarīraṃ yātanātmīyaṃ \ T75
yamalokaṃ vrajaṃstena śarīreṇa yamājñayā|| 6.95||
% śarīreṇa vrajantyete \ T75
yamadūtair mahāghorair nīyamānaḥ suduḥkhitaḥ|
% nīyamānāssuduḥkhitāḥ| \ T75
devamānuṣatiryāṇām adharmaniratātmanām|| 6.96||
% devatiryaṅmanuṣyāṇāmadharmaniyatātmanām| \ T75
dharmarājaḥ smṛtaḥ śāstā sughorair vividhair vadhaiḥ |
% dharmarājā smṛtaśśāstā sughorairvividhairvidhaiḥ| \ T75
vinayācārayuktānāṃ pramodaskhalitātmanām|| 6.97||
% niyamācārayuktānāṃ pramādātskhalitātmanām| \ T75
prāyaścittair guruḥ śāstā na vadhair iṣyate yamaḥ|
% na yamo vadhayiṣyati| \ T75
pāradārikacaurāṇām anyāyavyavahāriṇām|| 6.98||
% paradārakacorāṇām \ T75
nṛpatiḥ śāsakaḥ proktaḥ pracchannānāñca dharmarāṭ|
tasmāt kṛtasya pāpasya prāyaścittaṃ samācaret|| 6.99||
%% Tp.69
nābhuktasyānyathā nāśaḥ kalpakoṭiśatairapi|
yaḥ karoti svayaṃ karma kārayed vānumodayet|| 6.100||
% kārayeccānumodayet| \ T75
kāyena manasā vācā tasyordhā gotate phalam|
% tasyacādhogatiḥ phalam| \ T75
iti saṃkṣepataḥ proktāḥ pāpabhedāstrisādhanāḥ|| 6.101||
% pāpabhītāstrisādhanāḥ| \ T75
kathyante gatayaścitrā narāṇāṃ pāpakāiṇām|
% narāṇāṃ pāpakarmaṇām| \ T75

\Colo
iti śivadharmottare pāpabhedādhyāyaḥ ṣaṣthaḥ|
% iti śivadharmottare pāpabhedaṃ nāma ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ| \ T75
% śrīsāmbasadāśivāya parabrahmaṇe namaḥ| \ T75

%% Chapter 7

%% p.230
%% Tp.70

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivadharmottare
pāpagatir nāma saptamo'dhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
% śrīḥ|
% atha saptamo'dhyāyaḥ|
atha pāpair ime yānti yamalokaṃ caturvidhaiḥ |
% atha pāpairito yānti yamalokaṃ ca tadvidhaiḥ| \ T75
santrāsajananaṃ ghoraṃ vivaśāḥ sarvadehinaḥ || 7.1||
garbhasthair jāyamānaiś ca bālais taruṇamadhyamaiḥ |
% bālaistaruṇadudhyamaiḥ| \ T75
strīpunnapuṃsakair vṛddhair yātavya sarvajantubhiḥ || 7.2||
% dhyātavyaṃ sarvajantubhiḥ| \ T75
śubhāśubhaphalaṃ tatra dehināṃ pravicāryate |
% śubhāśubhaphalaṃ cātra dehināṃ pravicāryate| \ T75
citraguptādibhiḥ ṣadbhir madhyasthaiḥ sarvadarśibhiḥ || 7.3||
% citraguptādibhissadbhir \ T75
na te'tra prāṇinaḥ santi ye na yānti yamālayam|
% na tatra pāṇinassanti yena yānti yamālayam| \ T75
avaśyaṃ hi kṛtaṃ karma bhoktavyaṃ tadvicāritam || 7.4||
% bhoktavyamavicārataḥ| \ T75
tatra ye śubhakarmāṇaḥ saumyacittā dayānvitāḥ|
% tatra ye śubhakarmāṇassāmyacittā dayānvitāḥ| \ T75
te narā yānti saumyena pathā yamaniketanaṃ || 7.5||
% pathā yānti niketanam| \ T75
yaḥ pradadyād dvijendrāṇam upānatkāṣṭhapāduke |
% yaḥ padadyād dvijendrāṇām \ T75
sa varāśvena mahatā sukhaṃ yānti yamālayam || 7.6||
% sa parāśvena mahatā \ T75
chatradānena gacchanti yathā sābhreṇa dehinaḥ |
% pathā sāndreṇa dehinaḥ| \ T75
divyavastraparīdhānā yānti vastrapradāyinaḥ|| 7.7||
% yānti vastrān pradāya saḥ| \ T75
śibikāśvapradānena tadrathena sukhaṃ vrajet |
% śibikāśyebhadhānenanadṛdhena sukhaṃ vrajet| \ T75
śaiyāśanapradānena svapan yāti ca viśramam|| 7.8||
% śayyāsanapradānena sukhaṃ yānti saviśramāḥ| \ T75
ārāmakartā chāyāsu śītalāsu sukhaṃ bhavet|
% ārāmakartāścāyāsu śītakāsu sukhaṃ vrajet| \ T75
yānti puṣpakayānena puṣpārāmapradāyinaḥ|| 7.9||
% yānti puṣpavimānena \ T75
%% Tp.71
devāyatanakartā ca yatīnāmāśramasya ca|
% devāyatanakartāro \ T75
anāthamaṇḍapānāñ ca krīḍan yāti gṛhottamaiḥ || 7.9||
% anāthamaṇḍapānāṃ ca krīḍamānagrahottamaḥ| \ T75
devāgniguruviprāṇāṃ mātu pituśca pūjakāḥ|
% mātāpitrośca pūjakaḥ| \ T75
pūjyamānā narā yānti kāmikena yathāsukham|| 7.10||
udyotayandiśaḥ sarvā yāti dīpapradāyakaḥ|
% dyotayanto diśassarvāḥ yānti dīpapradāyinaḥ| \ T75
pratiśrayapradānena sukhaṃ yānti gṛhe svayam|| 7.11||
% pratiśrāya pradānena sukhaṃ yānti graheṣvayam| \ T75
sarvakāmasamṛddhena pathā gacchanti gopradāḥ |
% sarvakāmasamṛddhena pathā gacchati gopradāḥ| \ T75
ye 'nnapānāni kurvanti te taptā yānti tatpathā || 7.12||
% ye tṛptā yānti satpathā| \ T75
%% p.231
annauṣadhapradātāraḥ sukhaṃ yānti nirāmayāḥ|
% ārtauṣadhapradātāraḥ \ T75
viśrāmyamānā gacchanti guruśuśrūṣaṇe ratāḥ|| 7.13||
% guruśiśrūṣaṇe ratāḥ| \ T75
pādaśaucapradānena śītalena pathā vrajet|
% pādaśāca pradānena \ T75
hemaratnapradānena yāti durgāṇi nistaran|| 7.14||
% yānti durgāṇi dustaram| \ T75
pādābhyaṅgañca yaḥ kuryādaśvapṛṣṭhena sa vrajet|
% pādābhyāṃ gaccha yaḥ kuryādaśvavṛttena so vrajet| \ T75
ruṣyā(vṛṣā) naḍvahadānena naro yānena gacchati|| 7.15||
% rathāsuduhadānena divyayānena gacchati| \ T75
sarvakāmasamṛddhātmā bhūmidānena gacchati |
% sarvakāmasamṛddhena \ T75
annapānapradānena khādan pibaṃś ca gacchati || 7.16||
% annapānapradānena pibankhādaṃśca gacchati| \ T75
ity evamādibhir dānaiḥ sukhaṃ yānti yamālayam |
% sukhaṃ yānti yamakṣayam| \ T75
svarge ca vipulān bhogān prāpnoti vividhān naraḥ|| 7.17||
sarveṣām eva dānānām annadānaṃ paraṃ smṛtam|
sadyaḥ prītikaran divyaṃ balabuddhivivardhanam|| 7.18||
% sarvaprītikaraṃ divyaṃ balapuṣṭivivardhanam| \ T75
%% Tp.72
nānnadānasamaṃ dānaṃ triṣu lokeṣu vidyate|
annād bhavanti bhūtāni tasmād annam idaṃ jagat|| 7.19||
% annādbhavanti bhūtāni tadabhāve mriyanti ca| \ T75
raktaṃ māṃsaṃ vasā śukraṃ kramād annāt pravardhate|
% raktamāṃsavasāśuklaṃ kramādannātpravardhaye| \ T75
śukrād bhavanti bhūtāni tasmād annam idaṃ jagat || 7.20||
% śuklādbhavanti bhūtāni tasmādannamayaṃ jagat| \ T75
hemaratnāsvanāgendranārīstrak candanādibhiḥ|
% @nārīsrak candanādibhiḥ| \ T75
samastair api samprāptair na ramante bubhukṣitāḥ|| 7.21||
% na ramante cubhukṣitāḥ| \ T75
garbhasthā jāyamānāś ca bālavṛddhāś ca madhyamāḥ|
āhāramabhikāṃkṣanti devadānavatāpasāḥ|| 7.22||
% āhāramabhikāṃkṣante \ T75
kṣudhā hi sarvarogānāṃ vyādhiḥ śreṣṭhatamaḥ smṛtaḥ|
% rogaśśreṣṭhatamassmṛtaḥ| \ T75
tasmānn auṣadhilepena pratīkāraḥ prakīrtitaḥ|| 7.23||
% tasmādauṣadhalepena vratakārāḥ prakīrtitāḥ| \ T75
nāsti kṣudhāsamaṃ duḥkhaṃ nāsti rogaḥ kṣudhāsamaḥ|
nāstyāhārasamaṃ saukhyaṃ nāsti krodhasamo ripuḥ|| 7.24||
ata eva mahat puṇyam annadānaprabhāvataḥ|
% annadānapradānataḥ| \ T75
yataḥ kṣudhāgnisantaptā mriyante sarvadehinaḥ|| 7.25||
% yataḥ kṣudhābhisantaptāḥ \ T75
annadaḥ prāṇadaḥ proktaḥ prāṇadaś cāpi sarvadaḥ|
tasmād annapradānena sarvadānaphalaṃ labhet|| 7.26||
trailokye yāni ratnāni bhogāḥ strīvāhanāni ca|
% triloke yāni ratnāni bhogāḥ sti vāhanāni ca| \ T75
annadānapradaḥ sarvān ihāmutra ca tāṃ labhet || 7.27||
% annadānapradānena ihāmutra ca tallabhet| \ T75
yasyānnapānapuṣṭāṅgaḥ kurute dharmasañcayam |
% kurute puṇyasañcayam| \ T75
annapradātus tasyārdhaṃ kattuś cārdhan na saṃśayaḥ|| 7.28||
% kartuścārdhaṃ na saṃśayaḥ| \ T75
%% p.232
%% Tp.73
dharmārthakāmamokṣāṇāṃ dehaḥ paramasādhanam |
sthitis tasyānnapānābhyām atas tat sarvasādhanam|| 7.29||
annaṃ prajāpatiḥ sākṣād annaṃ viṣṇuḥ śivaḥ svayam|
tasmād annamayaṃ dānaṃ na bhūtan na bhaviṣyati|| 7.30||
% tasmādannasamaṃ dānaṃ \ T75
trayāṇām api lokānām udakaṃ jīvitaṃ smṛtam |
% trayāṇāmevalokānām \ T75
pavitram amṛtaṃ divyaṃ śuddhaṃ sarvarasāśrayam|| 7.31||
% pavitramamṛtaṃ divya śuddhaṃ \ T75
annapānāśvagovastraśaiyyāchatrāsanāni ca|
% @ścatrāsanāni ca| \ T75
pretaloke praśastāni dānānyaṣṭau viśeṣataḥ|| 7.32||
% pretaloke prasthitasya tānyaṣṭau ca viśeṣataḥ| \ T75
evaṃ dānaviśeṣeṇa dharmarājapurannarāḥ |
% dharmarājapuraṃ naraḥ| \ T75
yasmād yānti sukhenaiva tasmād dharmaṃ samācaret || 7.33||
ye punaḥ krūrakarmāṇo narā dānavivarjitāḥ |
% ye punaḥ krūrakarmāṇaḥ pānādānavivarjitāḥ| \ T75
te ghoreṇa pathā yānti dakṣiṇena yamālayam || 7.34 ||
ṣaḍaśītisahasrāṇi yojanānāṃ vyatītya tat|
% yojanānāmatītya vai| \ T75
vaivasvatapuraṃ teyaṃ nānārūpam avasthitam || 7.35||
% vaivasvatapuraṃ jñeya nānārūpaṃ vyavasthitam | \ T75
tatsamīpam ivābhāti nārāṇāṃ śubhakarmaṇām|
% samīpasthamivābhāti narāṇāṃ puṇyakarmaṇām| \ T75
pāpānām atidūrasthaṃ yathā raudreṇa gacchatām|| 7.36||
% pāpīnāmapi dūrasthaṃ \ T75
tīvrakaṇṭakayuktena śarkarānicitena ca |
kṣuradhārānibhaistīvraiḥ pāṣāṇair nicitena ca|| 7.37||
% kṣurābhārānibhaistīvrai pāṣāṇainiśitena ca| \ T75
kacitpaṅkena mahatā durāt tāraiś ca khātakaiḥ |
% kvacitpaṅkena mahatā duruktāraiśca ghātakaiḥ| \ T75
lohasūcīnibhair darbhaiḥ sañchannena pathā kvacit || 7.38||
% lohasūcimukhairdarbhaiḥ sacchannena pathā kvacit| \ T75
%% Tp.74
tataḥ prayānti viṣamaiḥ parvatair vṛkṣasaṃyutaiḥ|
% taṭaprapātaviṣamaiḥ parvatairvṛkṣasaṃkulaiḥ| \ T75
prataptāṅgārayuktena yānti mārgeṇa duḥkhitāḥ || 7.39||
kvacid viṣamagartābhiḥ kvacilloṣṭhaiḥ supicchilaiḥ|
% kvacidviṣamagartaiśca kvacilloṣṭhaiśca piñchalaiḥ| \ T75
sutaptabālukābhiśca tathā tīkṣṇaiśca śaṅkubhiḥ|| 7.40||
anekaśākhāvitatairvyāptaṃ vaṃśa . . ai kvacit|
% anekaśākhāvitatairvyāptavaṃśasakhaiḥ kvacit| \ T75
kaṣṭena tamasā mārgamanālambhena kutracit|| 7.41||
ayaḥsaṅkaṭakaistaptaiḥ kvaciddāvāgninā punaḥ|
% atha śṛṅgāṭakaistaptaiḥ \ T75
kvacittaptaśilābhiśca kvacid vyāpta himena ca|| 7.42||
% kvacidvyāptaṃ himena ca| \ T75
kvacid bālukayā vyāptam ākaṇṭhānna praveśayā|
% ākaṇṭhāntapraveśayā| \ T75
kvaciduṣṇāmbunā vyāptaṃ kvaci . karīṣāgninā|| 7.43||
% kariṣāgninā \ ed
% kvaciduṣṇāṃbhunā vyāpta kvacitkariṣavahninā| \ T75
kvacit siṃhair vṛkair vyāghrair daśaiḥ kīṭaiś ca dāruṇaiḥ|
% kvacit sihmairmṛgairvyāgraiḥ daṃśaiḥ \ T75
kvacinmahājalaukābhiḥ kvaciccājagaraiḥ punaḥ|| 7.44||
% kvacinmahājalūkābhiḥ \ T75
%% p.233
makṣikābhiśca raudrābhiḥ kvacit sarpair viṣolvaṇaiḥ|
% makṣikābhiśca kādrābhiḥ \ T75
mahāgajendrayūthaiśca balonmattaiḥ pramāthibhiḥ|| 7.45||
% mattamātaṅgayuthaiśca [balokīlaiśca dāruṇaiḥ| \ T75
% kvacinmahājalūkādibhiḥ kvaciccājagaraiḥ punaḥ|] \ T75
% balonmattaiḥ pramādibhiḥ| \ 75
panthānamullikhadbhiśca tīkṣṇaśṛṅgairmahāvṛṣaiḥ|
mahāśṛṅgaiśca mahiṣairuṣṭrairmattaiśca khādanaiḥ|| 7.46||
% mahiṣiaruprermattaiśca khādakaiḥ| \ T75
ḍākinībhirvikarālai rākṣasairbhīmarūpibhiḥ|
% ḍākinībhiśca raudrābhirvikarālaiśca rākṣasaiḥ| \ T75
vyādhibhiśca mahāghoraiḥ pīḍyamānā brajanti ca|| 7.47||
% vrajanti ca| \ T75
%% Tp.75
mahādhūlīvimiśreṇa mahācaṇḍena vāyunā|
mahāpāṣāṇavarṣeṇa hanyamānā nirāśrayāḥ|| 7.48||
kvacid vidyutprapātena dāryamāṇā vrajanti ca|
% vāryamāṇā vrajanti ca| \ T75
mahatā bāṇavarṣeṇa bhidyamānāśca sarvataḥ|| 7.49||
% pūryamāṇā rudanti ca| \ T75
patādbhīrvajranirghātairulkāpātaiśca dāruṇaiḥ|
pradīptāṅgāravarṣeṇa dahyamānā naśyanti ca|| 7.50||
% naśanti ca\ ed
mahatā pāṃśuvarṣeṇa ghūryamāṇā rudanti ca|
% pāṃśuvarṣeṇa \ conj; pāśuvarṣeṇa \ ed
%% Above 3 lines 50 ab,cd & 51ab are missing in T75.
mahāmegharavair ghoraiḥ sanyāsyantai muhurmuhuḥ|| 7.51||
% mahāmedhuranairghorairvitrāsyanti \ T75
niśitāyudhavarṣeṇa cūrṇīkṛtāśca sarvataḥ|
% niśitairloṣṭhavarṣaiśca cūrṇyamānāśca sarvaśaḥ| \ T75
mahākṣārāmbudhārābhiḥ sicyamānā dravanti ca|| 7.52||
% sicyamānā vrajanti ca| \ T75
mahāśītena marutā rukṣeṇa puruṣeṇa ca|
% rūkṣeṇa puruṣeṇa ca| \ T75
samantādvāsyamānāśca śuṣyante sadvacanti ca|| 7.53||
% samantādvandyamānāśca śiṣyante sma rudanti ca| \ T75
itthaṃ mārgeṇa raudreṇa pātheyarahitena ca|
% sahāyarahitena ca| \ T75
nirālambena durgeṇa nirjalena samannataḥ|| 7.54||
% nirālambena mārgeṇa durjanena samantataḥ| \ T75
aviśrāmeṇa mahatā nirgatāpāśrayeṇa ca|
% avi(pi)śrameṇa mahatā \ T75
tamorūpeṇa kaṣṭena sarvaduḥkhāśrayeṇa ca|| 7.55||
% tamorūpeṇa kalpena sarvaduḥkhāśrayeṇa ca| \ T75
nīyante dehinaḥ sarve ye mūḍhāḥ pāpakāriṇaḥ|
yamadūtair mahāghorais tadājñākāribhir balāt || 7.56||
% yamadūtairmahāghorai yamājñākāribhirbalāt| \ T75
ekākinaḥ parādhīnā mitrabandhuvivarjitāḥ|
% parādhīnāḥ mitrabandhuvivarjitāḥ| \ T75
śocantaḥ svāni karmāṇi rudantaś ca muhur muhuḥ|| 7.57||
% śocante svāni karmāṇi rodante ca muhurmuhuḥ| \ T75
pratībhūtā vivastrāśca śuṣkakaṇṭhoṣṭhatālukāḥ|
% pretabhūtā vivastrāśca \ T75
kṛśāṅgā bhītabhītāśca dahyamānāḥ kṣudhāgninā|| 7.58||
bṛddhāḥ śṛṅkhalayā keciduttānāḥ pādayor narāḥ|
% baddhāśśṛṅkhalayā \ T75
% Tp.76
ākṛṣyante ghṛṣyamāṇā yamadūtair balotkaṭaiḥ|| 7.59||
% ākṛṣyante ghuṣyamāṇā yamadūtai baloddhṛtaiḥ| \ T75
urasā'dhomukhāś cānye ghṛṣyamāṇā suduḥkhitāḥ |
% gṛṣyamāṇāssuduḥkhitāḥ| \ T75
keśapāśanibaddhena samākṛṣyanti rajjunā|| 7.60||
%% p.234
lalāṭe cāṅkuśenānye bhinnāḥ kṛṣyanti dehinaḥ|
uttānāḥ kaṇṭakapathā kecidaṅgāravartmanā|| 7.61||
% uttānakaṇṭakapathā kvacidaṅgāravartmanā| \ T75
paścādbaddhāśca jaṭhare pāśena ca prapīḍitāḥ|
% kvacitpaścānnibaddhāśca jaṭharaiśca prapīḍitāḥ| \ T75
pūritāḥ śṛṅkhalābhiśsca hastāyośca sukīrtitāḥ|| 7.62||
% nibaddhāśśṛṅkhalābhiśca hastayośca surīyatāḥ| \ T75
grīvāpāśena kṛṣyante prayānti ca suduḥkhitāḥ|
% grīvāṃ pāśe nighṛṣyantaḥ prayāntyete suduḥkhitāḥ| \ T75
jihvāśaṅkuprabaddhena kṛṣṭā nīyanti rajjunā|| 7.63||
% jihvāṃ śaṅkuprabandhena samākṛṣyanti nāpare| \ T75
% [nānādravyedharajjvādi dha sadākṛṣyanti rañjasā]| \ T75
%% Above line written inside a square bracket in T75 is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal. 
kavaryāmardhacandreṇa kṣipyamāṇā itastataḥ|
% kṛra(ka)ṭyāmardhacandreṇa \ T75
śiśne savṛṣaṇe baddhā nīyante'nye ca rajjunā|| 7.64||
% śiśne ca vṛs'ṇe badhvā \ T75
nāsāviddhāśca rajjvā ca rajjvā ca samākṛṣyanti cāpare|
% nānādhvapedharajvada sadā kṛṣyanti cāpare| \ T75
bhinnāḥ kapolayo rajjvā kṛṣyante'nye tathoṣṭhayoḥ|| 7.65||
% kṛṣyantasya tadoṣṭhayoḥ| \ T75
vibhinnāścodare cānye taptaśṛṅkhalayā narāḥ|
% tatvaśṛṅkhalayānvitāḥ| \ T75
kṛṣyante karṇayoścānyebhinnāśca civuke pare|| 7.66||
% kṛṣyante karṇayoścānye vibhinnāścubuke pare| \ T75
chinnāgrahastapādāśca chinnakaṇoṣṭhanāsikāḥ|
% chinnāgre hastapādāśca bhinnakaṇṭhoṣṭhanāsikāḥ| \ T75
sañchinnaśiśnavṛṣaṇāścinnabhinnāṅgasandhayaḥ|| 7.67||
% sa(na) chinnaśiśnāvṛṣaṇāśchinnabhinnāggasandhayaḥ| \ T75
prabhidyamānāḥ kuntaiśca bhidyamānāśca sāyakaiḥ|
itastataḥ pradhāvante krandamānā nirāśrayāḥ|| 7.68||
% itastataḥ pradhāvanti \ T75
%% Tp.77
mudgarairlohadaṇḍaiśca hanyamānā muhurmuhuḥ|
kleśaiśca vividhairghorairjvalitāgnisamaprabhaiḥ|| 7.69||
% keśaiśca vividhairghorairjvalanāgnisamaprabhaiḥ| \ T75
bhindipālairvibhidyantaḥ śravaṇāḥ pūyaśoṇitam|
% bhiṇḍipālaiḥ prabhidyante sravantaḥ vūyaśoṇitam| \ T75
sakṣatāḥ kṛmidaṣṭhāśca nīyante vivaśā narāḥ|| 7.70||
% karmadāḥ kramadaṣṭāśca \ T75
yācamānāśca salilam annaiścāpi bubhukṣitāḥ|
% annaṃ cāpi bubhuṣitāḥ| \ T75
chāyāṃ prārthayamānāśca śītārtāścānalaṃ punaḥ|| 7.71||
dānahīnāḥ prayāntyevaṃ prārthayanti sukhānnarāḥ|
% prārthayante sukhaṃ narāḥ| \ T75
gṛhītadānapātheyāḥ sukhaṃ yānti yamālayam|| 7.72||
evaṃ pathātikaṣṭena prāptāḥ pretapurannarāḥ|
% evaṃ vadanti kaṣṭena prāptāḥ pretapuraṃ narāḥ| \ T75
ājñāpitāstadā dūtaiḥ praveśyante yamāgrataḥ|| 7.73||
% yadā prajñārpitā dūtairniveśyante yamāgrataḥ| \ T75
tatra ye śubhakarmāṇas tān sammānayate yamaḥ|
% tāndharmānnayate yamaḥ| \T75
svāgatāsanadānena pādyārgheṇa priyeṇa ca|| 7.74||
dhanyā yūyaṃ mahātmānaḥ svātmano hitakāmyayā|
% svātmano hitakariṇaḥ| \ T75
yena divyasukhārthāya bhavadbhiḥ sukṛtaṃ kṛtam|| 7.75||
idaṃ vimānamāruhya divyastrībhogabhūṣitam|
svargaṃ gacchadhvamatulaṃ sarvakāmasamanvitam|| 7.76||
%% p.235
tatra bhuktvā mahābhogāṃstadante puṇyasaṃkṣayāt|
% tatra bhuktvā mahābhogādatte(nante) puṇyasya saṃkṣayāt| \ T75
yatkiñcidalpamaśubhaṃ punastadiha bhokṣyatha|| 7.77||
% yatkiñcidalpamatulaṃ punastadiha bhokṣyate| \ T75
te cāpi dharmarājānaṃ narāḥ puṇyānubhāvataḥ|
% tenāpi dharmarājena narāḥ puṇyānubhāvataḥ| \ T75
paśyanti saumyavadanaṃ mitrabhūtamivātmanaḥ|| 7.78||
% paśyanti saumyapavanaṃ mitrabhūtāmivātmanaḥ| \ T75
%% Tp.78
ye punaḥ krūrakarmāṇaste paśyanti bhayānakam|
pāpā vastabdhanayanā viparītātmabuddhayaḥ|| 7.79||
% pāpāvaṣṭabdanayanā \ T75
dṃṣṭrākarālavadanaṃ bhṛkuṭīkuṭilekṣaṇam|
% duṣṭākarālavadanaṃ \ T75
ūrdhvakeśaṃ mahāśmaśruṃ prasphuratsvadharāṃ haram|| 7.80||
% ūrdhvakeśāruṇāśmaśru praspharaddattavānanam| \ T75
aṣṭādaśabhujaṃ kruddhaṃ nīlāñjanacayopamam|
% aṣṭādaśabhujammūrdhvaṃ nīlāñjanachadopamam| \ T75
sarvāyuddhodyatakaraṃ brahmadaṇḍena tarjayan|| 7.81||
% darvāyudhodyanakaraṃ yamadaṇḍena tarjitam| \ T75
trāsantamiva trailokyam udgirantā mivānanam|
% Above line 82ab is missing in T75.
mahāmahiṣam ārūḍhaṃ dīptāgnisamalocanam|| 7.82||
raktamālyāmbaradharaṃ mahāmerumivocchritam|
pralayāmbudanirghoṣaṃ pivantamiva sāgaram|| 7.83||
% praśayāmbudanirghoṣaṃ vidantamiva sāgaram| \ T75
mṛtyuñca tatsamīpasthaḥ kālānalasamaprabham|
kālaścāñjanasaṃkāśaḥ kṛtāntaśca bhayānakāḥ|| 7.84||
% kālaṃ cāñjanasaṃkāśaṃ kṛtāṃ ca bhayanānakam| \ T75
mārī cogramahāmārī kālarātrī ca dāruṇāḥ|
% mārīṃ cogrāṃ mahāmārīṃ kālarātriṃ ca dāruṇām| \ T75
vividhā vyādhayaḥ kaṣṭā nānārūpā bhayāvahāḥ|| 7.85||
śaktikuśāṅkuśakarāḥ pāśacakrāsidhāriṇaḥ|
% śaktiśūlāṅkuśadharāḥ cakrapāśāsidāriṇaḥ| \ T75
vajradaṇḍadharā raudrāḥ kṣuratūṇadhanurdharāḥ|| 7.86||
asaṃkhyātā mahāvīryāḥ krūrāś cāñjanasaprabhāḥ|
% krūrāścāñjanasannibhāḥ| \ T75
sarvāyudhodyatakarā yamadūtā bhayanakāḥ|| 7.87||
% sarvāyudhodyotakarāḥ \ T75
anena parivāreṇa mahāghoreṇa saṃvṛtam|
% saṃvṛtaṃ ghoradarśanam| \ T75
yamaṃ paśyanti pāpiṣṭhāś citraguptañ ca bhīṣaṇam|| 7.88||
% dharmaṃ paśyanti pāpiṣṭhāścitraguptaṃ \ T75
%% Tp.79
nirbhatsayati cātyarthaṃ yamastān papakāriṇaḥ|
citraguptaś ca bhagavān dharmavākyaiḥ prabodhayan|| 7.89||
% dharmavākyaiḥ prabodhayet| \ T75
bho bho duṣkṛtakarmāṇaḥ paradravyāpahāriṇaḥ|
garvitā rūpavaryeṇa paradāravimardakāḥ|| 7.90||
% garvitā rūpadīryeṇa paradārābhimarśakāḥ| \ T75
yassvayaṃ kriyate karma tatsvayaṃ bhujyate punaḥ|
% yatsvayaṃ kriyate karma \ T75
tatkimātmopaghātārthaṃ bhavadbhirduṣkṛtaṃ kṛtam|| 7.90||
% tatkindānopabhogārthaṃ bhadbhirduṣkṛtaṃ kṛtam| \ T75
idānīṃ kiṃ pratapyadhvaṃ pīḍyamānāḥ svakarmabhiḥ|
bhuñjadhvaṃ svāni karmāṇi mātra doṣo'sti kasyacit|| 7.91||
% bhuñjadhvaṃ svāni duḥkhāni nātra doṣo na kasyacit| \ T75
%% p.236
ete me pṛthivīpālāḥ samprāptā matsamīpataḥ|
% ye te ca \ T75
svakīyaiḥ karmabhirghorairduṣprajñā balagarvitāḥ|| 7.92||
bho bho nṛpā durācārāḥ prajāvidhvaṃsakārakāḥ|
% prajāvidhvaṃsakāriṇaḥ| \ T75
alpakālasya rājyasya kṛte kiṃ duṣkṛtaṃ kṛtam|| 7.93||
rājyalobhena mohena balādanyāyataḥ prajāḥ|
yaddaṇḍitāḥ phalantasya bhuñjadhvamadhunā nṛpāḥ|| 7.94||
kva tadrājyaṃ kalatrañca yadatra(yatkṛte) cāśubhaṃ kṛtam|
% kva tadrājyaṃ kalatraṃ yadardhamardhaśubhaṃ kṛtam| \ T75
tatsarvaṃ samparityajya yūyamekākinaḥ sthitāḥ|| 7.95||
paśyāmastadbalaṃ vā'dya yena vidhvaṃsitāḥ prajāḥ|
% paśyāmastadbalaṃ sarvaṃ yena \ T75
dūtaiḥ prayātyamānānāmadhunā kīdṛśambhavet|| 7.96||
% maddūtaihanyamānānāmadhunā kīdṛśaṃ bhavet| \ T75
evaṃ bahuvidhairvākyair upalabdhāyasena te|
% upalabdhāyamena ca| \ T75
śocantaḥ svāni karmāṇi tūṣṇīntiṣṭhanti pārthivāḥ|| 7.97||
% śocanti svāni karmāṇi \ T75
%% Tp.78
iti dharmaṃ samādiśya nṛpāṇāṃ dharmarāṭ punaḥ|
tatpātakaviśuddhyartham idaṃ vacanam avravīt|| 7.80||
% tātaḥ pāpaviśudhyarthaṃ \ T75
bho bho caṇḍa mahācaṇḍa gṛhītvā nṛpatinimān|
% bho bho caṇḍā mahācaṇḍā \ T75
viśodhayadhvaṃ pāpebhyaḥ krameṇa narakāgniṣu|| 7.81||
% krameṇa narakeṣu ca| \ T75
tataḥ śīghraṃ samutthāya nṛpāṃstān gṛhya padayoḥ|
% nṛpān saṃgṛhya pādayoḥ| \ T75
bhrāmayitvātivegena vikṣipyordhvaṃ pragṛhya ca|| 7.82||
% prakṣipyordhvaṃ pragṛhya ca| \ T75
sarvaprāṇena mahatā sutapte ca śilātale|
% supratapte śilātale| \ T75
āsphārayanti tarasā vajreṇeva mahādrumāḥ|| 7.83||
% vajreṇeva mahādrumam| \ T75
tataḥ svaraktaṃ strotobhiḥ sravate tarjanīkṛtāḥ|
% tatassaraktasrotāṃsi nṛpate jharjharīkṛtāḥ| \ T75
nissaṃjñatsatataṃ deho niścetaśca prajāyate|| 7.84||
% nissaṃjñaśca tathā dehī niśceṣṭāśca prajāyate| \ T75
tataḥ sa vāyunā spṛṣṭaḥ śanair ujjīvate punaḥ|
% spṛṣṭaśśanairucchasate punaḥ| \ T75
tataḥ pāpaviśuddhyarthaṃ kṣipyate narakārṇave|| 7.85||
% kṣipanti narakārṇave| \ T75
aṣṭāviṃśatirevādhaḥ kṣiternarakakoṭayaḥ|
% kṣite narakakoṭayaḥ| \ T75
saptamasya talasyānte ghore tamasi saṃsthitāḥ|| 7.86||
% yamassvatasyādho ghrore viṣame tamasi sthitāḥ| \ T75
% pādhāntare saptamasya tṛnyānte ghore tamasi sthitāḥ| \ T75
ghorākhyā prathamā koṭiḥ sughorā tadadhaḥ sthitā|
% tadadhasthitaḥ| \ T75
atighorā mahāghorā ghorarūpā tu pañcamī|| 7.87||
% atha ghoramahāghorāghorarūpā ca pañcame(mī)| \ T75
ṣaṣṭhi taralaghorākhyā saptamī ca bhayānakā|
% ṣaṣṭhī taraṅgatārākhyā \ T75
aṣṭamī kālarātriśca navamī ca bhayotkaṭā|| 7.88||
daśamī ca tataścaṇḍā mahācaṇḍā tato'pyadhaḥ|
caṇḍakolāhalā cānyā pracaṇḍā naranāyikā|| 7.89||
%% Above 3 lines 88ab - 89cd are missing in T75.
padmā padmāvatī bhīmā bhīma bhīṣaṇanāyikā|
% bhīmā bhīṣaṇa nā(sā)yakā| \ T75
%% 237
karālā vikarālā ca caturviṃśatimā smṛtā|| 7.90||
% karālā vikarālā ca vajrā viṃśatikassmṛtā| \ T75
%% Tp.81
trikoṇā pañcakoṇā ca sudīrghā parivartulā|
saptabhaumāṣṭabhaumā ca dīptā māyetī cāṣṭamī|| 7.91||
% saptabhūmāṣṭabhaumā ca dīptā māyeti cāṣṭamī| \ T75
tā nāmataḥ samuddiṣṭā ghorā narakakoṭayaḥ|
% tāsāmatassamuddiṣṭā \ T75
aṣṭāviṃśatirevaitāḥ pāpināṃ yātanātmikāḥ|| 7.92||
% pāpānāṃ yātanātmakāḥ| \ T75
āsāṃ krameṇa vijñeyāḥ pañca pañcaiva nāyakāḥ|
% pañcapañcaiva nāyakāḥ| \ T75
pratyekaṃ sarvakoṭīnānnāmatastānnibodhata|| 7.93||
rauravaḥ prathamas teṣāṃ rudanti yatra dehinaḥ|
mahārauravapīḍābhirmahānto'pi rudanti ca|| 7.94||
tamaḥ śītaṃ tathā coṣṇaḥ pañcādyā nāyakāḥ smṛtāḥ|
% tapaśśītastathācoṣṇaṃ pañcādhyānāyakasmṛtāḥ| \ T75
sughoraḥ sutamastīkṣṇaḥ padmaḥ sañjīvanastathā|| 7.95||
% sughorāssumahāstīṣṇāḥ padmasañjīvanaśśadaḥ| \ T75
mahāmāyī vilomaśca sulomaśca kaṭaṅkataḥ|
% mahānāso vilomaśca surahīmaśca kaṅkataḥ| \ T75
tīvrakeśaḥ karālaśca vikarālaḥ prakampanaḥ|| 7.96||
% tīvravegaḥ karālaśca \ T75
mahāpadmaḥ suvaktraśca kālasūtraḥ pragarjanaḥ|
% kālavaktraḥ pramardanaḥ| \ T75
sūcīmukhaḥ sunemaśca khādakaḥ suprapīḍanaḥ|| 7.97||
% sūmukhassunamiśca khādakaḥ supradhīdhitāḥ| \ T75
kumbhīpākaḥ supākaśca krakacaścātidāruṇaḥ|
% kṛtakaścātidāruṇaḥ| \ T75
aṅgārarāśibhavanaścāmrak pūyamahāhradaḥ|| 7.98||
% aṅgārarāśibhivanamasṛk pūrahṛdayastathā| \ T75
tīkṣṇāyaḥ khaṇḍaḥ śakunir mahāsaṃvartakaḥ kratuḥ|
% tīkṣṇāyasuṇḍaśakunī mahāsaṃvartakaḥ kratuḥ| \ T75
taptajatuḥ paṅkalepaḥ pūtimāṃso dravastapuḥ|| 7.99||
% taptadantaḥ paṅkalevaṃ vūtimāṃsodravastrapuḥ| \ T75
ucchvāsakaśca niśvāsaḥ sudīrghaḥ kūṭaśālmaliḥ|
% ucchvāsaśca nirucchvāsaḥ sudīrghaḥ kūṭaśālmaliḥ| \ T75
dureṣṭaḥ sumahānādaḥ prvahaḥ supravāhaṇaḥ|| 7.100||
% pravāhassupravāhinaḥ| \ T75
% Tp.82
ṛkṣameṣavṛkāścānye siṃhavyāghragajānanāḥ|
% ṛkṣameṣavṛṣaśśalyavyāghrasihmagajānanaḥ| \ T75
śvaśūkarāśca mahiṣā vṛṣameṣā ajāstathā|| 7.101||
% aśvasūkararājāna vṛṣameṣavṛkānanāḥ| \ T75
grāhakumbhīranakrāsyāḥ sarpakūrmāśca vāyasāḥ|
% grāhakuṃbhinanarakāssarpakūrmaśca vāyasāḥ| \ T75
gṛdhrolūkajalokāśca śārdūlakapikarpaṭāḥ|| 7.101||
% gṛddhro śūkajaśūkāśca śārdūlakapikukkuṭāḥ| \ T75
gaṇḍakāḥ pūtivaktrāśca ekākṣāḥ pūtimṛttikāḥ|
% gaṇḍa(ndha)kāṣṭhādivaktrāśca raktākṣaḥ pūtamṛttikāḥ| \ T75
kaṇadūmāstuṣāgniśca kṛmīṇānnicayastathā|| 7.102||
% karṇadhūmastuṣāgniśca kṣamīṇāṃ nacayastathā| \ T75
abhedyaścāpratiṣṭhaśca rudhirāṇāñca bhojanaḥ|
% amedhyśca pratīkāro rudhirāmbhaḥ prapūjanam| \ T75
lalābhakṣātmabhakṣaśca sarvabhakṣaḥ sudāruṇaḥ|| 7.103||
% lalābhikṣātmabhikṣā ca \ T75
saṅkaṭaḥ suviśālaśca vikaṭaḥ kaṭapūtanāḥ|
% saṅkaṭāssuviśālāśca vikaṭaḥ kaṭapūtanaḥ| \ T75
ambarīṣaḥ kaṭāhaśca kaṣṭā vaitaraṇī nadī|| 7.104||
sutaptalohaśayanam ekapādaḥ prapūraṇaḥ|
% ekapādaḥ supūraṇaḥ| \ T75
asitālavanaṃ ghroraṃ makṣibhṛṅgaprapīḍitam|| 7.105||
% api tālavanaṃ ghoraṃ gatibhaṅgaḥ prapīḍanam| \ T75
%% p.238
tilātasīkṣuyantrāṇi kūṭapāśapramardanaḥ|
% tilātanīkṣuyantrāṇi kūṭaveṣaḥ pramardanaḥ| \ T75
mahācullī sucullī ca taptalohamayī śilā|| 7.106||
% mahācūrṇānadūrṇā ca taptalohamayā śilā| \ T75
parvataḥ kṣuradhārākhyastathā yamalaparvatam|
% sarvatakṣuradhārākhyastathāyamalaga(sa)rvataḥ| \ T75
mūtraviṣṭhāndhakupaśca śā(kṣā)lakūpaśca śātanaḥ|| 7.107||
% yūtra(mūtra) niṣṭhāndhā kūpāśca kṣārakūpāśca śātanāḥ| \ T75
muśalolūkhalaṃ yantraṃ śilāśakaṭalāṅgalam|
% śilāśakaṭalāṅgalaḥ| \ T75
tālapatrāsigahanaṃ mahāpātakamaṇḍapam|| 7.108||
% lālapatrāsigahanaṃ mahāmaśakamaṇḍapam| \ T75
sammohanāsthibhaṅgaśca taptaśulamayo'śubham|
% sammohano hastibhaṃgaḥ taptaśūlamayo gulaḥ(śa)| \ T75
bahuduḥkhaṃ mahāduḥkhaṃ kaśmalaṃ śavalaṃ malaṃ|| 7.109||
% bahuduḥkhamahāduḥkhaṃ kaśmalaṃ śamalaṃ malam| \ T75
%% Tp.83
halāhalaṃ virūpañca surūpaśca yamānugaḥ|
% halāhalo virūpāśca \ T75
ekapādastripādaśca tīvraścāvīcirantimaḥ|| 7.110||
% tīvraścāpi cirantamaḥ| \ T75
aṣṭāviṃśatirityete kramaśaḥ pañcanāyakāḥ|
% aṣṭāviṃśatirevaite kramaśaḥ pañcakāsmṛtāḥ| \ T75
koṭīnāmānupūrveṇa pañca pañcaiva nāyakāḥ|| 7.111||
% koṭīnāmanupūrveṇa \ T75d
rauravādyamavīcyantaṃ narakāṇāṃ śataṃ smṛtam|
% kāravādyamapīcyantaṃ \ T75
catvāriṃśacchatādhikaṃ mahānarakamaṇḍalam|| 7.112||
% catvāriṃśatsamadhikaṃ mahānarakamaṇḍapam| \ T75
eṣu pāpāḥ prapacyante narakarmānurūpataḥ|
% yeṣu pāpāḥ prapīḍyante narāḥ karmānurūpataḥ| \ T75
yātanābhirvicitrābhirnarāḥ karmakṣayā bhṛśam|| 7.112||
% yātanābhirvicitrābhiḥ ātmakarmakṣayādbhṛśam| \ T75
āmalaprakṣayād yadvadagnau dhāmyanti dhātavaḥ|
% āmalavṛkṣadhādyadyadagnādhāmyanti dhātavaḥ| \ T75
tathā pāpakṣayāt pāpāḥ śodhyante narakāgniṣu|| 7.113||
sugāḍhaṃ taptayorbaddhā taptaśṛṅkhalayā naraḥ|
% sugāḍhaṃ hastayorbadhvā taptaśṛṅkhalayā narāḥ| \ T75
mahāvṛkṣāgraśākhāsu ullambyante'sya kiṅkaraiḥ|| 7.114||
% lambyante yamakiṅkaraiḥ| \ T75
tataste sarvayatnena kṣiptā dolanti kiṅkaraiḥ|
% tataste sarvayatnena kṣiptāloḍyanti kiṅkaraiḥ| \ T75
dolāntaścāti vegena niḥsaṃjñā yānti yojanam|| 7.115||
% dāryantāścātivegena vassaṃ jñāyanti yojanam| \ T75
antarikṣasthitānāntu lohabhāradvayannaraḥ|
% lohabhāraśataṃ tataḥ| \ T75
pādayor badhyate teṣāṃ yamadūtair mahābalaiḥ|| 7.116||
tena bhāreṇa mahatā bhṛśamātānitā narāḥ|
% bhṛśamāyāsitā narāḥ| \ T75
dhyāyantaḥ svāni karmāṇi tūṣṇīntiṣṭhanti niścalāḥ|| 7.117||
% dhyāyanti svāni karmāṇi \ T75
tataḥ keśairagnikalpairlohadaṇḍaiḥ sakaṇṭakaiḥ|
