atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivadharmottare saṁsāra gatir nāma
aṣṭamo’dhyāyaḥ
oṃ namaḥ śivāya

atha nārakiṇāṃ puṃsām adharmād eva kevalāt ||
kṣaṇamātreṇa bhūtebhyaḥ śarīram upajāyate || 8.1 ||
tadvad dharmeṇa caikena devānām aupapātikaṃ ||
sadyaḥ prajāyate divyaṃ śarīraṃ bhūtasārataḥ || 8.2 ||
karmaṇā vyatimiśreṇa yaccharīram ihātmanaḥ ||
tadbhūtapariṇāmena vijñeyaṃ hi caturvidhaṃ || 8.3 ||
udbhijjāḥ sthāvarā jñeyās tṛṇagulmādirūpiṇaḥ ||
kṛmikīṭapataṅgādyāḥ svedajā nāma dehinaḥ || 8.4 ||
aṇḍajāḥ pakṣiṇaḥ sarpā nakrā matsyāḥ sakacchapāḥ || 
jarāyujāś ca vijñeyā mānuṣāḥ sa catuṣpadāḥ || 8.5 ||
tatra siktā jalair bhūmir antaraṣmavipācitā ||
vāyunā vyūhyamānā ca khe bījatvaṃ prapadyate || 8.6 ||
yathartukāni bījāni saṃsiktāny ambhasā punaḥ ||
ucchūnatāṃ mṛdutvañ ca mūlabhāva vrajanti ca || 8.7 ||
tanmūlād aṅkurotpattir aṅkurāt patrasambhavaḥ ||
parṇān nālan tataḥ kāṇḍaṃ kāṇḍāc ca prasavaḥ punaḥ || 8.8 ||
prasavāc ca tuṣaṃ kṣīraṃ kṣīrāt taṇḍulasambhavaḥ ||
taṇḍulāś ca yadā pakvā mriyantyoṣadhayas tadā || 8.9 ||
yavādyāḥ ṣaṇaparyantāḥ śreṣṭhāḥ saptadaśa smṛtāḥ ||
oṣadhyāḥ phalapākāntāḥ śeṣāḥ kṣudrāḥ prakīrtitāḥ || 8.10 ||
etā lūnā marditāś ca śanai ruddhṛtya saṃskṛtāḥ ||
sūrpolūkhalayantrādyaiḥ sthālyām udakavanhibhiḥ || 8.11 ||
ṣaḍvidhāhārabhedena pariṇāmyanti tadvidhaiḥ ||
anyonyarasasaṃyogād anekasvādunā punaḥ || 8.12 ||
bhakṣyaṃ bhojyaṃ ca peyaṃ ca lehyaṃ cosyas ca picchilaṃ ||
iti bhedāḥ ṣaḍaṅgasya madhurādyāś ca ṣaḍguṇāḥ || 8.13 ||
tad annaṃ piṇḍakavalair grāsair bhuktaṃ ca dehibhiḥ ||
antaḥ sthūlāśaye pūrvaṃ prāṇaḥ sthāpayati kramāt || 8.14 ||
ātiṣṭhed bhukta āhāras taṃ vāyuḥ kurute dvidhā ||
sampraviśyānnamadhye ca pṛthag annaṃ pṛthag jalaṃ || 8.15 ||
agner ūrdhvajalaṃ sthāpya tad annaṃ cajalopari ||
jalasyādhaḥ svayaṃ sthitvā so’gnir vidhamate śanaiḥ || 8.16 ||
vāyunā dhmāyamāno ’gnir atyuṣṇaṃ kurute jalaṃ ||
tadannam uktatoyena samantāt pacyate punaḥ || 8.17 ||
dvidhā bhavati tat pakvaṃ pṛthakkīṭaṃ pṛthag rasaḥ ||
malair dvādaśabhiḥ kīṭaṃ bhinnaṃ dehād vahir vrajet || 8.18 ||
karṇākṣināsikājivhād antāḥ śiśnaṃ gudaṃ nakhāḥ ||
malāśrayāḥ kaphaḥ (cāḥ) svedo viṇmūtre dvādaśa smṛtāḥ || 8.19 ||
hṛtpadme pratibaddhāś ca sarvā nāḍyaḥ samantataḥ ||
tāsāṃ mukheṣu taṃ sūkṣmaṃ prāṇaḥ sthāpayate rasaṃ || 8.20 ||
rasena tena tā nāḍīḥ prāṇaḥ pūrayate punaḥ ||
pratarppayanti sampūrṇās tāś ca dehaṃ samantataḥ || 8.21 ||
tataḥ sa nāḍīmadhyasthaḥ śārīreṇoṣmaṇā rasaḥ ||
pacyate pacyamānāc ca bhavet pākadvayaṃ punaḥ || 8.22 ||
tvaṅmedasaṃ samantāc ca rudhiraṃ ca prajāyate ||
raktāl lomāni māṃsaṃ ca keśāḥ snāyuś ca māṃsataḥ || 8.23 ||
snāyoḥ śirās tathā’sthīni nakhā majjāsthiṃsambhavāḥ ||
majjātaḥ karaṇaṃ vaikalyaṃ śukraṃ ca prasavātmakaṃ || 8.24 ||
iti dvādaśadhānnasya pariṇāmaḥ prakīrtitaḥ ||
śukrāntaś ca tataḥ śukrādasya dehasya sambhavaḥ || 8.25 ||
ṛtukāle sadā śukraṃ nirdoṣaṃ yonisaṃsthitaṃ ||
tadā tadvāyunā spṛṣṭaṃ strīraktenaikatāṃ vrajet || 8.26 ||
visargakāle śukrasya jīvaḥ kāraṇasaṃyutaḥ ||
vṛttyā praviśale yoniṃ karmabhiḥ svairnniyojitaḥ || 8.27 ||
tac chukraṃ raktam ekastham ekānhāt kalkalam bhavet |
pañcarātreṇa kalalama …….. (?) …………….. || 8.28 ||
budbudaṃ saptarātreṇa māṃsapeśī bhavet tataḥ ||
dvisaptāhād bhavet peśā raktamāṃsācitādṛḍhā || 8.29||
bījasyevāṅkuraḥ peśyāṃ pañcaviṃśatirātritaḥ ||
bhavanti māsamātreṇa pañcadhā jāyate punaḥ || 8.30 ||
grīvā śiraś ca skandhaś ca pṛṣṭhavaṃśastathodaraṃ ||
māsadvayena sarvāṇi kramaśaḥ sambhavanti ca || 8.31 ||
tribhir māsaiḥ prajāyante saddravyāṅkerasandhayaḥ ||
māsaiś caturbhir aṅgulyaḥ prajāyante yathākramaṃ || 8.32 ||
mukhaṃ nāsā ca karṇau ca māsair jāyanti pañcabhiḥ ||
dantapaṅktis tathā guhyaṃ jāyante ca nakhā punaḥ || 8.33 ||
vibhaktāvayavaḥ spaṣṭaḥ punar māsāṣṭakena ca ||
pañcātmakasamāyuktaḥ paripakva satiṣṭhati || 8.34 ||
māturāhāravīryeṇa ṣaḍvidhena rasenaca ||
nābhisūtranibandhena varddhate sa dine dine || 8.35 ||
tataḥ smṛtiṃ labhej jīvaḥ sampūrṇe’smin śarīrake ||
sukhaduḥkhaṃ vijānāti nidrāsvapnaṃ purā kṛtaṃ || 8.36 ||
mṛtaś cāhaṃ punarjāto jātaś cāhaṃ punarmṛtaḥ ||
nānāyonisahasrāṇi mayā dṛṣṭāni jāyate || 8.37 ||
adhunā jātamātro’haṃ prāpte saṃskāra eva vā ||
tat tac chreyaḥ kariṣyāmi yena gacche na sambhave || 8.38 ||
garbhasthaś cintayaty evam ahaṃ garbhād viniḥsṛtaḥ ||
adhyeṣyāmi śivajñānaṃ saṃsāravinivartakaṃ || 8.39 ||
evaṃ sa garbhaduḥkhena mahatā paripīḍitaḥ ||
jīvaḥ karmavaśād āste mokṣopāyaṃ vicintayan || 8.40 ||
yathā girivarākrāntaḥ kaś cid duḥkhena tiṣṭhati ||
tathā jarāyuṇā dehī duḥkhan tiṣṭhati veṣṭitaḥ || 8.41 ||
patitaḥ sāgare yadvad duḥkham āste samākulaḥ ||
garbhodakena siktāṅgas tathāste vyākulaḥ pumān || 8.42 ||
lohakumbhe yathā nyastaḥ pacyate kaścid agninā ||
garbhakumbhe tathā kṣiptaḥ pacyate jaṭhar āgninā || 8.43 ||
sūcibhir agnivarṇābhir vibhinnasya nirantaraṃ || 
yad duḥkhan tu prajāyeta tadgarbhe’ṣṭaguṇambhavet || 8.44 ||
garbhavāsāt paro vāsaḥ kaṣṭenaivātra kutracit ||
dehinā duḥkhabahulaṃ sughoram atisaṅkaṭaṃ || 8.45 ||
ityetad garbhaduḥkhaṃ hi prāṇināṃ parikīrtitaṃ ||
calāsthirāṇāṃ sarveṣām ātmagarbhānurūpataḥ || 8.46 ||
garbhāt koṭiguṇaṃ duḥkhaṃ yoniyantraprapīḍanāt ||
sammūrcchitasya jāyeta jāyamānasya dehinaḥ || 8.47 ||
śarīraṃ pīḍyamānasya yantreṇaiva samantataḥ ||
śirasā tāḍyamānasya pāpam udgarakeṇa ca || 8.48 ||
garbhāt koṭiguṇaṃ duḥkhaṃ paritrāṇam avindataḥ ||
yantreṇa pīḍitā yadvan niḥsārāḥ syustilekṣavaḥ || 8.49 ||
tathā śarīraṃ niḥsāraṃ yoniyantraprapīḍitaṃ ||
asthipaṭatulāstambhasnāyubandhena yantritaṃ || 8.50 ||
raktamāṃsamṛdāliptaṃ viṇmūtradravyabhājanaṃ ||
keśaromatṛṇācchannaṃ rogāyatanamāturaṃ || 8.51 ||
badanaikamahādvāraṃ gavākṣāṣṭaka bhūṣitaṃ ||
oṣṭhadvayakapāṭaṃ ca dantajihvārggalānvitaṃ || 8.52 ||
nāḍisvedapravāhaṃ ca kaphapittapariplutaṃ ||
jarāśokasamāviṣṭakālavaktrānalombhitaṃ || 8.53 ||
kāmakrodhendhanākrāntaṃ vyasanaiś copamarditam ||
bhogatṛṣṇāturaṃ mūḍhaṃ rāgadveṣavaśānugaṃ || 8.54 ||
saṃvartitāṅgapratyaṅgajarāyupariveṣṭitaṃ ||
saṅkaṭena viviktena yonimārgeṇa nirgataṃ || 8.55 ||
viṇmūtraraktasiktāṅgaṃ ṣaṭkośāṃśasamudbhavaṃ ||
asthipañjarasaṃkhyāntaṃ jñeyam asmin kalevare || 8.56 ||
śatatrayaṃ ṣaṣṭyadhikaṃ pañca peśīśatāni ca ||
sārddhābhis tisṛbhiś channaṃ samantād romakoṭibhiḥ || 8.57 ||
śarīraṃ sthūlasūkṣmābhir dṛśāś cayāvatāḥ sthitāḥ ||
tāvat ībhiś ca nāḍīnāṃ koṭibhis tatsamanvitaṃ || 8.58 ||
prasvedam aśucir yābhir antasthaṃ sravate vahiḥ ||
dvātriṃśad daśamāḥ proktāḥ viṃśatiś ca nakhāḥ smṛtāṃ || 8.59 ||
pittasya kuḍavaṃ jñeyaṃ kaphasyārddhāḍhakaṃ smṛtaṃ ||
vasāḥpalāni viṃśac ca tad arddhe kalalasya ca || 8.60 ||
pañcābrade (?) palājñeyāḥ palāni daśa medasaḥ ||
palatrayaṃ mahāraktamajjāyās tu caturguṇaṃ || 8.61 ||
śukrārddhaṃkuḍavaṃ jñeyaṃ tadvīryan dehināṃ varaṃ ||
māṃsāsthnām ekapiṇḍena palasāhasratram ucyate || 8.62 ||
raktaṃ palaśataṃ jñeyaṃ viṇmūtrañ cāpramāṇataḥ ||
iti dehagṛhaṃ hy etan nityasyānityam ātmanaḥ || 8.63 ||
aviśuddhaṃ viśuddhasya karmabandhavinirmitaṃ ||
śukraśoṇitasaṃyogād dehaḥ sañjāyate yataḥ || 8.64 ||
nityaṃ viṇmūtrapūrṇaś ca tenāśuddhaḥ prakīrtitaḥ ||
yathāntarviṣṭhayā pūrṇaḥ śuciḥ syān na bahirghaṭaḥ || 8.65 ||
yatnataḥ śodhyamāno’ pi deho’yamaśucis tathā ||
yaṃ prāpyāti pavitrāṇi pañcagavyaṃ havīṃṣi ca || 8.66 ||
aśucitvaṃ kṣaṇādyānti kim anyad aśucis tataḥ ||
hṛdy ānyapy annapānāni yaṃ prāpya surabhīṇi ca || 8.67 ||
aśucitvaṃ prayāntyāśu kim anyad aśucis tataḥ ||
 hejanāḥ! kin na paśyadhvaṃ yan niryāti dine dine || 8.68 ||
svadehāt kaśmalaṃ pūtis tad ādhāraḥ kathaṃ śuciḥ ||
dehaḥ saṃśodhyamāno’pi pañcagavyakuśāmbubhiḥ || 8.69 ||
ghṛṣyamāṇam ivāṅgāraṃ nirmalatvaṃ na gacchati ||
srotāṃsi yasya satataṃ pravahanti girer iva || 8.70 ||
kaphamūtrād yamaśuci sa dehaḥ śuddhyate kathaṃ ||
sarvāśucinidhānasya śarīrasya na vidyate || 8.71 ||
śucir ekaḥ pradeśo’ pi viṇmūtrasya dṛter iva ||
smṛtvātmadehasrotāṃsi mṛttoyair dhāvataḥ karau || 8.72 ||
tathāpyaśuci bhāṇḍasya na virajyanti kiñjanāḥ ||
kāyaḥ sraggandhapuṣpādyair yatnenāpi susaṃskṛtaḥ || 8.73 ||
na jahāti svabhāvaṃ hi śvapuccham iva nāmitaṃ ||
yathā jātyaiva kṛṣṇārṇī na śuklāsyādupāyataḥ || 8.74 ||
tathā saṃśodhyamānāpi bhaven mūrtir anirmalā ||
jighrann api svadurgandhaṃ paśyann api svakalmalaṃ || 8.75 ||
na virajyati loko’yaṃ pīḍayann api nāsikāṃ ||
aho mohasya māhātmyaṃ yena vyāmohitaṃ jagat || 8.76 ||
jighrana paśyan svadoṣāṃś ca kāvyasya na virajyate ||
svadehāśucigandhena na virajyeta yo naraḥ || 8.77 ||
virāgakāraṇantasya kim anyad upadiśyate ||
sarvam etaj jagatpūtaṃ deha evāśuciḥ paraḥ || 8.78 ||
tatpalāvayavasparśāc chucir apyaśucir bhavet ||
gandhalepāpanodārthaṃ śaucaṃ dehasya kīrtitaṃ || 8.79 ||
dvayasyāpagamāt paścād bhāvaśuddhyā viśuddhyati ||
gaṇgātoyena sarveṇa mṛdbhāraiś ca na gopamaiḥ || 8.80 ||
 āmṛtyorācaracchaicaṃ bhāvaduṣṭo na śuddhyati ||
tīrthasnānais tapobhir vā bhāvaduṣṭo na śuddhyati || 8.81 ||
adṛtiḥ kṣālitastīrthe kiṃ śuddhim adhigacchati || 
antarbhāvapraduṣṭasya viśato’pi hutāśane || 8. 82 ||
na svargo nāpavargaś ca dehanirdahanam paraṃ ||
bhāvaśuddhiḥ paraṃ śaucaṃ pramāṇaṃ sarvakarmasu || 8.83 ||
anyathāliṅgyate kāntā bhāvena duhitānyathā ||
manasābhidyate bṛttir abhinneṣv api bastuṣu || 8.84 ||
anyathaiva stanaṃ putraś cintayatyanyathā patiḥ ||
paśya paśya ca bhāvasya mahābhāgyam aśoṣataḥ || 8.85 ||
pariṣvakto’pi yannāryā bhāvahīno na kāmayet ||
bhāvanā dvividhānasyambhakṣyāṇi surabhīṇi ca || 8.86 ||
abhāvena narastasmād bhāvaḥ sarvatra kāraṇaṃ ||
cittaṃ śodhaya yatnena kimanyairbāhyaśodhanaiḥ || 8.87 ||
bhāvataḥ suviśuddhātmā svargaṃ mokṣaṃ ca vindati ||
jñanām alāmbhasā puṃsaḥ sadvairāgyamṛdā punaḥ || 8.88 ||
avidyā rāgaviṇmūtralepagandhaviśodhanaṃ ||
evam etac charīraṃ hi nisargād aśuci smṛtaṃ || 8.89 ||
tvaṅmātrasāraṃ nissāraṃ kadalīsārasannibhaṃ ||
jñātvaivaṃ doṣavad dehaṃ yaḥ prājñaḥ śithilībhavet || 8.90 ||
so’tikrāmati saṃsāraṃ dṛḍhagrāhī ca tiṣṭhati ||
evam etan mahākaṣṭaṃ janmaduḥkhaṃ prarkīrtitaṃ || 8.91 ||
puṃsām ajñānadoṣeṇa nānākarmavaśena ca ||
garbhasthasya smṛtir yāsīt sā jātasya praṇaśyati || 8.92 ||
sammūrcchitasya duḥkhena yoniyantraprapīḍanāt ||
bāhyena vāyunā tasya mohājñānena dehinaḥ || 8.93 ||
spṛṣṭamātrasya ghoreṇa jvaraḥ samupajāyate ||
tena jvareṇa mahatā mahāmohaḥ prajāyate ||8.94 ||
sammūḍhasya smṛtibhraṃśaḥ śīghraṃ sañjāyate punaḥ ||
smṛtibhraṃśāt tatas tasya pūrvakarmavaśena ca || 8.95 ||
rasaḥ sañjāyate tūrṇaṃ jantos tatraiva janmani ||
rakto mūḍhaś caloko’yam akārye sampravartate || 8.96 ||
nacātmānaṃ vijānāti na paraṃ naca daivataṃ ||
na śṛṇoti paraṃ bhūyaḥ sati cakṣuṣi nekṣate || 8.97 ||
same pathi śanair gacchan skhalatīva pade pade ||
buddhau satyāṃ na jānāti bodhyamāno budhair api || 8.98 ||
saṃsāre kṣipyate tena rāgalobhavaśānugaḥ ||
gaṃgāsmṛter abhāvena śāstramuktaṃ śivena tu || 8.99 ||
tad dukhaḥ kathanārthāya svargamokṣaprasādhakaṃ ||
ye satyasmin śivajñāne sarvakāmārthasādhake || 8.100 || 
na kurvanty ātmanaḥ śreyas tadatraṃ mahad adbhutaṃ ||
avyaktendriyavṛtvitvād āste duḥkhaṃ mahatpunaḥ || 8.101 ||
icchann api na śaknoti vaktuṃ kartuṃ ca satkriyāṃ ||
dantotthāne mahad duḥkhaṃ maulena vyādhinā tathā || 8.102 ||
bālarogaiś ca vividhaiḥ pīḍābālagrahair api ||
tṛḍbubhukṣāparītāṅgaḥ kvacit tiṣṭhati cāraṭan || 8.103 ||
viṇmūtrabhakṣaṇādyaṃ ca mohād bālaḥ karoti vai ||
kaumāre karṇavedhe ca tanmātā pitṛtāḍanaṃ || 8.104 ||
akṣarādhyayanādyaiś ca duḥkhaṃ syād guruśāsanāt ||
pramattendriya bṛtteś ca kāmarāgaprapīḍanāt || 8.105 ||
rāgābṛtasya satataṃ kutaḥ saukhyaṃ hi yauvane ||
īrṣyayā ca mahad duḥkhaṃ mohādraktasya jāyate || 8.106 ||
netrasyākupitasyeva rāgo duḥkhāya kevalaṃ ||
na rātrau vindate nidrāṃ kāmāgniparikheditaḥ || 8.107 ||
divā cāsya kutaḥ saukhyam arthopārjanacintayā ||
striyāyāsitadehasya ye puṃsaḥ śukravindavaḥ || 8.108 ||
na te sukhāya mantavyaḥ khedajā iva bindavaḥ ||
kṛmibhiḥ khādyamānasya kuṣṭhinaḥ pāmitasya ca || 8.109 ||
kaṇḍūyānāgnitāpena yad bhavet strīṣu tad vidhaḥ ||
yādṛśaṃ manyate saukhyaṃ gaṇḍapūjya vinirgamāt || 8.110 ||
tādṛśaṃ strīṣu mantavyaṃ nādhikaṃ tāsu vidyate ||
gaṇḍasya vedanā yadvat sphuṭitasya nivartate || 8.111 ||
tadvat strīṣv api tad viddhi na saukhyaṃ paramārthataḥ ||
barccomūtrasamutsargāt sukhaṃ bhavati yādṛśaṃ || 8.112 ||
tādṛśaṃ strīṣu vijñeyaṃ mūḍhaiḥ kalpitam anyathā ||
nārīṣvavastubhūtāsu sarvadoṣāśrayāsu ca || 8.113 ||
nāṇumātrakamapy evaṃ sukham asti vicārataḥ ||
sammānam apamānena viyogena ca saṅgamaḥ || 8.114 ||
yauvanaṃ jarayā grastaṃ ka saukhyam anupadravaṃ ||
valīpalitakhālityaiḥ śithilīkṛtavigrahaḥ || 8.115 ||
sarvakriyāsvaśaktaś ca jarayā jarjarīkṛtaḥ ||
strīpuṃsor yauvanaṃ rupaṃ yad anyonyaṃ priyaṃ purā || 8.116 ||
tad eva jarayā grastam ubhayor api na priyaṃ ||
apūrvavat svamātmānaṃ jarayā parivartitaṃ || 8.117 ||
yaḥ paśyan na virajyeta ko’nyastas mādacetanaḥ ||
jarābhibhūtaḥ puruṣaḥ patnīputrādibāndhavaiḥ || 8.118 ||
aśaktatvād durācārair bhṛtyaiś ca paribhūyate ||
dharmam arthaṃ cakāmaṃ ca mokṣaṃ ca na jarīyataḥ || 8.119 ||
śaktaḥ sādhayituṃ tasmād yuvā dharmaṃ samācaret ||
vātapittakaphādīnāṃ vaiṣamyaṃ vyādhiriṣyate || 8.120 ||
vātādīnāṃ samūhaś ca deho’yaṃ parikīrtitaḥ ||
tasmād vyādhimayaṃ jñeyaṃ śarīram idam ātmane || 8.121 ||
vātādyavyatiriktatvād vyādhīnāṃ pañjarasya ca ||
rogair nānāvidhair yāni dehe duḥkhāny anekadhā || 8.122 ||
tāni naivātmavedyāni kim anyatkathayāmy ahaṃ ||
ekottaraṃ mṛtyuśatam asmin dehe pratiṣṭhitaṃ || 8.123 ||
tatraikaḥ kālasaṃjñaś ca śeṣāstvāg antavaḥ smṛtāḥ ||
ye tv ihāgantavaḥ proktās te praśāmyanti bheṣajaiḥ || 8.124 ||
japahomapradānaiś ca kālamṛtyur na śāmyati ||
yadi vā’pamṛtyur nna syād viṣayaḥ syād aśaṅkitaḥ || 8.125 ||
na cāsti puruṣas tasmād apamṛtyor vibheti yaḥ ||
vividhā vyādhayaḥ śastraṃ sarpādyāḥ prāṇinas tathā || 8.126 ||
viṣāṇi cābhicārāś ca mṛtyor dvārāṇi dūhinī ||
pīḍitaṃ sarvarogādyair api dhanvantariḥ svayaṃ || 8.127 ||
svasthī kartu nna śaknoti kālaprāptaṃ hi dehinaṃ ||
nauṣadhan na tapodānaṃ na mantrā na ca bāndhavāḥ || 8.128 ||
śaknuvanti paritrātuṃ naraṅkālaprapīḍitaṃ ||
rasāyanatapojapyair yogasiddhair mahātmabhiḥ || 8.129 ||
kālamṛtyur api prājñair jīyate nālasair naraiḥ ||
nāsti mṛtyusamaṃ duḥkhaṃ nāsti mṛtyusamaṃ bhayaṃ || 8.130 ||
nāsti mṛtyusamas trāsaḥ sarveṣām eva dehināṃ ||
sadbhāryāputramitrāṇi rājaiśvyaryasukhāni ca || 8.131 ||
abadhyāni ca bairāṇi mṛtryuḥ sarvāṇi kṛntati ||
henarāḥ! kin na paśyadhvaṃ sahasrasyāpi madhyataḥ || 8.132 ||
janāḥ śatāyuṣaḥ pañca bhavanti na bhavanti vā ||
aśītikā vipacyante kecit saptatikā narāḥ || 8.133 ||
paramāyuḥ sthitaṃ ṣaṣṭis tad apy aniścitaṃ punaḥ ||
yasya yāvad bhaved āyur dehinaḥ pūrvakarmabhiḥ || 8.134 ||
tasyārddhaṃ cāyuṣo rārtri harate’rddhaṃ smṛto yamaḥ ||
bālabhāve ca mohena vārddhakye jarayā punaḥ || 8.135 ||
varṣāṇāṃ viṃśatiryāti dharmakāmārthavarjitāḥ ||
āgantukair bhayaiḥ puṃsāṃ vyādhiśokair anekadhā || 8.136 ||
hriyate’rddhaṃ ca tatrāpi yacchreyas tad vivarjitaṃ ||
jīvitānte ca maraṇaṃ mahāghoram avāpnuyāt || 8.137 ||
jāyate yonikoṭīṣu mṛtaḥ karmavaśāt punaḥ ||
dehabhedena yaḥ puṃsāṃ viyogaḥ karma saṃkṣayāt || 8.138 ||
maraṇaṃ tad vinirdiṣṭaṃ na nāśaḥ paramārthataḥ ||
mahātamaḥ praviṣṭasyac cidyamāneṣu marmasu || 8.139 ||
yad duḥkhaṃ maraṇe jantor nna tasyehopamā kvacit ||
hātāta! mātarhākānte! krandantyevaṃ suduḥkhitāḥ || 8.140 ||
maṇḍūkā iva sarpeṇa gīryante mṛtyunā janā ||
bāndhavaiḥ sa pariṣvaktaḥ priyaiś ca parivāritaḥ || 8.141 ||
niśvasandīrghomuṣṇaṃ ca mukhena pariśuṣyatā ||
caturantena khaṭvāyāḥ parivartan muhur muhuḥ || 8.142||
sa mūḍhaḥ kṣipate’ty arthaṃ hastapādānitas tataḥ ||
khaṭvāto vāñchate bhūmiṃ bhūmeḥ khaṭvāṃ punar mahīṃ || 8.143 ||
vivastras tyaktalajjaś ca mūtraviṣṭhānulepanaḥ ||
yācamānaś ca salilaṃ śuṣkakaṇṭhoṣṭhatālukaḥ || 8.144 ||
cintamānaś ca vittāni kasyaitāni mṛte mayi ||
khe nayaṃ ca balāt bhūyaḥ kālapāśena karṣitaḥ || 8.145 ||
mriyate paśyatām eva gale ghuraghurāyate ||
jīvas tṛṇajalaukeva dehād dehaṃ viśet kramāt || 8.146 ||
samprāpyottaram aṅgena dehaṃ tyajati pūrvikaṃ ||
narāṇāṃ prārthanāduḥkham adhikaṃ hi vivekinaḥ || 8.147 ||
kṣaṇikaṃ maraṇe duḥkham anantaṃ prārthanākṛtaṃ ||
jagatām patir arthitvād viṣṇur vāmanatāṅ gataḥ || 8.148 ||
adhikaḥ ko’paras tasmād yo na yāsyati lāghavaṃ ||
jñātaṃ mayedam adhunā mṛto bhavati yadguruḥ || 8.149 ||
na paraṃ prārthayed bhūyas tṛṣṇālāghavakāraṇaṃ ||
ādau duḥkhaṃ madhyaduḥkham ante duḥkhaṃ ca dāruṇaṃ || 8.150 ||
nisargād eva bhūtānām iti duḥkhaparamparā ||
vartamānāny atītāni duḥkhāny etāni yāni tu || 8.151 ||
narā na bhāvayanty ajñā na virajyanti tena te ||
aty āhārān mahāduḥkham anāhārāt tato’dhikaṃ || 8.152 ||
turitaṃ jīvitaṃ kaṣṭam anne’py evaṃ kutaḥ sukhaṃ ||
kṣudhā hi sarvarogāṇāṃ vyādhiḥ śreṣṭhatamaḥ smṛtaḥ || 8.153 ||
sā cānnauṣadhimātreṇa kṣaṇamātraṃ praśāmyati ||
kṣudvyādhivedanā tīvrā niḥ śeṣabalakṛntanī || 8.154 ||
te yānti bhūto mriyate yathānyair vyādhitor naraḥ ||
tad rasaṃ mihikā gandhāj jivhāgraparivartinī || 8.155 ||
tatkṣaṇārdhārdhakālena kaṇṭhaṃ prāpya nivartate ||
iti kṣudvyādhitaptānām annauṣadhabalaṃ smṛtaṃ || 8.156 ||
na tat sukhāya mantavyaṃ paramārthena paṇḍitaiḥ ||
mṛtopamaś ca yacchete sarvakāryavivarjitaḥ || 8.157 ||
tatrāpi tu kutaḥ saukhyaṃ tamasāc chāditātmanaḥ ||
prabodhe’pi kutaḥ saukhyaṃ kāryair upahatātmanaḥ || 8.158 ||
kṛṣisevādhvagorakṣāvāṇijyādipariśramaiḥ ||
prātaḥ purīṣamūtrābhyāṃ madhyānhe tṛḍbubhukṣayā || 8.159 ||
tṛptāhaṃ yena vādhyante nidrayā niśi jantavaḥ ||
arthasyopārjane duḥkhamarjitasya ca rakṣaṇe || 8.160 ||
nāśe duḥkhaṃ vyaye duḥkham arthe’py evaṃ kutaḥ sukhaṃ ||
caurebhyaḥ svajanād agneḥ salilāt pārthivād api || 8.161 ||
bhayam arthavatān nityaṃ mṛtror dehabhṛtām iva || 
khe yathā pakṣibhir māṃsaṃ bhakṣyante śvāpadair bhuvi || 8.162 ||
jale ca bhakṣyate matsyais tathā sarvatra vittavān ||
vimohayanti sampattau tāḍayanti vipattiṣu || 8.163 ||
khedayantyar janākāle kadā bhogāḥ sukhāvahāḥ ||
yaś cārthapatir udvigno yaś ca sarvārthanispṛhaḥ || 8.164 ||
tayor arthapatir duḥkhī sukhī sarvārthanispṛhaḥ ||
śītena duḥkhaṃ hemante grīṣme tāpena dāruṇam || 8.165 ||
barṣāsu vātavarṣābhyāṃ kāle’pye vaṃ kutaḥ sukhaṃ ||
vivāhe vistarair duḥkhaṃ tadgarbhodvahane punaḥ || 8.166 ||
prasave’patyadoṣaiś ca duḥkhaṃ viṣṭhādikarmabhiḥ ||
dantākṣirogaḥ putrasya hā kaṣṭaṅkiṅkaromyahaṃ || 8.167 ||
gāvo naṣṭā bṛtti bhagnān kvadhiṃ vā prapalāyitāḥ ||
amī prāhuśakāḥ prāptā bhaktacchedaś ca me gṛhe || 8.168 ||
bālāpatyā ca me bhāryā kaḥ kariṣyati rādhanaṃ ||
pradeyakālaḥ kanyāyāḥ kīdṛśaś ca varobhavet || 8.169 ||
…………………………………………………………….
iti cintābhibhūtānāṃ kutaḥ saukhyaṃ kuṭumbināṃ || 8.170 ||
kuṭumbacintākulitasya puṃsaḥ śrutaṃ ca śīlaṃ ca guṇāś ca sarve ||
apakvakumbhe nihitā ivāpaḥ prayānti dehena samaṃ vināśaṃ || 8.171 ||
rājyepi hi mahad duḥkhaṃ sandhivigrahacintayā ||
putrād api bhayaṃ yatra tatra saukhyaṃ hi kīdṛśaṃ || 8.172 ||
svajātīyād bhayaṃ prāyaḥ sarveśām eva dehināṃ ||
ekadravyābhilāṣitvāc chunām iva parasparaṃ || 8.173 ||
cāpadhṛpyabalaḥ kaścin nṛpaḥ khyātosmi bhūtale ||
nikhilaṃ yat tiraskṛtya sukhaṃ tiṣṭhati nirbhayaḥ || 8.174 ||
yuddhebāhusahastraṃ hi prapapāta mahītale ||
śrīmataḥ kārtavīryasya ṛṣiputraḥ pratāpavān || 8.175 ||
ṛṣiputrasya rāmasya rāmodaśarathātmajaḥ ||
jaghāna vīryamatulam ūrdhvagaṃ yanmahātmanaḥ || 8.176 ||
jarāsandhena rāmasya kṛṣṇatve nāśitaṃ yaśaḥ ||
jarāsandhasya bhīmena bhīmasyāpi hanūmatā || 8.177 ||
hanumānapi sūryeṇa vikṣiptaḥ patitaḥ kṣitau ||
sūryaḥ pratāpayukto’pi meghaiḥ pracchādyate kvacit || 8.178 ||
kṣipyante vāyunā meghā vāyor vīryaṃ nagair jitaṃ ||
dahyante vanhibhiḥ śaulāḥ sa vanhiḥ śāmyate jalaiḥ || 8.179 ||
taj jalaṃ śoṣyate sūryais te sūryāḥ saha vāriṇā ||
trailokyena sametāś ca naśyanti brahmaṇo dine || 8.180 ||
brahmāpi trideśaiḥ sārddham upasaṃhriyate punaḥ ||
parārddhadvayakālānte śivena paramātmanā || 8.181 ||
evaṃ nāsti sa saṃsāre yasya sarvotamaṃ balaṃ ||
vihāyaikaṃ jagannāthaṃ paramātmānamavyayaṃ || 8.182 ||
jñātvā sātiśayaṃ sarvam abhimānaṃ vivarjayet ||
evambhūte jagatyasmin kaḥ śūraḥ paṇḍito’pi vā || 8.183 ||
nehāsti sarvavit kaścin na ca mūrkhaś ca sarvathā ||
yo yad vastu vijānāti tena tatra sa paṇḍitaḥ || 8.184 ||
na sarvadā na sarvatra prabhāvaḥ sadṛśaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
sthitiḥ sātiśayatvena prabhāvaḥ kasyacit kvacit || 8.185 ||
dānavainnirjitā devās te devair nirjitā punaḥ ||
ity anyonyasthitāveṣāṃ bhogau jayaparājayau || 8.186 ||
nivātakavacāḥ sarve dānavā balagarvitāḥ ||
nirjitās te’rjjunenaiva gopālaiḥ so’pi nirjitaḥ || 8.187 ||
evaṃ vastraṣugaṃ rājñaḥ prasthamātrān na bhojanaṃ ||
pānaśayyāsanaṃ caikaṃ śeṣaṃ duḥkhāya kevalaṃ | 8.188 ||
saptabhaume’pi bhavane khaṭvāpādaparigrahaḥ ||
udakumbhaṃ cavantībhyaḥ kleśāyānyaḥ pravistaraḥ || 8.189 ||
pratyūṣe tūryanirghoṣaḥ samaḥ sarvanivāsibhiḥ ||
rājño’bhimānamātraṃ hi mamaitad vādyate gṛhe || 8.190 ||
sarvam ābharaṇam bhāraḥ sarvam ālepanaṃ malaṃ ||
sarvaṃ pralapitaṃ gītaṃ nṛtyam unmattaceṣṭitaṃ || 8.191 ||
ity eva rājyasambhogaiḥ kutaḥ saukhyaṃ vicārataḥ ||
nṛpāṇāṃ vyagracittānām anyonyātiśayāḥ sthitāḥ || 8.192 ||
naraiḥ puṇyaphalaṃ svarge mūlacchedena bhujyate ||
na cānyat kriyate karma so’tradoṣaḥ sudāruṇaḥ || 8.193 ||
chinnamūlastarur yadvad avasyaṃ patati kṣitau ||
tadvat puṇyakṣayāt sarve prapatanti divaukasaḥ || 8.194 ||
sukhābhilāṣaniṣṭhānāṃ duḥkhaṃ bhogābhisaṃkṣayāt ||
akasmāt patanād duḥkhaṃ kaṣṭaṃ sarva divaukasāṃ || 8.195 ||
iti svarge’pi devānāṃ nāsti saukhyaṃ vicārataḥ ||
kṣayoccātiśayācchuddhau svargabhogīya karmaṇāṃ || 8.196 ||
tatrakaṣṭaṃ mahāduḥkhaṃ narakāgniṣu dehināṃ ||
ghoraiś caturvidhaiḥ pāpair vāṅmanaḥ kāyakarmabhiḥ || 8.197 ||
kuṭhāraiś chedanaṃ tīvraṃ valkalānāṃ ca takṣaṇaṃ ||
parṇaśākhāphalānāṃ ca pātanañ 
cogravāyunā || 8.198 ||
unmūlanaṃ vimardaś ca gajair anyaiś ca dehibhiḥ ||
dāvāgnihimaśoṣaiś ca duḥkhaṃ sthāvarajātiṣu || 8.199||
tṛḍbubhukṣā ca sarpāṇāṃ krodhaduḥkhaś ca dāruṇaṃ ||
dṛṣṭvā taṃ ghātanaṃ loke pāśena ca nibandhanam || 8.200 ||
akasmāj janmamaraṇaṃ kīṭānāṃ ca muhur muhuḥ ||
sarīsṛpanikāyānām evaṃ duḥkhāny anekadhā || 8.201 ||
varṣāśītātapair duḥkhaṃ sukaṣṭaṃ mṛgapakṣiṇāṃ ||
kṣuttṛṣṇākleśādibhiś ca bhayatrastāḥ sadā mṛgāḥ || 8.202 ||
kṣuttṛṣādidamantaś ca vadhabandhanatāḍanaṃ ||
nāsāvedhena santrāsaḥ pratodakaśaghātanaṃ || 8.203 ||
veṇukuntādinigaḍaṃ muhuraṅkuśavādhanaṃ ||
bhārodvahanasaṃkleśaḥ śikṣāyuddhādipīḍanaṃ || 8.204 ||
ātmayūthaviyogaś ca vīlīnayanabandhanaṃ ||
paśunāganikāyānām evaṃ duḥkhāny anekadhā || 8.205 ||
garbhavāse mahad duḥkhaṃ janmaduḥkhaṃ tathā nṛṇāṃ ||
vālye ca duḥkham ajñānāt kaumāre guruśāsanāt || 8.206 ||
yauvanekāmarāgābhyāṃ duḥkhaṃ caiverṣyayā punaḥ ||
kṛṣivāṇijyasetnādhvagorakṣādyaiś ca karmabhiḥ || 8.207 ||
bṛddhabhāve ca jarayā vyādhibhiś ca prapīḍitam ||
maraṇe ca mahadduḥkhaṃ prārthanāyān tathādhikam || 8.208 ||
rājāgnijaladāyādacauraśatrubhayaṃ mahat ||
arthasyārjanarakṣārthaṃ duḥkhaṃ nāśe vyaye punaḥ || 8.209 ||
kārpaṇyamat sarau yadvat tṛṣṇādhikyaṃ bhayaṃ madaḥ ||
akārye sampravṛttiś ca duḥkhāni dhanināṃ sadā || 8.210 ||
bhṛtir dhṛtiḥ kusīdaś ca dāsatvaṃ paratantratā ||
iṣṭāniṣṭairviyogāś ca saṃyogaś ca sahasraśaḥ || 8.211 ||
durbhikṣaṃ durbhagatvaṃ ca mūrkhatvaṃ ca daridratā ||
adharottara bhāgaś ca marakaṃ rāṣṭravibhramaḥ || 8.212 ||
anyonyātiśayād duḥkham anyonyābhibhavāt punaḥ ||
antarbahiḥ prakopāś ca rājye duḥkhaṃ mahībhṛtāṃ || 8.213 ||
anityatā ca bhāvānām adhupāṇāṃ ca pātanaṃ ||
anyonyasmānmahīyastvam anyonyaś cāpi lakṣaṇaṃ || 8.214 ||
ity evam ādibhir duḥkhair yasmād vyāptaṃ carācaraṃ ||
nirayādimanuṣyāntan tasmāt sarvaṃ jayed budhaḥ || 8.215 ||
skandhāt kvacinnayan bhāraṃ viśrāmaṃ manyate yathā ||
tadvat sarvam idaṃ loke duḥkhaṃ duḥkhena śāmyate || 8.216 ||
anyonyātiśayāt pāpābhibhavād bhogasamplavāt ||
dharmakṣayāc ca devānāṃ divi duḥkham avanti taṃ || 8.217 ||
nānāyonisahasreṣu sambhavaḥ puṇyasaṃkṣayāt ||
rogāś ca vividhākārā devaloke’pi saṃsthitāḥ || 8.218 ||
yajñasya hi śiraśichannam aśvibhyāṃ saṃhitaṃ punaḥ ||
tena doṣeṇa yajñasya śirorogaḥ sadaiva hi || 8.219 ||
mārtaṇḍabhānoḥ kuṣṭhaṃ ca varuṇasya jalodaraḥ ||
pūṣṇo daśanavaikalyaṃ bhujastambhaḥ śacīpateḥ || 8.220 ||
kṣayarogaś ca sumahān somasya parikīrtitaḥ ||
 jvaraś ca sumahānāsīd dakṣasyāpi prajāpateḥ || 8.221 ||
kalpe kalpe’pi devānāṃ mahatām api saṃkṣayaḥ ||
parārdhadvayakāle ca brahmaṇaś cāpy anityatā || 8.222 ||
dakṣaduhitaraṃ pautrīṃ brahmā kāmitavān punaḥ ||
krodhena ca jayādevīṃ yogasthāṃ śaptavān prabhuḥ || 8.223 ||
kāmakrodhau sthitau yatra tatra doṣās tadātmakāḥ ||
duḥkhāni ca samastāni saṃsthitāni na saṃśayaḥ || 8.224 ||
viṣṇoś ca janmamaraṇaṃ māyāvitvaṃ ca sarvataḥ ||
strīvadhaḥ kāmaśaktiś ca sārathyam pāṇḍave bale || 8.225 ||
rudreṇa tripuraṃ dagdhaṃ dakṣayajñaś ca nāśitaḥ ||
skandasya janma tacchrutvā krīḍāś cānyāḥ sahasraśaḥ || 8.226 ||
evaṃ trayo’pi rāgādyair doṣair devāḥ samanvitāḥ ||
śivaḥ
ebhyaḥ paraḥ śivaḥ śāntaḥ paripūrṇas tu muktidaḥ || 8.227 ||
evam etaj jagat sarvam anyonyātiśaye sthitaṃ ||
duḥkhair ākulitaṃ jñātvā nirvedaṃ paramaṃ vrajet || 8.228 ||
nirvedāc ca virāgaḥ syād virāgājjñānasambhavaḥ ||
jñānena tatparaṃ jñātvā śivamuktin tadāpnuyāt || 8.229 ||
samastaduḥkhanirmuktaḥ svasthātmā sa sukhī sadā ||
sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇaś ca muktaḥ ity abhidhīyate || 8.230 ||

iti śivadharmottare saṃsāragatirnnāmāṣṭamo’dhyāyaḥ ||






atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivadharmottare svargyanārakacinho
navamo’dhyāyaḥ
oṃ namaḥ śivāya
atha svargabhogam anubhūya narāḥ kṣīṇapuṇyās tadvāsanānubhavād imaṃ lokam āgatya śubha deśa-
jāti-  kula-rūpāyuḥśrutaḥ-prajñā-  śīla-  śauca-satya-dama-dāna-dayā-dākṣiṇya-  kṣamārogyaḥ
satva- balotsāha- prabhāvataḥ ||
pradhāna-  dhana-  dhānya-  ratna-  yān-  vāhana-  harmya-  prāsāda-  gīta-  nṛtya-  vādya kalā-
sukha – śayāsana-  mṛṣṭānna-  pāna-  sugandhavāsa – strīratna-  putra-  paśu-  vastrālaṅkāra-
hiraṇya-  mahī-  bhogāyatanāvasathaḥ-  sabhā-  satra prapārāma-  taḍāga-  dīrghikā-  kūpodyāna-
deva-  dvija-  guru – vidyā-  vinītaḥ-  sādhu-  tapasvi-  pūjā-  satkārānuṣṭhānābhiratas tapaḥ
svādhyāya- dhyāna jñānāpavarga svarge kathābhirāmaś ca bhavatīti || 9.1 ||
tasmād yuktaṃ ca svarggīyaṃ karma kartuṃ ca vastutaḥ ||
dharmādrakṣyaṃ dhanaṃ saukhyam adharmād duḥkhasambhavaḥ || 9.2 ||
tasmād dharmaṃ sukhārthāya kuryāt pāpaṃ ca varjjayet ||
lokadvaye’pi yatsaukhyaṃ dharmāt tatprāpyate yataḥ || 9.3 ||
dharmam evam ataḥ kuryāt sarvakāmārthasiddhaye ||
muhūrtam api jīveta naraḥ śuklena karmaṇā || 9.4 ||
na kalpam api kṛṣṇena lokadvayavirodhinā ||
atha narakeṣu narāḥ kena pāpena karmaṇā yātanāvicitrāḥkaṣṭā anubhūya
bhūmim abhyāgacchanti || 9.5 ||
tataḥ pāpaśeṣeṇa vṛkṣa-kīṭa-mṛga-paśu jāti-  lakṣaṇaiḥ
pratyakṣa narakeṣu punardduḥkhānyanubhavanti || 9.6 ||
tataḥ kṣīṇāvaśiṣṭa-pāpāstadvāsanāmāyānubhāvādetairllakṣaṇairmanuṣyajātau jāyante || 9.7 ||
tadyathā || brahmahā kṣayī || surāpaḥ śyāmadantaḥ || suvarṇacauraḥ kunakhī ||
duścarmāgurutalpagaḥ || tadapavādapariśravaṇād badhiraḥ || svayam anukīrtanāt kharaḥ ||
ānindakaḥ pratihantā guror apasmārī || tadājñābhaṅgād bhagandarī || matsarī ca bhavet kṛmiḥ ||
avajñākārī cāndhaḥ || gurukāryopekṣī kṛmiḥ || duṣprajñas tatkarmaṇi śaṭhaḥ kṛkalāsaḥ ||
kupitamakṣamāpya gurum apakrāmataḥ śirorogaḥ || ete gurukarmavipākāḥ || 9.8 ||
śvacaṇḍālāḥ patitāḥ pāpiṣṭhāḥ || dvijakharāḥ || sandhyavahāryāntyajātiḥ || agnidaḥ kuṣṭhī ||
rajatāpahārī darduraḥ || kūṭasākṣī mukharogī || mātāpitṛ guru tapasvi
vyādhita. bāla. vṛddhārta. śaraṇāgata. tyāgī. animittaḥ pādākṣirogī || pratijñāya 
brāhmaṇasyādānādalpāyuḥ || tadvṛtyapahārādāmagarbhāntaḥ || pākī prapā nāśaka naiṣṭika
pratinirvṛttaḥ sadārogī || patnībahutve satyekarāmaḥ sadālkībaḥ || svāminā dharme
niyuktastadanuṣṭhāna. satkāra. pūjā. pradānādiṣu śāṭhya. vyavahārī jalodarī || durbbala
vadhe balavataḥ samutprekṣādaṅgahīnatvaṃ || annahāryajīrṇavyavahārapakṣapātī jivhārogī || svayaṃ
pravartita. vrata. dharmānuṣṭhāna. vicchedanaḥ pratipatnīṣvaviyogaḥ svayamagrahīturggalarogaḥ ||
akṛta pañca mahāyajña bhogī viṭvarāhaḥ || parvamaithunī pramehī || svadārebhyo’nyatra dīvyataḥ
keśālpatvaṃ || parīkṣīṇa. mitra. bandhu. svāmi. sādhu. janāyamantā paribhūtakaṣṭabṛttiḥ
kṣīṇavṛttirathātithi. manaḥ khedako'ntaḥkapolapiṭakaḥ || sūryoḍhasyāpratiśrayadānādiṣṭapatnī.
viyogaḥ || chadmanā guru. svāmi. mitramupacarataḥ prāptārtha. pari bhraṃśoviśrambhāpahārī sarvaḥ
duḥkhāśrayī || mithyā guṇairātmāpakarṣī vāmanaḥ || gopṛṣṭha ghāti kaṭillutī godhno
jātyandhaḥ || goduḥkhakārī gonāsaḥ || gonirddayāścipiṭanāsaḥ || nistejaskaḥ sabhāyāṃ
galagaṇḍī || krodhanaś caṇḍālaḥ || piśunaḥ pūtināsikaḥ || sūcakaḥ pūtivaktraḥ || trapu. cāmara.
sīsa. sahasra . jaṇḍakāśeṣa . vikrayī. mṛgavyādhaḥ || kuṇḍāśī bhṛtakaḥ || tailiko
nāstikaḥ || raṅgopajīvī . abhakṣyabhakṣī . || apratirūpavyavahāradarśī gaṇḍamālī ||
jñānamanyāyataḥ pratigṛhṇan mūkaḥ || pustakahāryandhaḥ || puṇyakathākṣepako vakranāsaḥ ||
śiṣṭācīrṇa .  dharma. dūṣakaḥ kekarākṣaḥ || sādhu. tapasvi. deva. dvijāti. jñāna. yoga. dveṣṭā
puṇya. dāna. pravṛtta. pratiṣedhakaḥ kṛmidantī || deva. brahmasvāpahārako vāntāśī || 
taḍāgārāmabhettāchettāṅgahīnaḥ prabhu, surādi, vyavasthā samaya bhedakastaskarāṇāmarakṣitā
vyavahāreṣvamadhyasthāṃ || chala. grāhyajitabhṛtyaḥ || sadāpuruṣovyādhyabhibhūtaḥ ||
paradārābhigāmyaguptadāraḥ || svāmi. mitra. guru. drohī. vātarogī || goṣṭhotkarṣī
duścarmā || kharāśvābhigāmī madhumehī || dharmapatnīṣvanyamaithuna. pravartakastūvarakaḥ ||
svagotra. samaya. stryabhigāmī ślīpadī || mātāpitṛbhaginīstryabhigāmyajīvī ||
parāpavādyalasaḥ || kṛtaghnaḥ sphuṭitākṣaḥ || sarvārambhaviphalāstadaśeṣa, kubja, kuṇḍa.
puṇḍa. vyaṅga daridratāḥ sphūṭitapāṇi . pādāṅgāvayavāḥ || dhūsarāś chadminaḥ ||
parapiṇḍopajīvinaś cīrakarppaṭadharāḥ sthūlamalinavāsasaḥ || kṣutpipāsāturāḥpretarupiṇaḥ
satatamudvignahṛdayā bahupralāpinaḥ puṇyakathāparāṅmukhāḥ || strīṣvāsaktā cittā durbhagāḥ ||
strīparādhīnānnapāna maithunāmbarā devāgni. guru. bṛddha. brāhmaṇāvamantāraḥ ||
pasabhābhirsṛṣṭastrīkāḥ sadāpahṛta. sarvasvā badhabandhana. tāḍana. nirbhartsanābhibhūtāḥ ||
strīdyūta . madyapāna . niratā nitya . kruddhāsyāḥ || pāpaniratāḥ smṛtiparihīṇāḥ
puṇyadveṣṭāraḥ paramarma. kīrtana. ratāhīnāṅgā hīnācārā hīnānnapānavastra. śayāsanāḥ
kalyāyuṣaḥ svalpabuddhayaḥ || śaṭha. ṣaṇḍha, caṇḍa.bhaṇḍa. śailūṣa. taskara. parapreṣya. parakarma.
vyādhitā duḥkhitāḥ krūrakarmāṇaś copajāyante || tasmādenasi prāyaścittavyaṃ, tīrṇa
yaś cittāḥ pariśuddha lakṣaṇā jāyante || svargā nārakāś ca. puṇya hetutvād ubhayarupāḥ ||
saṅkīrṇaphalās tatkarmādhikonabhogya. vyavahārādhāra. parirakṣitād bhavanti ||
tatraiteślokāḥ || 9.9 ||
yasmāt pāpena duḥkhāni tīvrāṇi subahūni ca ||
tasmāt pāpaṃ na kartavyam ātmapīḍākaraṃ hi tat || 9.10 ||
yasmin kāle ca deśe ca vayasā yādṛśena ca ||
kṛtaṃ śubhāśubhaṃ karma tat tasmāt tena bhujyate || 9.11 ||
tasmāt sadaiva dātavyam avicchinnaṃ sukhārthibhiḥ ||
vicchidyante yathā bhogā grīṣme kusarito yathā || 9.12 ||
satyaṃ vaktum aśeṣato ’sti sulabhā vāṇī manodhyāyituṃ ||
dātuṃ dānavaraṃ śaraṇyam abhayaṃ vāhyaṃ pitṛbhyo jalaṃ ||
pūjārthaṃ hi sadāśivasya vimalaḥ sandhānayajñaḥ paraḥ 
kṣudvyādheḥ phalamūlam asti rasituṃ kleśātmakaiḥ kindhanaiḥ || 9.13 ||

iti śivadharmottare svargganārakacinhādhyāyo navamaḥ ||

atha paśupatimate śivadharmemahāśāstre śivadharmottare prāyaścittaṃnāma

atha saṃsāramuktyarthaṃ jñānayogaṃ bravīmi te
śivaprakāśakaṃ jñānaṃ yogas tatraikacintanā 1
svasiddhāntāvirodhena yas tarkeṇa vicārayet
dharmajñānāpavargārthaṃ satatvaṃ vetti netaraḥ 2
pūrvottaravirodhena ko ’trārtho ’bhimato bhavet
ity ādyam ūhanaṃ tarkaḥ śuṣkatarkān vivarjayet 3
tasmād āgamayuktyaivaṃ sūkṣmārthapravicāraṇam
kartavyaṃ nānumānena kevalena vipaścitā 4
hīnamadhyottamaphalaṃ bahudvāraṃ yataḥ śubham
parīkṣya tasmāt kūrvīta puṇyaṃ sādhu mahatphalam 5

[Śiva known through his authoritative scripture]
ādimadhyāntanirmuktaḥ svabhāvavimalaḥ prabhuḥ
sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇaś ca śivo jñeyaḥ śivāgame 6
sarvārthasādhakaṃ jñānaṃ śivayogaṃ ca śāśvatam
prakāśayati muktyarthaṃ mumukṣūṇām ayaṃ śivaḥ 7
bahutve ’pi hi śāstrāṇāṃ sarvajñena śivena yat
praṇītam amalaṃ jñānaṃ tat pramāṇaṃ na saṃśayaḥ 8
yaḥ sarvajñaḥ susaṃpūrṇaḥ svabhāvavimalaḥ śivaḥ
sarvadoṣavinirmukto brūyāt sa katham anyathā 9

[the world inconceivable without Śiva]
asaty asmiṃ jagannāthe tamobhūtam idaṃ bhavet
sūryeṇaiva vihīnaṃ hi nirālokaṃ jagad yathā 10
abhāvād īśvarasyeyaṃ jagatsṛṣṭiḥ kathaṃ bhavet
acaitanyāt pradhānasyāśaktitvāt puruṣasya ca 11
pradhānaparamaṇvādi yāvat kiñcid acetanam
tadakartṛ svayaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ buddhimatkāraṇaṃ vinā 12
na yathā ghaṭabhāvena mṛtpiṇdaḥ svayam arcchati
tathājñā buddhibhāvena na tiṣṭhet prakṛtiḥ svayam 13
dharmādharmāpadeśaś ca bandhamokṣavicāraṇam
na sarvajñaṃ vinā puṃsām ādisarge prasidhyati 14
vaidyaṃ vinā nirākrandāḥ kliśyanti rogiṇo yathā
śivaṃ vinā jagat tadvan nirākrandaṃ bhavet sadā 15
tasmād anādiḥ sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇaḥ paraḥ śivaḥ
asti nāthaḥ paritrātā puṃsāṃ saṃsārasāgarāt 16
ye bhyasyanti śivajñānaṃ śivoktaṃ śivabhāvitāḥ
te bhavanti śivāḥ śāntā bhave majjanty abhāvitāḥ 17
asaty asmin jagannāthe tamobhūtam idaṃ jagat
sūryeṇaiva vihīnaṃ hi nirālokaṃ jagad yathā 18
yathānādipravṛtto ’yaṃ ghoraḥ saṃsārasāgaraḥ
śivo ’pi hi tathānādiḥ saṃsārān mocakaḥ sthitaḥ 19
vyādhīnāṃ bhaiṣajaṃ yadvat pratipakṣaṃ svabhāvataḥ
tadvat saṃsāradoṣāṇāṃ pratipakṣaḥ śiva sthitaḥ 20
tasmād anādiḥ sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇaḥ svabhāvataḥ
muktihetuḥ śivaḥ siddhaḥ sarvajño jñānabhāṣakaḥ 21
yadi cedaṃ pramāṇaṃ syān na sarvajñasya bhāṣitam
kiṃ pramāṇaṃ tadā grāhyaṃ brūta paśyāmahe budhāḥ 22
vākyaliṅgā hi vaktāraḥ kriyāliṅgāś ca kārakāḥ
tasmāt svenaiva liṅgena vijñeyās tadguṇā budhaiḥ 23

[liberation in one birth taught in scripture]
āgamatve ’pi sāmānye kaḥ pradveṣaḥ śivāgame
anāyāsena yatroktā muktir ekena janmanā 24
svapakṣarāgam utsṛjya guṇeṣv ādhīyatāṃ manaḥ
yato guṇās tataḥ puṃsāṃ kalyāṇaṃ sakalāṃ sthitam 25
yuktaṃ caitad guṇaiḥ sarvair yasmāj jñānaṃ śivātmakam
tasmāt tenaitadabhyasyaṃ yasyāsti guṇagauravam 26
atyāsannātisukaram atīva ca mahāphalam
kaḥ prājñaḥ kāryam utsṛjya dīrghaṃ sūtraṃ samāśrayet 27
madhvarthī parvataṃ kaścid dūraṃ samprasthitaḥ śanaiḥ
yady adho madhu sampaśyet kimarthaṃ parvataṃ vrajet 28
evam evaikabhavikāṃ vimuktiṃ purataḥ sthitām
vihāyānekabhavikāṃ kaḥ prājñaḥ pratipatsyate 29
ihānyatra gataḥ kālas tatraikaṃ janma gacchatu
jijñāsyatām iyat tāvan muktir ekena janmanā 30
yadi nāma na muktiḥ syād ekenaivātra janmanā
anekabhavikā muktir bhavataḥ kena vāryate 31
tasmād yatraikabhavikā muktir jñānena niścitā
tacchraddhā tu bhaven nyāyam apratyakṣāsu muktiṣu 32
yathā samīpe dūre ca sadṛśaṃ bhojanadvayam
sānukāle vikāle ca bhoktā cātibubhūkṣitaḥ 33
tayor gṛhṇātu katamaṃ kathayadhvaṃ vipaścitaḥ
samīpe yadi manyethā muktim evaṃ śivātmikām 34
sanmārgauṣadhadṛṣṭāntaiḥ svayam utprekṣya yuktitaḥ
vaktavyaṃ pratibodhāya kāryākāryavivekinaḥ 35
iti ye paramaṃ śāntaṃ pratipannā maheśvaram
te labhanti sukhenaiva vimuktiṃ bhavasāgarāt 36
akartājñaḥ paśur bhoktā vibhur nityaś ca sa prabhuḥ
kiñcitkartā sa kiñcijjñaḥ puruṣaḥ pañcaviṃśakaḥ 37
na karoti yataḥ sarvaṃ svabhogād yat karoti ca
asvātantryād akartā yaḥ kiñcitkartā tu so ’ndhavat 38
na vetti tattvataḥ sarvaṃ tenājñaḥ puruṣaḥ paśuḥ
buddhyādhyavasitaṃ kiñcij jñānaṃ kiñcijjña ucyate 39

[knowledge of creation]
acetanaṃ vibhu sūkṣmaṃ bhogyaṃ sādhāraṇaṃ dhruvam
caturviṃśakam evaṃ ca pradhānaṃ guṇalakṣaṇam 40
puṃsāṃ bhogāpavargārtham īśvarecchāpracoditam
pradhānād abhavad rudras tathā viṣṇupitāmahau 41
satkāryakaraṇopetāḥ suviśuddhā mahābalāḥ
jagataḥ kāraṇatvena trayo devā vyavasthitāḥ 42
pradhānāc cābhavad buddhir jagaddhetuḥ śivecchayā
buddher api ca saṃkṣobhād ahaṃkāras tridhābhavat 43 
ahaṃkārāc ca sūkṣmāṇi tanmātrāṇīndriyāṇi ca
sūkṣmebhyaḥ pañca bhūtāni tebhyaḥ sthūlam idaṃ jagat 44
caturviṃśakam avyaktaṃ puruṣaḥ pañcaviṃśakaḥ
rudraḥ ṣaḍviṃśakaḥ proktaḥ śivaś ca paratas tataḥ 45
saptāviṃśatimaḥ śāntaḥ susūkṣmaḥ parameśvaraḥ
svargāpavargayor dātā taṃ vijñāya vimucyate 46

[motivation for yoga]
jñānena hi bhaven muktir na vā yasyāsti saṃśayaḥ
sa muktipratyayārthāya śivayogaṃ samabhyaset 47
yogasiddhyekadeśe ’pi dṛṣṭe mokṣe bhaven matiḥ
dṛṣṭam etan mayā yadvan mokṣas tadvad dhruvaṃ bhavet 48
na kevalaṃ hi yogena muktiḥ sampratyayo bhavet
apy aṣṭaguṇam aiśvaryaṃ yogābhyāsāt pravartate 49
dhyātā dhyānaṃ tathā dhyeyaṃ yac ca dhyānaprayojanam
etac catuṣṭayaṃ jñātvā yogaṃ yuñjīta yogavit 50
jñānavairāgyasampannaḥ śraddadhānaḥ kṣamānvitaḥ
śivabhaktaḥ sadotsāhī dhyānecchaṃ puruṣaḥ smṛtaḥ 51
dhyai cintāyāṃ smṛto dhātuḥ śivacintā muhur muhuḥ
jñānena pariśuddhena jñānaṃ dhyānam ataḥ smṛtam 52
sakalaḥ satanuḥ śāntaḥ sarvajñaḥ sarvadaḥ prabhuḥ
nānārūpavikalpena dhyeyaḥ siddhyartham īśvaraḥ 53
vimuktiḥ pratyayaḥ pūrvam aiśvaryaṃ cāṇimādikam
ity etad dvividhaṃ jñeyaṃ śivadhyānaprayojanam 54
yujaty anena puruṣaḥ śivaḥ saṃyojakaḥ smṛtaḥ
phalena yojakaṃ tasmād dhyāyet satatam īśvaram 55

[factors unpropitious for yoga]
nājīrṇāmlarasodgāre na ca viṇmūtrabādhane
na chardyāṃ nātisāre ca nātibhuktaḥ śramānvitaḥ 56
na cātikarmanirataś cintāvyākulitendriyaḥ
na ḍimbe gurukārye vā na cātikṣutpipāsitaḥ 57
na daṃśamaśakākīrṇe na ca prāṇisamanvite
śmaśānacaityavalmīke sarpaśvāpadasevite 58
nadīsamudratīre vā na jalāśrayasannidhau
jīrṇodyānagṛhāvāse na bhīsthāne vicintayet 59
[a state conducive to yoga]
susnigdhānnālpabhojī ca vātalāhāravarjitaḥ
yuktāhāravihārātmā yuktaceṣṭaś ca karmasu 60
yuktanidrāvabodhaś ca sarvāyuktavivarjitaḥ
śraddadhānaḥ kṣamī nityaṃ yāvadarthaparicchadaḥ 61
[a place for yoga]
sthitaḥ śivāśrame guhye niḥśabde janavarjite
puṣpāmrādiphalopete pūrvoktāvasathānvite 62
supralipte susaṃmṛṣṭe gandhadhūpādhivāsite
muktapuṣpasamākīrṇe vitānoparisaṃyute 63
āsanaṃ tūlasampūrṇaṃ sitavastrāvaguṇṭhitam
kṛṣṇājinottarīyaṃ ca vinyasen mṛducarmaṇi 64 
padmakasvastikādīnām anyas tenāsanena tu
tadadhyāsya namaskṛtvā śivaṃ devīṃ gaṇādhipam 65
[karaṇa]
ṛjugrīvāśirovakṣo nātiśliṣṭoṣṭhalocanaḥ
kiñcidunnāmitaśirā dantair dantān na saṃspṛśet 66
dantāgrasannidhau jihvām acalāṃ sanniveśya ca
pārṣṇibhyāṃ vṛṣaṇau rakṣan tathā prajananaṃ punaḥ 67
ūrdhvorūpari saṃsthāpya bāhū tiryakprayatnataḥ
dakṣiṇaṃ karapṛṣṭhaṃ tu nyased vāmatalopari 68
unnāmya śanakaiḥ pṛṣṭham uro viṣṭabhya cāgrataḥ
samprekṣya nāsikāgraṃ svaṃ diśaś cānavalokayan 69
saṃhṛtaprāṇasaṃcāraḥ pāṣāṇa iva niścalaḥ
maitrādivāsanāyuktaḥ paraṃ vairāgyam āśritaḥ 70
amārgeṇāpi yo yogaṃ śraddadhānaḥ samabhyaset
so ’pi kālena bahunā dhruvaṃ yogam avāpnuyāt 71
[the throne]
gacchaṃs tiṣṭhan svapan jāgran nimiṣann amiṣann api
śucir vāpy aśucir vāpi śivaṃ sarvatra cintayet 72
svadehāyatanasyāntar manasā sthāpya śaṅkaram
hṛtpadmapīṭhikāmadhye śivadhyānena cintayet 73
dhyānayajñaḥ paraḥ śuddhaḥ sarvadoṣavivarjitaḥ
teneṣṭvā muktim āpnoti bāhyaśuddhaiś ca nādhvaraiḥ 74
jñānayogapradhānatvād antaraṅgaṃ vimuktidam
bahiraṅgapradhānaṃ ca yajñādyaṃ bhogasādhanam 75
tasmāt svargīyam utsṛjya karma yajñādyam adhruvam
śāśvataṃ mokṣadaṃ śuddhaṃ jñānadhyānaṃ samāśrāyan 76
hiṃsādidoṣamuktatvād viśuddhaś cittasādhanaḥ
dhyānayogaḥ paras tasmād apavargaphalapradaḥ 77
tasmād aśuddhaṃ svargīyam anityaṃ bāhyasādhanam
yajñādyaṃ karma santyajya muktyarthaṃ yogam abhyaset 78
vikāramuktam avyaktaṃ bhogyabhogasamanvitam
cintayed dhṛdaye pūrvaṃ kramād vāpi guṇatrayam 79
tamaḥ pracchādya rajasā rajaḥ sattvena cchāditam
dhyāyet trimaṇḍalaṃ pūrvaṃ kṛṣṇaṃ raktaṃ sitaṃ kramāt 80
sattvopari guṇātītaṃ puruṣaṃ pañcaviṃśakam
heyam etad aśuddhaṃ ca tyaktvā śuddhaṃ vicintayet 81
aiśvaryapaṅkajaṃ divyaṃ puruṣopari saṃsthitam
dvādaśāṅgulavistīrṇaṃ śuddhaṃ vikasitaṃ sitam 82
nālam aṣṭāṅgulaṃ tasya nābhīkandasamudbhavam 
padmapatrāṣṭakaṃ jñeyam aṇimādiguṇāṣṭakam 83
tatkarṇikā ca vairāgyaṃ nālaṃ jñānaṃ śivātmakam
śivadharmaṃ ca tatkandam iti padmaṃ vicintayet 84
tad dharmajñānavairāgyaśivaiśvaryamayaṃ param
jñātvā padmāsanaṃ śārvaṃ sarvaduḥkhāntam āpnuyāt 85

[god as oṃ on the throne in the heart]
tatpadmakarṇikāmadhye śuddhaṃ dīpaśikhākṛtim
aṅguṣṭhamātram acalaṃ dhyāyed oṅkāram īśvaram 86
kadambagolakākāraṃ tārārūpam iva sthitam
dhyāyed vā raśmijālena dīpyamānaṃ samantataḥ 87
dhyāyed vā satanuṃ śāntaṃ vakṣyamāṇakarūpakam
pradhānapuruṣātītaṃ sitapadmastham īśvaram 88 
japed dhyāyec ca satatam oṃkāraṃ śivarūpiṇam
vācyavācakabhāvena mātratrayavibhāgataḥ 89
mātrās tisraḥ samākhyātāḥ skandadevīmaheśvarāḥ
akārokāramakārās tāś ca mātrāḥ prakīrtitāḥ 90
akārād agnigarbhatvāt kumāraḥ parigṛhyate
ukārād apy umādevī makārāc ca maheśvaraḥ 91
athavānyaprakāreṇa brahmaviṣṇumaheśvarāḥ
kramān mātrāḥ samuddiṣṭās tatparaś cārdhamātrayā 92
bhāvanāmātragamyatvād acintyaḥ paramaḥ śivaḥ
sakalaṃ cintayet tasmāt siddhyarthaṃ satanuṃ śivam 93
athavā vyaktam avyaktaṃ puruṣaṃ cety anukramāt
mātrās tisraḥ samākhyātāḥ śivaś cāpyardhamātrayā 94
śrīkaṇṭhanāthaṃ varadaṃ caturvedaparaṃ haram
dhyāyamānasya satatam aiśvaryaṃ sampravartate 95

[tattvajayaḥ]
kecit kṣityāditattvānāṃ jayam icchanty anukramāt
ajitvaivādharāṃ bhūmim ūrdhvaṃ gacchet kathaṃ muniḥ 96
siddhe sarveśvare deve yugapat saṃpravartate
aiśvaryaṃ sarvatattveṣu tajjayaṃ ca na saṃśayaḥ 97
manaḥsthityartham icchanti sthūladhyānam anukramāt
tatra taṃ niścalībhūtaṃ labhet sūkṣme ’pi saṃsthitim 98
sthityarthaṃ manasā pūrvaṃ sthūlarūpaṃ vicintayet
nānārūpākṛtir bhedo na tu tattvam acetanam 99 
yac chivādhiṣṭhitaṃ rūpaṃ taddhyānaṃ pāpaśuddhidam
manaḥsthitikaraṃ cāśu na tu tattvam acetanam 100
tasmād dhyeyāni sarvāṇi tyaktvā dhyeyaṃ maheśvaram
tatsiddhau sarvataḥ siddhir na sarvaiḥ siddhyate śivaḥ 101
yadā śivātmakaṃ rūpaṃ dhyāyan prāṇair viyujyate
tadā sa śivatāṃ yāti nānyaṃ dhyāyet tataḥ śivāt 102
yad yat tattvaṃ tad evaṃ vā dhyāyed abhyāsakāraṇāt
tat tad īśvararūpeṇa tattvaṃ dhyāyed adhiṣṭhitam 103
merusaṃsthaṃ kṣitau śarvaṃ dhyāyed bhavam umāpatim
agner adhipatiṃ rudram ugraṃ pavanamūrttinam 104
lower ākāśādhipatiṃ bhīmam īśānaṃ sūryasatpatim
candrādhipaṃ mahādevaṃ puṃsāṃ paśupatiṃ patim 105

[tattvajayaḥ: Śiva in each tattva]
ahaṃkāre smared īśaṃ buddhau sarvajñam īśvaram
puṃprakṛtyāsanaṃ śāntaṃ dhyāyeta parameśvaram 106
bhūtasiddhau bhavet siddhir munes tanmātrapañcake
buddhyahaṃkārasiddhasya vasitvaṃ prakṛtau bhavet 107
yatrasthaṃ yena varṇena śivarūpam anusmaran
lakṣayed ātmasaṃsthair yat tat tad dhyeyaṃ punaḥ punaḥ 108
[tattvajayaḥ: visualisation of Śiva]
śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśaṃ jaṭāmukuṭabhūṣitam
prasannavadanaṃ śāntaṃ sarvāvayavaśobhanam 109
sitapadmajamadhyasthaṃ samādhiṣṭhaṃ trilocanam
padmāsanastham acalam īṣatsaṃvṛtalocanam 110
sabījapūrakakaraṃ varadābhayapaṇinam
dvīpicarmaparīdhānam akṣamālādharaṃ haram 111
prabhākiraṇaparyantaṃ bhāsayantaṃ digānanam
saṃsārārṇavaparyastapuruṣānīkatāraṇam 112
itthaṃrūpaṃ śivaṃ dhyāyet pratitattvam anukramāt 
aṣṭāṅgulaṃ vitastiṃ vā yathā syān manasaḥ sthitiḥ 113
rūpavarṇapramāṇādyaiḥ parikalpyātmabuddhinā
tathā dhyāyīta deveśaṃ yathā cittaṃ sthiraṃ bhavet 114
śivenādhiṣṭhitaṃ yasmāj jagat sarvaṃ carācaram
sarvarūpaḥ śivas tasmād iti jñātvā na muhyati 115
prāṇāyāmaiḥ susampūrṇaiḥ kuryād vā niścalaṃ manaḥ
sarvasaṅgavinirmuktaḥ seved vā vijanaṃ vanam 116
[six factors for the success of yoga (?)]
utsāhān niścayād dhairyāt santoṣāt tattvadarśanāt
muner janapadatyāgād yogaḥ ṣaḍbhiḥ prasiddhyati 117
[ṣaḍaṅgo yogaḥ]
prāṇāyāmaḥ pratyāhāraḥ prati sthānaṃ ca dhāraṇā
dhyānaṃ japaḥ samādhiś ca ṣaḍaṅgaṃ yogasādhanam 118
[prāṇāyāmaḥ]
prāṇo vāyuḥ śarīrasthas tasyāyāmo nirodhanam
recakaḥ pūrakaḥ kumbhas trividhaḥ samprakīrtitaḥ 119
nāsikāpuṭam aṅgulyāpīḍyaikam apareṇa ca
audaryaṃ recayed vāyuṃ recanād recakaḥ smṛtaḥ 120
bāhyena vāyunā dehaṃ dṛtivat pūrayed bhṛśam
tathā pūrṇaś ca santiṣṭhet pūraṇāt pūrakaḥ smṛtaḥ 121
na muñcati na gṛhṇāti vāyum antarbahiḥsthitam
āpūrṇakumbhavat tiṣṭhed acalaḥ sa tu kumbhakaḥ 122
kanyasaḥ sakṛd udghātaḥ sa ca dvādaśamātrakaḥ
madhyamaś ca dvirudghātaś caturviṃśatimātrakaḥ 123
uttamaś ca trirudghātaḥ ṣaṭtriṃśattālamātrakaḥ
svedakampābhighātānāṃ jananaś cottamottamaḥ 124 
ajitvā nāruhed bhūmiṃ vāyor uttamakāṅkṣayā
ajitvā rohaṇād bhūmer āśu jāyanty upadravāḥ 125
hikkā śvāsaḥ pratiśyāyaḥ karṇadantākṣivedanāḥ
mūkatā jaḍatā kāsaḥ śirorogaḥ śramo jvaraḥ 126
ity evam ādayo doṣā jāyante vyutkrameṇa tu
sarvarogacikitsāś ca saṃkṣepāc chṛṇu yoginām 127
[āgneyī dhāraṇā]
yasmin yasmin bhaved aṃśe yogināṃ vyādhisambhavaḥ
tat tad aṅgaṃ dhiyā vyāpya dhārayet tatra dhāraṇām 128 
āgneyīṃ dhāraṇāṃ dhyāyed roge vāyavyavāruṇe
vāyavyāgneyadoṣe ca viṣadoṣe ca sarvataḥ 129
 [amṛta-dhāraṇā]
amṛtañ cintayet prājñaḥ kṣutpipāsāturas tathā
anyonyābhibhavād eva jñātvā yuñjīta dhāraṇām 130
dhyānenaiva praṇaśyanti ye rogā yogasambhavāḥ
bheṣajair japahomaiś ca dānapuṇyaiś ca karmmajāḥ 131
[power of breath when controlled]
yathāraṇye gajaḥ siṃhaḥ puruṣair aprayogataḥ
nāśayed dhāryamāṇas tu tathā vāyur abuddhibhiḥ 132
sa caiva hi yathā hastī prayogād damyate śanaiḥ
nirdoṣaś ca bhavet kālād vaśyaḥ saumyaś ca jāyate 133
śanaiḥ śanais tathā prāṇaḥ prayogād vaśyatāṃ gataḥ
svecchayā dhāryate dehe na taddoṣaṃ karoti ca 134 
yathā pracodito hastī parasainyaṃ vināśayet
rakṣate ca prayoktāram ārūḍhañ svabalena saḥ 135
tathā śarīrasaṃruddhaḥ prāṇaḥ samyak pracoditaḥ
nirdahet sarvapāpāni taccharīrañ ca rakṣati 136
prāṇair vinirjite dehe cihnāny etāni lakṣayet
viṇmūtraśleṣmadoṣāṇām alpabhāvaḥ prajāyate 137
bahubhojanasāmarthyaṃ cirād ucchvasanaṃ tathā
ārogyaṃ śīghragāmitvam utsāhaḥ surasauṣṭhavaṃ 138
balavarṇaprasādaś ca sarvvadoṣakṣayas tathā
evamādīni cihnāni satvasthasya prajāgrati 139
[agarbhaḥ sagarbhaś ca prānāyāmaḥ]
agarbhaś ca sagarbhaś ca prāṇāyāmo dvidhāsthitaḥ
japadhyānaṃ vināgarbhaḥ sagarbhas tatsamanvitaḥ 140
agarbhād garbhavān jñeyaḥ prāṇāyāmaḥ śatādhikaḥ
sagarbhaṃ dhārayet tasmād indriyāṇāṃ jayotsukaḥ 141
samastendriyavṛttiś ca prāṇo vāyuḥ prakīrtitaḥ
tajjayād indriyāṇy eva nirjjitāni bhavanti tu 142
vṛttivṛttimator yasmād abhedaḥ parigīyate
tasmād vṛttijayād eva vṛttimān nirjjito bhavet 143
jñānavairāgyayoktrābhyāṃ prāṇāyāmakaśena ca
indriyāśvān vinirjjitya sarvvam eva jitam bhavet 144
indriyāṇy eva tat sarvvaṃ yat svarganarakāv ubhau
nigṛhītavisṛṣṭāṇi svargāya narakāya ca 145
śarīraṃ ratha ity āhur indriyāṇy asya vājinaḥ
sārathiḥ puruṣaḥ proktaḥ prāṇāyāmaḥ kaśaḥ smṛtaḥ 146
jñānavairāgyaraśmibhyām āyāmya vidhṛtam manaḥ
śanair niścalatām eti prāṇāyāmakaśāhate 147
manovājinam atyugraṃ nigṛhnānaḥ punḥ punaḥ 
vinirvvedyaṃ punar gacchet kuryād evātmano hitaṃ 148
jalabindukuśāgreṇi māse māse ca yaḥ kvacit
saṃvatsaraśataṃ sāgraṃ prāṇāyāmaś ca tatsamaḥ 149
tapāṃsi yāni paṭhyante yajñā dānaṃ vratāni ca
sarvvatīrthābhiṣekaś ca prāṇāyāmaś ca tatsamaḥ 150
prāṇasyaiva jayo yogaḥ prāṇasyaiva jayas tapaḥ
prāṇasyaiva jayāt sarvaṃ prāpyate nātra saṃśayaḥ 151
atha pratyāhāracittaṃ visṛtaṃ bhogatṛṣṇayā
bhavadoṣavicāreṇa kuryyād unnīya sarvvataḥ 152
uddhared ātmanātmānam uhyamānam anāthavat
bhogam adyātivegena jñānavṛkṣasamāśrayā 153
indriyāṇi prasaktāni pratitvaṃ viṣayodadhau
āhṛtya yo nigṛhṇāti pratyāhāraḥ sa ucyate 154
evaṃ yaḥ śānticittātmā pratyāhāram anukramāt
sa sarvatīrthayajñānāṃ phalaṃ prāpya śivaṃ vrajet 155
yadvā yāvat sthitaṃ lakṣyan tat tasmāc calate manaḥ
tāvatkālaṃ pradeśeṣu dhāraṇā manasaḥ sthitiḥ 156
kālāvadhiparicchinnaṃ dehe saṃsthāpitaṃ manaḥ
na pracyavati pakṣyād vā dhāraṇā sābhidhīyate 157
dhāraṇā dvādaśāyāmā dhyānaṃ dvādaśadhāraṇaṃ
dhyānadvādaśakaṃ yāvat samādhir abhidhīyate 158
dhāraṇābhyāsayuktātmā yadi prāṇair viyujyate
kulaikaviṃśad uttārya svayaṃ yāti śivaṃ padam 159
dhyai cintāyāṃ smṛto dhātuḥ śivacintā muhur muhuḥ
anākṣiptena manasā dhyānam ity abhidhīyate 160
ātmanaḥ samanaskṛtya muktāśeṣoṣadhasya ca
śivacintā samāsaktir dhyānaṃ nāma tad ucyate 161
dhyeyālambanasaṃsthasya sadvaśaḥ pratyayasya ca
pratyayāntaranirmmuktaḥ pravāho dhyānam ucyate 162
dhyeyāvasthitacittasya pradeśe yatra kutracit
dhyānan tatredam uddiṣṭaṃ pratyayasyaikatānatā 163
evaṃ dhyānasamāyuktaḥ svadehaṃ yaḥ parityajet 
kulasvajanamitrāṇi samuddhṛtya śivo bhavet 164
evaṃ muhūrttam arddhaṃ vā dhyāyed yaḥ śraddhayā śivaṃ
so’pi yāṅ gatim āpnoti na tāṃ sarvvair mahāmakhaiḥ 165
yāvantaḥ karmmayajñās syur vratadānatapāṃsi ca
sarve te japayajñasya nārghanti ṣoḍaśīṃ kalāṃ 166
māhātmyaṃ vācikasyaiva japayajñasya kīrtitaṃ
asmāc chataguṇopāṃśuḥ sāhasro mānasaḥ smṛtaḥ 167
yad uccanīcasvaritaiḥ śabdaiḥ spaṣṭapadākṣaraiḥ
mantram uccārayed vācā japayajñaḥ sa vācikaḥ 168
śanair utthāpayen mantram īṣad oṣṭhau pracālayan
kiñcic chabdāt svayaṃ vidyād upāṃśur ujjapaḥ smṛtaḥ 169
dhiyā yadakṣaraś śroṇyāṃ varṇād varṇaṃ padāt padaṃ
śabdārthacintanābhyastaṃ tad uktaṃ mānasaṃ japaḥ 170
trayāṇāṃ japayajñānāṃ śreyaḥ syād uttarottaraṃ
bhaved yajñaviśeṣaś ca viśeṣas tatphasya ca 171
japena devatānityaṃ stūyamānā prasīdati
prasannā vipulān bhogān dadyān muktiñ ca śāśvatīṃ 172
yakṣarakṣaḥpiśācāś ca grahāḥ sarppādibhīṣaṇāḥ
jāpinan nopasarppanti bhayabhītāḥ samanatataḥ 173
japena pāpaṃ kṣapayed aśeṣaṃ yat tat kṛtaṃ janmaparamparāsu
japena rogāñ jayate ca mṛtyuṃ japena siddhiṃ labhate ca mokṣam 174
japācchrantaḥ (?) śivaṃ dhyāyed dhyānāc chrāntaḥ punar japet
japadhyānābhiyuktasya śivaḥ kṣipraṃ prasīdati 175
padārthamātranirbhāsaḥ stimitodadhivat sthitaḥ
svarūpaśūnyavad dhyānaṃ tatsamādhir ihocyate 176
dhyeye manaḥ sanniveśya yat tiṣṭhen niścalaś ciram
nirvāṇānalavad yogī samādhisthaḥ prakīrtitaḥ 177
na śṛṇoti na ca prīti (jighrati) na rasyati na paśyati
na ca sparśaṃ vijānāni na saṅkalpayate manaḥ 178
na cātimanyate kiñcin na ca buddhyati kāṣṭhavat
evam īśvarasaṃllīnaḥ samādhisthaḥ pragīyate 179
yathā dīpo nivātastho neṅgatesopamā smṛtā 
dhyāyataḥ śivam ātmasthaṃ samādhisthasya yogainaḥ 180
prāṇāyāmād bhavet kṣipraṃ sarvvapāpaparikṣayaḥ
sarvendriyavaśīkāraḥ pratyāhāreṇa jāyate 181
manasaḥ paramaṃ sthairyaṃ dhāraṇātaḥ pravarttate
dhyānena pralayaṃ gacched anaiśvaryaguṇāṣṭakam 182
prasādābhimukhī prītā bhavej japyena devatā
samādhinā ca sarvvatra prajñālokaḥ pravarttate 183
evam abhyasyataḥ puṃsaḥ ṣaḍaṅgaṃ yogasādhanaṃ
tadantarāyā naśyanti mṛgāḥ siṃhabhayād iva 184
ālasyaṃ vyādhayas tīvrāḥ pramādadhyānasaṃśayāḥ
anavasthitacittatvam aśraddhābhrāntidarśanaṃ 185
duḥkhāni daurmanasyañ ca viṣayeṣu ca lolatā
ity evam ādikāḥ proktā yogavighnāḥ svabhāvataḥ 186
atyantotsāhayuktasya japadhyānaratasya ca
tadantarāyā naśyanti sarvve vighnāḥ śanaiḥ śanaiḥ 187
upaśānteṣu vighneṣu samādhisthasya yoginaḥ
upasargāḥ pravartante divyās te siddhisūcakāḥ 188
prātibhaḥ śrāvaṇo vārttā darśanāsvādavedanāḥ
ṣaḍ upasargā yogasya parityāge ca siddhayaḥ 189
prārthayanti ca tān devā bhogair divyaiś ca yoginaḥ
nṛpāś ca pṛthivīdānair dravyaiś cānye dhanādhipāḥ 190
upatiṣṭhanti ratnāni dhanāni ca mahānti ca
vedādisarvvaśāstrāṇi svayam eva bhavanti ca 191
abhīṣṭacchandohṛdayaṃ kāvyaṃ cāsya pravarttate
rasāyanāni sarvvāṇi divyāś cauṣadhayaḥ svayaṃ 192
samastāni ca śilpāni kalāḥ sarvvāś ca vindati
nāgāḥ surendrakanyāś ca praṇipatya namanti ca 193
mahāmahodadher yadvad bhagnāj jāyanti vipruṣāḥ
yogaiśvaryodadhes tadvad vipruṣapratibhādayaḥ 194
prātibhādiṣu kṣudreṣu guṇeṣv āsakta cetasaḥ
sambhavet paramaiśvaram akṣayaṃ sārvvakāmikaṃ 195
tasmād guṇāṃś ca bhogāṃś ca devāsuramahībhṛtāṃ 
tṛṇavad yas tyajet sarvān īśas tasya prasīdati 196
tataḥ prasannā deveśi buddhiḥ satvāt pravarttate
aṇimādiguṇaiśvaryya sarvvajñatvañ ca yoginaḥ 197
sarvajñaś ca tanuṃ tyaktvā śuddhaḥ śāntaḥ sadā sukhī
nirdvandvaḥ paripūrṇaś ca muktaḥ svātmani tiṣṭhati 198
anugrahāya cānyeṣāṃ yadi dehaṃ na santyajet
aṇimādiguṇaiśvaryyaḥ santiṣṭhec chivavat prabhuḥ 199
dātā harttā ca karttā ca bhoktā ca prakṛter vaśī
jñānāñjanopadeṣṭā ca kujñānāvṛtacetasāṃ 200
ity evam icchayā bhogān bhuktvā jñānaṃ prakāśya ca
pralayānte tanuṃ tyaktvā svātmany evāvatiṣṭhate 201
yasmāt saukhyañ ca mokṣañ ca yogād ubhayam āpnuyāt
tasmāt sarvvaṃ parityajya japed dhyāyet sadā śivaṃ 202
ye saṃśritā jñānamayaṃ sunāvaṃ te yānti pāraṃ bhavasāgarasya
tiṣṭhanti magnā bhavasāgare ’smin putreṣu dāreṣu gṛheṣu saktāḥ 203
dhyānena mokṣaṃ paramañ ca saukhyaṃ vindanti sarvve puruṣāḥ striyāś ca
anena dehena labhanti kecit siddhāś ca bhogān pralaye ca muktiṃ 204
idaṃ paraṃ pāpaharaṃ pavitraṃ jñānāmṛtaṃ mṛtyuvināśanañ ca
vijñāya yaḥ prāṇihitāya dadyāj jagadgurus tena samaḥ kuto ’nyaḥ 205
sa eva vandyaḥ pratipūjanīyaḥ sa eva mātā jagataḥ pitā ca
sa eva bandhuḥ sa guruḥ śivaś ca jñānāmṛtaṃ yaḥ paramaṃ prapadyāt 206
iti śivadharmottire jñānayogo nāma daśamo ’dhyāyaḥ || 10 ||








|| ekādaśo’dhyāyaḥ ||
oṃ namaḥśivāya
atha pāpaviśuddhyarthaṃ prāyaścittaṃ samācaret ||
kṛtvā śaucaṃ tathā snānaṃ śivāgnigurupūjakaḥ || 11.1 ||
utthāya paścime yāme sugṛhītakamaṇḍaluḥ ||
dhautapādukamākramya maitraṃ kuryād yathākramaṃ || 11.2 ||
dīkṣavinītacittajñas toyadānavidhānavit ||
sahāyaḥ śaucakāryaṣu tad abhāvāt kamaṇḍaluḥ || 11.3 ||
vācaṃ niyamya yatnena ṣṭhīvanotkāsavarjjitaḥ ||
śiraḥ prāvṛtya tat kuryād antardhāya tṛṇair mahīṃ || 11.4 ||
divā sandhyāsu karṇasthabrahmasūtrī hy udaṅmukhaḥ ||
kuryān mūtrapurīṣetu rātrau ced dakṣiṇā mukhaḥ || 11.5 ||
mārjanaṃ vāmahaste vīraṇādyair ayājñikaiḥ ||
viṇmūtram utkṣipet tatra chāyāyām ātmano na ca || 11.6 ||
nānilānaladevānāṃ gobrāhmaṇajalam prati ||
jantuśādbalabhasmāsthikṛṣṇacchāyāṃ vivarjayet || 11.7 ||
pādāvasevanaṃ mūtraṃ purīṣaṣṭhīvanaṃ ca yat ||
dūrād āvasathāt sarvaṃ yac cānyad vikṛtam bhavet || 11.8 ||
gṛhītaśiśnaś cotthāya samāyuktakamaṇḍaluḥ ||
śaucaṃ kuryān mṛdāmbhobhir gandhalepāpanuttaye || 11.9 ||
tistro liṅge mṛdo yojyās tv ekaikāntaramṛttikā ||
āmalīphalamātraṃ ca pañca vāmakare yathā || 11.10 ||
mṛdas tistraḥ karābhyāṃ tu mūtrotsarge bhavec chuciḥ ||
pañcāpāne mṛdo yojyās tan nirantaramṛttikāḥ || 11.11 ||
daśa vāmakare deyāḥ pāṇyoḥ sapta tathobhayoḥ ||
upasparśanakāle tu tisṛbhiḥ kṣālayet karau || 11.12 ||
jaṅvāśaucamṛdastisra ekaikāntaramṛttikā ||
akṣiṇī nāsikā karṇau tisraḥ saṃśodhya hastayoḥ || 11.13 ||
karddamāmedhyamūtrādyair madaṅge saptapañcadhā ||
kṣālite vāriṇa pūrvaṃ sa tisro’ntaramṛttikāḥ || 11.14 ||
āmaṇi bandhanāt pāṇiṃ mṛttoyena viśodhayet ||
antaḥ kṛtvā bhujau samyag bahij jānūr vidhāya ca || 11.15 ||
udvṛttānuṣṇaphenābhiḥ pūtābhir vastracakṣuṣā ||
hadayābhiraśabdābhis tricaturvāram ācaret || 11.16 ||
parimṛjya dvirācamya dvādaśāṅgāni cālabhet ||
tūṣṇīm eva tato bhūyaḥ śivamantreṇa pūrvavat || 11.17 ||
ācamed brahmatīrthena brahmasūtrī hy udaṅmukhaḥ ||
tadantarāntare pāṇim āplāvyāplāvya cāmbhasā || 11.18 ||
vastraśaucaṃ pravakṣyāmi tacchuddhau śuddhyate yataḥ ||
vastraśauca vihīnātmā śucir apy aśucir bhavet || 11.19 ||
devakāryā prayogānāṃ pratyahaṃ śaucam iṣyate ||
vāsasām itareṣāṃ ca śaucaṃ kuryān malāgame || 11.20 ||
śucinā toraṇaṅ kāryaṃ svāṅgadaṇḍatrayeṇa tu ||
tatra vāsāṃsi nirṇijya samyagbaddhāni śoṣayet || 11.21 ||
khagair vā’dūṣite vṛkṣe nirmale vā śilātale ||
durvājāle śucau vāpi kṣāliteṣu tṛṇeṣu vā || 11.22 ||
viṇmūtraśukladigdhānāṃ mṛttoyena viśodhanaṃ ||
kāryam ādau tataḥ kṣārair gomūtrādyaiś ca śodhanaṃ || 11.23 ||
mṛdvāri tāvad ādeyaṃ gandhalepau hi tad gatau ||
tasmāt tān dūrato yāvat sarvāsu dravya śuddhiṣu || 11.24 ||
kauśeyāvikayor uṣṇaiḥ kṣaumāṇāṃ gaurasarṣapaiḥ ||
śrīphalair aṃśupaṭṭānāṃ kutapānām ariṣṭakaiḥ || 11.25 ||
cailavad rajjuvetrāṇāṃ pakṣacāmaracarmaṇi ||
kalkalānāṃ ca sarveṣāṃ śuddhiḥ kāryā vijānatā || 11.26 ||
vidalālāṃbupātrāṇāṃ vasravacchuddhir iṣyate ||
gopālair varṣaṇaṃ caiṣāṃ viśeṣaḥ parikīrtitāḥ || 11.27 ||
kāṃsyāyas tāmraraupyāṇāṃ trapusīsakayor api ||
śuddhiḥ śaucārthanā kāryā bhasmakṣārāmlavāribhiḥ || 11.28 ||
nirlepaṃ kāñcanaṃ raupyam adbhiḥ pātraṃ viśuddhyati ||
maṇyaśmaśaṃkhaśuktīnāṃ śaucaṃ taijasavatsmṛtaṃ || 11.29 ||
rajaḥ kharāsūtikā dyarmūtrādyaiś cāpi dūṣitaṃ ||
agner apāś ca saṃyogāt taijasaṃ śuddhim āpnuyāt || 11.30 ||
śūdrocchiṣṭasya pātrasya triḥkṛtvā parimārjjanaṃ ||
śaucaṃ vai pūtakāmena kartavyaṃ taijasasya tu | 11.31 ||
dravyāṇām iha sarveṣāṃ śuddhir utplavanaṃ smṛtaṃ ||
palālatṛṇakāṣṭhānāṃ plavanāc chuddhir iṣyate || 11.32 ||
struvādicarupātrāṇāṃ musalolūkhalasya ca ||
śūrpagorasabhāṇḍānāṃ śuddhir uṣṇena vāriṇā || 11.33 ||
śṛṅgāsthidārudantānāṃ takṣaṇaiḥ pariśodhanaṃ ||
atyantopahatānān tu gomūtras sodakena tu || 11.34 ||
saṃhatānāṃ ca dravyāṇāṃ prokṣaṇāc chuddhir iṣyate ||
asaṃhata dravyaśaucaṃ kāryaṃ pratyātmikaṃ sadā || 11.35 ||
vastradhānyādir āśīnām ekadeśasya dūṣaṇe ||
tāvanmātraṃ samuddhṛtya śeṣaḥ prokṣaṇam arhati || 11.36 ||
ambhasālpīyasā kāryaṃ mṛdā caiva viśodhanaṃ ||
śākamūlaphalādyānāṃ dhānyavac chuddhir iṣyate || 11.37 ||
gokīṭam akṣikādyair vā kṛmisaṃsparśaneṣu vā ||
chāgopajidhraṇāc chuddhir anyasyādbhiś ca prokṣaṇāt || 11.38 ||
kharoṣṭraśvaśṛgālādyair biḍvarāhāvalepane ||
tāvanmātraṃ samuddhṛtya śeṣaṃ saṃskāram arhati || 11.39 ||
dīttolmukena saṃspṛśya trisaptadhautam eva ca ||
suvarṇatoyasaṃspṛṣṭaṃ śuddham eva na saṃśayaḥ || 11.40 ||
makṣikā keśasam miśraṃ padāntopahataś ca yat ||
rajaḥ pipīlikāyuktaṃ bhuñjan onnama vakṣyati || 11.41 ||
tāvanmātraṃ samuddhṛtya prokṣayed ambhasā tataḥ ||
ājñābhidhāraṇācchuddhir bhasmakṣepeṇa vā bhavet || 11.42 ||
bhūmistham udakaṃ śuddhaṃ vitṛṣṇā yatra gaurbhavet ||
āvyāptapadamadhyena gandhavarṇa rasānvitaṃ || 11.43 ||
na mukhodvipruṣocchiṣṭaṃ kuryāriṅgan na veṅgatāḥ ||
na śmaśrūṇi gatān āsyaṃ na dantāntarasaṃsthitāḥ || 11.44 ||
pādau spṛśanti ye vāpi parācamanabindavaḥ ||
te pārthivasamā jñeyā na tair aprayato bhavān (bhavet) || 11.45 ||
pītvā bhuktvā ca suptvā ca samprayāṣyādhamaiḥ saha ||
ṣṭhīvitvādhyayanādau ca śuddhir apy ācame punaḥ || 11.46 ||
dravyahaste samucchiṣṭas tān nidhyāyāṅgirācamet ||
dravyaśuddhiś ca pūrvoktā kāryā dravyānurūpataḥ || 11.47 ||
gośakṛnmūtra valmīkamṛttikā bhasmavāriṇā ||
veśmāyatanaliṅgānāṅ kāryam etad viśodhanaṃ || 11.48 ||
mārjjanollekhanaiḥ saktair gonisektair jalena ca ||
iti pañcavidhāśuddhir bhūmau kāryā vijānatā || 11.49 ||
grāmād hastaśataṅ gatvā nagarāc ca caturguṇaṃ ||
gṛhīsarvatram evāsyān nirlepā yatra dṛśyate || 11.50 ||
śucir ākarajandravyaṅkāruhastaḥ śuciḥ sadā ||
prasnave ca śucir vatsaḥ śukuniḥ phalapātane || 11.51 ||
vipragomakṣikāś cājac chāyāgnisūryaraśmayaḥ ||
rajobhūr vāyur āpaś ca medhyāni sparśanaṃ sadā || 11.52 ||
nagaraṃ grāmarathyāṃ vā paribhramya gṛhādvahiḥ ||
pādau prakṣālya mṛttoyair gṛhāntaḥ praviśet tataḥ || 11.53 ||
śirasnānaṃ prakurvīta sravantīṣu viśeṣataḥ ||
mṛdgomayaiḥ samudghṛṣya triḥ śarīraṃ samantataḥ || 11.54 ||
snānavastraṃ samutsṛjya dvitīyaṃ paridhāya ca ||
tena snātvā kaṣāyādyair vastram anyat samādadet || 11.55 ||
sopanīyaḥsamācamya pānīyam abhimantrayet ||
eka viṃśativārāṃś ca śivamantreṇa bhāvita || 11.56 ||
dhyāyamānaḥ śivaṃ śāntaṃ śanaiḥ snānaṃ samācaret ||
ācamya cātmanaḥ kuryād abhiṣekaṃ tataḥ punaḥ || 11.57 ||
kumbhena parṇapuṭakaiḥ karadvayapuṭena vā || 
japan ekādaśātmānaṃ sthāpayed yena vā punaḥ || 11.58 ||
vidyālakṣmī viśuddhyartham abhiṣiṃ can samantataḥ ||
ārabhya prokṣayed bhūyas tāvad evā ca nā śiraḥ || 11.59 || 
gṛhe ca parijaptena snānakumbhena kārayet ||
evaṃ bhāvena susnātaḥ sarvapāpavivarjitaḥ || 11.60 ||
sarvatīrthābhiṣekasya śraddadhānaḥ phalaṃ labhet ||
sandhyātrayaparibhraṣṭaḥ śivaikādaśikātrayaṃ || 11.61 ||
japtvā śuddhim avāpnoti snānahīnaś ca taj japet ||
parvaṇy apūjya deveśaṃ gurum agniṃ ca bhaktitaḥ || 11.62 ||
adatvā ca balin tatra śivasyāṣṭaśatañ japet ||
patraṃ puṣpaṃ phalaṃ mūlam annapānādyam auṣadhaṃ || 11.63 ||
anivedya na bhuñjīta yadāhārāya kalpitaṃ ||
anivedya prabhuñjānaḥ prāyaścittī bhaven naraḥ || 11.64 ||
śivāṣṭaśatajaptena pūjayā ca viśuddhyati ||
anasthiprāṇasaṅghātaṃ hutvaikādaśikāñ japet || 11.65 ||
hutvā ca pakṣiṇaḥ sarvaṃ strir ekādaśikām punaḥ ||
sarppamārjjāranakulaṃ śvānam uṣṭraṃ kharaṃ hayaṃ || 11.66 ||
gajādyāṃś ca mṛgān sarvān hatvā vāṣṭaśatañ japet ||
japed aṣṭasahasran tu kṣatraviḍ govadhe punaḥ || 11.67 ||
śivāgnigurupūjā ca yogindradvijabhojanaṃ || 
hatvā śudraṃ striyaṃ bālaṃ śivaṃ pañcaśataṃ japet || 11.68 ||
japed aṣṭasahasraṃ ca sa śūdrasya pramāraṇe ||
sadvṛttaḥ śivabhaktaś ca nādyāt mṛtakasūtake || 11.69 ||
saṃskāreṣu ca sarveṣu gṛheṣu kim utāny ataḥ ||
sūtake na tu bhoktavyan naityakaṃ ca vivarjayet || 11.70 ||
bhuktvā pramādataḥ snehāc chivasyāṣṭaśatañ japet ||
śvaviḍvarāhacaṇḍālair durjanaiḥ kapikukkuṭaiḥ || 11.71 ||
ulūka gṛdhrakākādyaiḥ spṛṣṭam annan na bhakṣayet ||
śivaikādaśajaptena gavyena haviṣābudhaḥ || 11.72 ||
pītena śuddhyakṣipram abhojyāhāradūṣitaḥ ||
tīrthayātrāviśuddhātmā sadvṛttaḥ śivabhāvitaḥ || 11.73 ||
putrair api na bhuñjīta sārddha krurair adhārmikaiḥ ||
mahāpātakaśuddhyarthaṃ sahasrāṇi japed daśa || 11.74 ||
prāṇāyāmais trisandhyaṃ ca śivam agniṃ ca pūjayet ||
retomūtrapurīṣāṇi prāśya pītvā ca vāruṇīṃ || 11.75 ||
bhuktvā cānnamabhojyānāṃ gatvā cāpyantyajāṃ striyaṃ ||
japtvā śivāyutaṃ samyak pūrvoktavidhinā budhaḥ || 11.76 ||
pañcagavyaṃ sakṛt pītvā sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate ||
gomūtraṃ gomayaṃ kṣīraṃ dadhi sarpir anukramāt || 11.77 ||
japet triḥ pañcabrahmeṇa oṃkāreṇa kuśodakaṃ ||
palāśapadminīpatre tāmrapātre’thavā sthitaṃ || 11.78 ||
kṛtvaikasthaṃ śivenaiva japed aṣṭaśataṃ punaḥ ||
ahorātroṣitaḥ snātaḥ śivasya purataḥ sthitaḥ || 11.79 ||
oṃkārādyena mantreṇa prāṅmukhais tacchanaiḥ pibet ||
pītamātro bhavet pūtaḥ sampūrṇaḥ śāśinirmalaḥ || 11.80 ||
brahmahatyādikaiḥ pāpaiḥ sarvair evāśu mucyate ||
mātāpitṛsamudbhūtaṃ sahajāgantukaṃ ca yat || 11.81 ||
asthimajjāgataṃ pāpaṃ brahmakūrcchaḥ kṣaṇād dahet ||
aṣṭamyaṃ brahmakūrcena snāpayitvā sakṛcchivaṃ || 11.82 ||
pītvā ca pātakair muktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate ||
tasmāt praticaturmāsaṃ brahmakūrcchaṃ pibed budhaḥ || 11.83 ||
sarvapāpaviśuddhyarthaṃ sarvapātakanāśanam ||
prāyaścitaṃ śivaproktaṃ na deyaṃ yasya kasya cit || 11.84 ||
etad rahasyam paramaṃ prāyaścittaṃ svayaṃ budhaḥ ||
kuryāt pracchannapāpeṣu prakāśe prārthayed guruṃ || 11.85 ||
śivajñānavidaṃ śāntaṃ mahāpātakanāśanaṃ ||
praṇipatya guruṃ paścāt prārthayec chuddhim ātmanaḥ || 11.86 ||

iti śivadharmottare prāyaścittannāmaikādaśo’dhyāyaḥ ||

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivadharmottare goloko nāma
dvādaśo’dhyāyaḥ
oṃ namaḥ śivāya

śrutvaitat paramaṃ guhyaṃ gavān dehasamudbhavam || 
brahmakūrcchasya māhātmyam agastiḥ punar abravīt || 12.1 ||
bhagavan! śrotum icchāmi golokaḥ kīdṛśaḥ punaḥ ||
prāpyate karmaṇā kena kiyat yadhvani saṃsthitaḥ || 12.2 ||
	|| skanda uvāca ||
śrūyatām abhidhāsyāmi namaskṛtya maheśvaram ||
gomātṛlokaṃ paramaṃ sarvakāmasamanvitam || 12.3 ||
adhastāt sarvalokānāṃ narakāḥ kramaśaḥ sthitāḥ ||
pātālāni tataḥ sapta pātālapatayas tathā || 12.4 ||
yāvatpramāṇaṃ svādūdaṃ paricchinnaṃ mahītale ||
tāvatpramāṇam evādhaḥ kūpākārāṇi tāni tu || 12.5 ||
teṣāṃ pratyekam utsedhaḥ pramāṇaṃ parikīrtitaṃ ||
yojanānāṃ sahasrāṇi daśa tantrārtha vittamaiḥ || 12.6 ||
sahasrayojanan teṣāṃ dalābhyantara nemayaḥ ||
suṣirāṇām pramāṇaṃ ca sahasrāṇi navaikaśaḥ || 12.7 ||
teṣāṃ ruciramambhodhis tāmatastanmahātalaṃ ||
divyadravyopasampannaṃ śrīmaccāmīkaradyutiḥ || 12.8 ||
nāgarājaḥ sadaivāste tasmin kṛtaniketanaḥ ||
ananto ’nantadhāmā ca mucukundo nṛpovalī || 12.9 ||
vāsuker nāgarājasya tatra cāru mahāpuraṃ ||
tato rasātalannābha śilāsaṃghātabhūmikaṃ || 12.10 ||
puraṃ sulomnas tatraiva dānavādhipater mahat ||
suparṇataś ca daityānām anyeṣāṃ ca mahātmanām || 12.11 ||
tatra talātalan nāma śarkarārcita bhūmikaṃ ||
nāgānāṃ khalikādīnāṃ nivāsas tatra kīrtitaḥ || 12.12 ||
dānavādhipatīnāṃ ca tatraiva nilayāḥ kṛtāḥ ||
vairācana hiraṇyākṣa prabhṛtīnāṃ mahātmanāṃ || 12.13 ||
tataḥ sutalam ityuktaṃ pātālaṃ pītabhaumikaṃ ||
tasya cordhvaṃ ca sarveṣāṃ mṛṇmayeva talakṣitiḥ || 12.14 ||
asurādhipates tatra kālanemer mahat puraṃ ||
cārucāmīkaraprakhyaṃ vainateyasya cāparaṃ || 12.15 ||
tataś ca vitalan nāma pātālaṃ rakta bhūtalaṃ ||
tasmin mahān tako nāgo dānavāś ca kṛtālayāḥ || 12.16 ||
tārakāgnimukhas tatraḥ anukrā(hrā)daś ca dānavaḥ ||
nivasanti kṛtāvāsāḥ prahlādas tu tathaiva ca || 12.17 ||
pātālan tritalan nāma śuklakṣititalan tataḥ ||
kambalāśvatarau nāgau sahitau yatra tiṣṭhataḥ || 12.18 ||
mahājambhahayagrīvaprabhṛtīnāṃ mahātmanāṃ ||
vīrāṇām asurendrāṇān nivāsas tatra kalpitaḥ || 12.19 ||
kṛṣṇakṣititalan tasmāt pātālan talasaṃjñitaṃ ||
śaṅkukarṇamahānāda namucīnāṃ niketanaṃ || 12.20 ||
pātālasaptakādūrdhvaṃ saptadvīpā mahī sthitāḥ ||
samudraiḥ saptabhir yuktā parvataiḥ samalaṅkṛtā || 12.21 ||
jambūdvīpo mahīmadhye plakṣadvīpastataḥ paraḥ ||
tṛtīyaḥ śālmalīdvīpaḥ kuśadvīpaś ca tadvahiḥ || 12.22 ||
krauñcadvīpaś ca parataḥ śākadvīpaś ca tadvahiḥ ||
parataḥ puṣkaradvīpaḥ saptamaḥ parikīrtitaḥ || 12.23 ||
kṣārodaś cekṣurasodaḥ surodaś ca ghṛtodadhiḥ ||
dadhyudaḥ kṣīrapūrṇaś ca svādūdaḥ saptamaḥ smṛtaḥ || 12.24 ||
atra dvīpasamudrāṇāṃ dviguṇād dviguṇottaraḥ ||
pramāṇaṃ vistarojñeyo niyutaḥ prathamaḥ smṛtaḥ || 12.25 ||
himavān hemakūṭaś ca niṣadhaś ceti dakṣiṇe ||
nīlaḥ śvetaś ca śṛṅgī ca meror uttaratas trayaḥ || 12.26 ||
madhye meruḥ sthitaḥ ṣaṇṇāṃ jambūdvīpasya madhyataḥ ||
mālyavān parvato jñeyaḥ paścime gandhamādanaḥ || 12.27 ||
ete parvatarājāno jambūdvīpe nava sthitāḥ ||
plakṣidvīpādiṣu jñeyāḥ sapta saptaiva parvatāḥ || 12.28 ||
puṣkaradvīpamadhye ca parvato balayākṛtiḥ ||
ekaḥ sthitaḥ samantāc ca nāmato mānasottaraḥ || 12.29 ||
vahir eka śirā nāma svādūdasya vyavasthitaḥ ||
urvākaratalākārāḥ kāñcanaiḥ parimaṇḍalāḥ || 12.30 ||
ārudrasanniveśāntā niveśyā vibudhākṣitiḥ ||
tasyāḥ pramāṇaṃ nirddiṣṭaṃ daśayojanakoṭayaḥ || 12.31 ||
lokāloka iti khyātas tatparyante samantataḥ ||
sthito hemamayaḥ śrīmān acalaḥ parimaṇḍalaḥ || 12.32 ||
yojanānāṃ sahasrāṇi adhaś cordhvaṃ samucchritaḥ ||
tāvad eva ca vistīrṇas tadūrdhvaṃ bhānumānyataḥ || 12.33 ||
gandharvayakṣarakṣobhiḥ piśācaiś ca niṣevitaḥ ||
manuṣyaiḥ paśubhiś caiva bhūmeḥ pakṣisarīsṛpaiḥ || 12.34 ||
sthāvarair vividhākārair bhūtair yuktas tu ṣaḍvidhaiḥ ||
bhūr lokato bhuvar loko yāvad ādityamaṇḍalaṃ || 12.35 ||
aniketābasanty asmin basurudrāḥ sabhāṣkarāḥ ||
ādityamaṇḍalād ūrdhvaṃ proktaḥ svarloka ādhruvaṃ || 12.36 ||
vimānakoṭayastasminnaṣṭāviṃśatirāsate ||
medhībhūto vimānānāṃ sarveṣām upari dhruvaḥ || 12.37 ||
samuhya yatra baddhāni krameṇānilamaṇḍalaṃ ||
yojanānāṃ mahīpṛṣṭhe ūrdhvaṃ pañcadaśa dhruvaḥ || 12.38 ||
niyatāś cānilaskandhāḥ saptāsmin uttarāḥ sthitāḥ ||
pṛthivyāṃ prathamaḥ skandhaḥ sthita āmeghamaṇḍalāt || 12.39 ||
āvaho nāma meghānāṃ vyāhārāvāhanād iṣaṭ ||
dvitīyaḥ pravahonāma vivaddhaḥ sūryamaṇḍale || 12.40 ||
tṛtīya udvaho vāyuskandha indau pratiṣṭhitaḥ ||
caturthaḥ saṃvahaskandhaḥ sthito nakṣatramaṇḍale || 12.41 ||
grahe’pi pañcamaḥ so’pi vivahaḥ parikīrtitaḥ ||
skandhaḥ parāvahaḥ ṣaṣṭhaḥ sthitaḥ saptarṣimaṇḍale || 12.42 ||
vāyuḥ parivahonāma vivaddhaḥ saptamo dhruve ||
karoty utplavanādīni varṣaṇādīni cāvahaḥ || 12.43 ||
upariṣṭāt sthitaḥ ṣaṇṇāṃ vimānodvahanakriyāṃ || 
yojanānāṃ dhruvātkoṭimaharlokaḥ samucchritaḥ || 12.44 ||
vinivṛttādhikārāṇāmadhivāsomahātmanāṃ ||
viṃśatiḥ koṭayo’ṣṭau ca surāṇāmadhikāriṇāṃ || 12.45 ||
janāḥ svarllokamāgamya niyogātpadmajanmanaḥ ||
sthitvā manvantarantatra svavyāpārāvasāyite || 12.46 ||
ārohanti maharllokamāgacchantyapare janāḥ ||
brahmaṇo divase netthan devavargāś caturdaśa || 12.47 ||
krameṇa kṛtvā karmāṇi mahārloke vasanti te ||
koṭidvayaṃ maharlokāj janalokaḥ samucchritaḥ || 12.48 ||
sādhyā nāma surās tasmin vasanti sukhinaḥ sadā ||
yojanānāntapolokaś catasraḥ koṭiyojanāḥ || 12.49 ||
prajānām patayas tatra mānasā brahmaṇaḥ sutā ||
satyalokas tapolokāt koṭayaḥ ṣaṭ samucchritaḥ || 12.50 ||
āste parivṛtas tatra surāṇām īśvarair virāṭ ||
tasyopari brahmaloko dviguṇena samucchritam || 12.51 ||
vistareṇa tadūrdhvaṃ ca divyabhoga samanvitaḥ ||
viṣṇulokāc ca parataḥ śrīmac chivapuraṃ mahat || 12.52 ||
dvātriṃśatkoṭi vistīrṇan tadarddhena samucchritam || 
sūryāyutapratīkāśaṃ sarvakāmasamanvitaṃ || 12.53 ||
anekākāravinyāsa racanā hy upaśobhitaṃ ||
sarvaratnacitair dravyais taptajāmbūnadaprabhaiḥ || 12.54 ||
sahasraguṇabhogaiś ca tadūrdhvaṃ guṇabhaumikaṃ ||
apsarogaṇasaṅkīrṇaḥ sarvavādyasamanvitaiḥ || 12.55 ||
gītanṛtyarasopetair aprameyaguṇānvitaiḥ ||
manojabair asaṃkhyaiś ca parivārasamanvitaiḥ || 12.56 ||
vimānaiḥ sarvato vyāptaṃ tārābhir iva cāmbaraṃ ||
kvacid dolāgṛhai ramyaiḥ kiṅkiṇīravakānvitaiḥ || 12.57 ||
budvudair arddhacandraiś ca ghaṇṭācāmarabhūṣitaiḥ ||
maṇimuktāvitānaiś ca chatraiś ca maṇidaṇḍakaiḥ || 12.58 ||
sarvaratnacitaiḥ śubhrair muktāhāraiś ca śobhitaiḥ ||
kvacit puṣpagṛhaiḥ prāpyam asaṃkhyeyaguṇānvitaiḥ || 12.59 ||
sadāpuṣpaphalair vṛkṣaiḥ kvacid vyāptaṃ manoramaiḥ ||
puṣpodyānair mahāramyair divyagandhaguṇānvitaiḥ || 12.60 ||
amṛtasyandinībhiś ca nadībhir upaśobhitaṃ ||
hemaratnacitā vāpyaḥ sopānaiḥ sphaṭikaprabhaiḥ || 12.61 ||
sitaraktāsitaiḥ pītaiḥ śuklavarṇaiḥ sugandhibhiḥ ||
pañcavarṇaiś ca mṛdubhiḥ padmaiḥ śobhitakāñcanaiḥ || 12.62 ||
sadā vikasitāsnānaiḥ śrīmadbhiḥ pañcahastakaiḥ ||
daśadvādaśahastaiś ca viṃśahastaiś ca śobhanaiḥ || 12.63 ||
nālair marakataprakhyaiḥ puṣpaiś ca sumanoharaiḥ ||
pūrṇā nīlotpalaiś cānyā dīrghikāśa kvacit kvacit || 12.64 || 
 saṃhavyāghramukhair divyair gajavājimukhānvitaiḥ ||
gomukhaiś chāgavadanair nānāvihagarūpibhiḥ || 12.65 ||
ekavaktrairmahāvaktrairvahuvaktraiḥ suvaktrakaiḥ ||
ekapādais tripādair vā bahupādair apādakaiḥ || 12.66 ||
vāmanair jaṭilair muṇḍair dīrghagrīvair mahodaraiḥ ||
mahākāyair mahānāsair mahākarṇair akarṇikaiḥ || 12.67 ||
nānārūpākṛtidharair nānābharaṇabhūṣitaiḥ ||
nānāveśadharair divyaiḥ kāmarūpair mahābalaiḥ || 12.68 ||
nānāprabhāvasaṃyuktair nānāśāstraviśāradaiḥ ||
asaṃkhyātair gaṇair vyāptaṃ striyaś cānyās tathāvidhāḥ || 12.69 ||
kubjavāmanikā dīrghā varadehāvarānanāḥ ||
muṇḍāś ca vikaṭāḥ sthūlāḥ surūpāś cipiṭanāsikāḥ || 12.70 ||
lambodarā hrasvabhujā vinatā hrasvajānukāḥ ||
mṛgendravadanāś cānyā gajavājimukhās tathā || 12.71 ||
hrasvakuñcitakeśāś ca sundaryaḥ priyadarśanāḥ ||
anyāś ca kāmarūpiṇyaḥ koṭiśaḥ paricārikāḥ || 12.72 ||
bahir antaḥ pracārās tā ramante sarvabhūmiṣu ||
vicitrā bhūmayas tatra vajravaidūryasannibhāḥ || 12.73 ||
kvacitsuvarṇasaṃkāśāḥ kvacin marakataprabhāḥ ||
sphaṭikendranīlavarṇāḥ padmarāganibhāḥ kvacit || 12.74 ||
candramaṇḍalasaṅkāśāḥ kvacidindīvaraprabhāḥ ||
amlānaiḥ pañcavarṇaiś ca mahāpadmair alaṅkṛtāḥ || 12.75 ||
golokaḥ śivalokaś ca
kvacic ca vividhai ramyaiḥ kusumairupaśobhitāḥ ||
evaṃ vibhinna varṇābhā bhūmayo’tīva śobhanāḥ || 12.76 ||
ramante yāsu satataṃ strībhiḥ sārddhaṃ śivāśritāḥ||
nīloptaladalaśyāmāḥ padmapatrāyatekṣaṇāḥ || 12.77 ||
taptacāmīkarākārāḥ śuddhaśyāmāstathāparāḥ ||
priyaṅguśyāmavarṇāś ca divyagandhamanoramāḥ || 12.78 ||
kṛśodaryaḥ susaṅvghā(dhā)stāḥ surūpāḥpriyadarśanāḥ ||
mattamātaṅgagāminyaḥ stanabhāravināmitāḥ || 12.79 ||
madālasāḥ sukeśāś ca sarvāvayavaśobhanāḥ ||
citravastraparīdhānā divyābharaṇa bhūṣitāḥ || 12.80 ||
sollāpollāpakuśalā gītavādyaratipriyāḥ || 12.81 ||
dantatviṣā rañjitagaṇḍadeśāḥ svātmaprabhābhāsitagātrayaṣṭyaḥ ||
svābhāvikaistā lalitaprayaugaiḥ prahṛṣṭacittā ramayanti nāryaḥ || 12.82 ||
nṛtyaprayogairmadhuraiś ca geyaistantrīnibandhairvividhaiś ca vādyaiḥ ||
hāsyaiḥ smitair llocanavibhramaiś ca krīḍā prayogairvividhaistathānyaiḥ || 12.83 ||
iti divyaguṇopetaiḥ strīsahasrairmanoramaiḥ ||
asaṃkhyātaiḥpuraṃ vyāptamīśvarasya samantataḥ || 12.84 ||
tanmadhye sarvatobhadraṃ divyamāyatanam mahat ||
śudhdasphaṭikasaṅkāśamādyasthānamumāpateḥ || 12.85 ||
tatrāstte bhagavān somaḥ pūjyamāno gaṇeśvaraiḥ ||
siddhaiś ca sthānasamprāptai_rbrahmaviṣṇavāgnivāyubhiḥ || 12.86 ||
īśvarāyatanasyādhaḥ śrīmān dharmabṛṣaḥsthitaḥ ||
yatra vīravṛṣastatra kṣityāṃ gomātaraḥ sthitā || 12.87 ||
golokaḥ śivalokaś ca eka eva tataḥ smṛtaḥ ||
ye guṇā rudralokasya golokasyāpi te guṇāḥ || 12.88 ||
nandā subhadrā surabhiḥ (bhī) suśīlā sumanāś ca tāḥ ||
iti gomātaraḥ pañca śivaloke vyavasthitāḥ || 12.89 ||
etā divyā jagaddhātryaḥ sarvalokasya mātaraḥ ||
tarppayanti jagat kṛtsnaṃ nityamātmarasāmṛtaiḥ || 12.90 ||
avatīrya śivasthānādīśvarecchāvaśānugāḥ ||
upakārāya sarveṣāmimaṃ lokaṃ samāśritāḥ || 12.91 ||
tṛṇānikhādanti basantyaraṇye pibanti toyānyaparigrahāmi (ṇi) ||
duhyanti bāhyanti punanti pāpaṃ gavāṃ rasairjjīvati jīvalokaḥ || 12.92 ||
kutasteṣāṃ hi pāpāni yeṣāṃ gṛhamalaṅkṛtaṃ ||
satataṃ bālabatsābhirgobhiḥ śrībhiriva svayaṃ || 12.93 ||
ye kurvanti gavāṃ bhaktiṃ tṛṇatoyapradānataḥ ||
(bra) praṇasaṃrohanādyaiś ca gavāṃ lokaṃ brajanti te || 12.94 ||
tṛṇatoyapradeśeṣu nītvā yatnena mātaraḥ ||
ye rakṣanti sadā gopāḥ śivaloke vrajanti te || 12.95 ||
ye śivāya gurorvāpi gāṃ prayacchanti bhaktitaḥ ||
te modanti śiveloke bhogaiḥ kalpāyutannarāḥ || 12.96 ||
nivedya gorasaṃ bhakatyā śivāya śivayogine ||
sarvān kāmānavāpnoti śivalokamito gataḥ || 12.97 ||
ihalokasukhārthāya paralokahitāya ca ||
sarvasvenāpi gāntasmādādadīta vipaścitaiḥ || 12.98 ||
aho! sumahadāś caryamaho! suṣṭhu subhāṣitaṃ ||
yat pavitraś ca mṛṣṭaś ca goraso buddhivarddhanaḥ || 12.99 ||
gomatā nirjjitāḥlokā vṛtāśāgomatārjitāḥ ||
gomatā nirjjitaḥ svargaḥ samastaṃ gomatā jitaṃ || 12.100 ||
gāvo bandhurmanuṣyāṇāṃ gāvaś ca dhanamuttamaṃ ||
gāvo yeṣāṃ gṛhe nasyurabandhuriva tadgṛhaṃ || 12.101 ||
spṛṣṭvātu gāvaḥ śamayanti pāpaṃ datvātu gāvastridivaṃ nayanti ||
saṃrakṣitāś copanayanti vittaṃ gobhirnna tulyaṃ dhanamasti kiñcit || 12.102 ||
sampannamaśnāti dadāti nityaṃ pāpāpahaṃ mitravivarddhanaṃ ca ||
sa eva cārthaḥ paribhujyate ca gobhirnna tulyaṃ dhanamasti kiñcit || 12.103 ||
tṛṇāni śuṣkāṇi vane caritvā pītvā ca toyānyamṛtaṃ sravanti ||
yadgomayādyaiś ca punanti lokān gobhirnna tulyandhanamasti kiñcit || 12.104 ||
sa evaloke paramaḥ pavitro gavāṃ rasaḥ puṣṭi vivarddhanaś ca ||
aśnāti nityaṃ vividhānnayuktāmiṣṭañciraṃ yena śiva prasādāt || 12.105 || (navaḥ prapānnāt)
gomātṛśālāṃ yaḥ kuryāt sudṛḍhāmiṣṭakāmayīṃ ||
mṛtpiṇḍakāṣṭhākuḍyaṃ vā satkapāṭārgalānvitāṃ || 12.106 ||
sapidhānairgavākṣaiś ca caturbhiḥ samalaṅkṛtāṃ ||
paścāt kuḍyaṃ ca kartavyamuc caireva gavākṣakaṃ || 12.107 ||
supakkvairvaṃśavidalaiḥ kaṭaṃ kṛtvā samaṃdṛḍhaṃ ||
gavāmadhaḥ pradātavyaṃ yena mūtramadho vrajet || 12.108 ||
gomayaṃ taṅgavākṣaiś ca kṣiptvā dūraṃ punarnnayet ||
vikīrya bhasmanā sarvaṃ dhūpayīta samantataḥ || 12.109 ||
kṛśavṛddhāturāṇāṃ ca pṛthagbhāvaṃ prakalpayet ||
pṛthak ca bālavatsānāmitareṣāṃ pṛthagbhavet || 12.110 ||
damyānaḍvāha ya prāṇāṃ (vṛṣāṇāṃ) vasatiṃ kalpayet pṛthak ||
gāḥ (gāvaḥ) svapanti sukhenaiva vasanti ca ramanti ca || 12.111 ||
rudro brahmā ca viṣṇuś ca gośālāyāṃ sadā yajet ||
vinyasya pūrvavadanāṃ paścāt kuḍayagavākṣake || 12.112 ||
saṃhārūḍhāṃ mahādurgāṃ pañca nandādimātaraḥ ||
vighneśaṃ somanandiṃ ca pūrvādārabhya vinyaset || 12.113 ||
nadyubhaya taṭāśvattha vilvavalmīkamṛttikāṃ ||
pañcagavyena saṃyojya devān piṇḍaiḥ prakalpayet || 12.114 ||
dvāraśākhāgavākṣābhyāṃ mṛdākāryau suśobhanau ||
nandīśvaramahākālau vṛṣaṃ coccair vahiḥ sthitaṃ || 12.115 ||
yādṛśo’yaṃ vṛṣendraḥ syātsarvāvayavaśobhanaḥ || 
taddarśanānubhāvena gavāṃ syustādṛśāḥ prajāḥ || 12.116 ||
aṣṭamyāṃ snāpanaṃ kṛtvā bhojanaṃ ca prakāmataḥ ||
svasti vācyaṃ tataś cāgre pradhānāṅgāmpraveśayet || 12.117 ||
iti yaḥ kārayed bhaktyā gomātṛgṛhamīdṛśaṃ ||
sa vidhūyāśu pāpāni śivaloke mahīyate || 12.118 ||
bālasūryapratīkāśaiḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaiḥ ||
kāñcanai_rbhavanairddivyaiḥ sarvaratnopaśobhitaiḥ || 12.119 ||
saptabhaumaiḥ puravaraiḥ śatasaṃkhyairyathepsitaiḥ ||
pratyekamatidivyena strīsahasreṇa saṃyutaiḥ || 12.120 ||
etairanyaiś ca vipulairmahābhogairyathecchayā ||
krīḍate tatra puṇyātmā yāvadācandratārakaṃ || 12.121 ||
tataḥ kālāt paribhraṣṭaḥ kramād bhogamavāpnuyāt ||
haribrahmādi lokeṣu tadante merumūrdhani || 12.122 ||
tasmādapi cyutaḥ kālāt prāpnuyāduttarān kurun ||
tato bhāratavarṣe’smin rājā bhavati dhārmika || 12.123 ||
surūpaḥ subhagaḥ śūraḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaḥ ||
tataḥ prāgvāsanāyogāt puṇyamācarate punaḥ || 12.124 ||
yaś ca grīṣme gavāṃ goṣṭhaṃ jalāśrayasamīpataḥ ||
kūryād bṛkṣākule sthāne tatraikatrācirannaraḥ || 12.125 ||
gavāmekatra saṃvāse doṣaḥ syād gomayoṣmaṇā ||
tasmānnaikatra vasatiṃ ciraṃ grīṣme prakalpayet || 12.126 ||
nānyasthānaṃ yadā paśyed gavāṃ grīṣme suśobhanaṃ ||
pūrvameva tadā sthānaṃ yatnācchodhyaṃ dine dine || 12.127 ||
yaiḥ śoghyate (yaḥ śodhayad) gavāṃ vāṭamātmīyaṃ vā parasya vā ||
sa pradāyagavāṃ saukhyaṃ śivaloke pramodate || 12.128 ||
duḥkhaṃ kṛtvā labhed duḥkhaṃ sukhaṃ kṛtvālabhet sukhaṃ ||
tasmāddhi sarvasatvānāṃ sukhārthī sukhamācaret || 12.129 ||
apyekaṃ kṣaṇamutpādya sukhamārtasya dehinaḥ ||
prāpnoti sumahat saukhyamavdakoṭiṃ śive pure || 12.130 ||
tasmādgāś cārayed grīṣme tṛṇabṛkṣajalānvite ||
varṣāsvakardamasthāne girivṛkṣasamīpataḥ || 12.131 ||
hemante tu divākāśe rātrau ca prasarannayet ||
nistṛṇe’pi gavāṃ sthāne prasareṇa dhṛtirbhavet || 12.132 ||
grīṣme triṣyāyayed gāś ca svādutoyaṃ hi taddhitaṃ ||
kṣārabhūḥ salilaṃ kṣāraṃ grīṣmādanyatra gohitaṃ || 12.133 ||
evaṃ yaḥ pāyayed gāś ca sa gopaś cārayīta ca ||
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate || 12.134 ||
yaḥ stambhaṃ (sāstraṃ) danturaṃ stambhaṃ goṣu madhye kvacitkvacit ||
kaṇḍūyanārthaṃ nikhanecchivalokaṃ sa gacchati || 12.135 ||
anāthāṃ durbbalāṃ gāṃ ca rogādiparipīḍitāṃ ||
mṛtavatsāmadugdhābhirmātṛbhiś ca vivarjjitāṃ || 12.136 ||
svakīyān parakīyān vā vatsānyaḥ paripālayet ||
vidhūya sarvapāpāni śivaloke mahīyate || 12.137 ||
dugdhalobhahataprajñā ye vatsān kṣīrajīvinaḥ ||
niṣpīḍayanti te gobhiḥ pīḍyante narakeṣu ca || 12.138 ||
niśvasanti gṛhe yeṣāṃ dahyamānāḥ kṣudhāgninā ||
nirddugdhā nirdayairvatsāḥ pacyante narakeṣu te || 12.139 ||
vikrośantaḥ kṣudhāviṣṭāḥ śuṣkakaṇṭhoṣṭhatālukāḥ ||
narakāgnau prapacyante varṣakoṭiśatannarāḥ || 12.140 ||
narakebhyaḥ samuttīrṇāḥ sāvaśeṣeṇa karmaṇā ||
yatra yatrābhijāyante tatra tatra bubhukṣitāḥ || 12.141 ||
yonikoṭisahasreṣu paribhramya kramātpunaḥ ||
manuṣyaloke jāyante daridrāḥ paratarjjakāḥ || 12.142 ||
tasmānna pīḍayed vatsānapuṣṭān kṣīratṛṣṇayā ||
vatse tṛpte yadadhikaṃ tatkṣīraṃ nirdduhet punaḥ || 12.143 ||
dvau māsau na duhedvavatsāṃstṛtīye’rdhanduheta vā ||
duhec caturthaṃ niḥśaṅkastasya lālāstu varjjayet || 12.144 ||
bandhanaṃbālavatsānāṅkarṇagrāhaṃ ca varjjayet ||
śītavarṣātapatrāṇaṃ kāryaṃ niṣkarddamaṃ samaṃ || 12.145 ||
yūkāpanayanaṃ dhūmaṃ kuryātkaṇḍūyanaṃ sadā ||
kṛmirogakṣudhādibhyaḥ sarvayatnena pālayet || 12.146 ||
ya evaṃ vālavatsānāmupakārāya vartate ||
ihāpnoti paraṃ saukhyaṃ paratra ca śivaṃ puraṃ || 12.147 ||
grāmabhojyagṛhaṃ prāptān nṛpatiryaḥ samuddharet ||
kulaikaviṃśamuddhṛtya śivaloke mahīyate || 12.148 ||
yaḥsa dvijaḥ prayatnena grāmabhojyātsamudhdaret ||
pratigrahādyupāyena śivaloke mahīyate || 12.149 ||
yaḥ pradadyātsudhavalaṃ śivasandhyāmahāvṛṣaṃ ||
vistīrṇā raktamuccāgraṃ samunnatavṛhatkaṭiṃ || 12.150 ||
ūrdhvaṃ kuñcitaśṛṅgāgramahāśṛṅgāntarantathā || 
sthūlāgraśṛṅgayuktaṃ vā sarvāvayavaśobhanaṃ || 12.151 ||
raktapītaiś ca kusumaiḥ kuṅkumādyaiś cavarṇakaiḥ ||
yathāśobhaṃ samālabhya vibhavaiḥ pūjayed vṛṣaṃ || 12.152 ||
kiṅkiṇīravakopetaṃ ghaṇiṭakā cāmarānvitaṃ ||
svastikairarddhacandraiś ca nānāratnaiś ca śobhitaṃ || 12.153 ||

aṣṭāṅgulapravīstīrṇāṃ hemapaṭṭavinirmitāṃ ||
rājatīṃ cārmaṇīṃ vāpi mālāmurasi vinyaset || 12.154 ||
tadvidhāṃ pṛṣṭhamālāṃ ca pucchāntakakudāśritāṃ ||
nānābharaṇasaṃyuktām udarārdhapralambinīṃ || 12.155 ||
hemarājatakauṣaṃ vā nānāratnopaśobhitaṃ ||
kāryaśṛṅgadvayantasya sadvastracamarānvitaṃ || 12.156 ||
paṭṭaṃ śirasi sauvarṇaṃcandracandrika bhūṣitaṃ ||
cāmarāśvatthapatraiś ca badhnīyād dravyasaṃyutaṃ || 12.157 ||
graiveyakeṇa divyena nānāratnopaśobhinā ||
ghaṇṭāṅkāṃsyamayī śuddhāṃ gale vadhnīta susvanām || 12.158 ||
khuraiḥ suvarṇakai raupyaiḥ keyūrāṅgadabhūṣitaṃ ||
paṭṭavastrairvicitraiś ca yathāśobhāmalaṅkṛtaṃ || 12.159 ||
vitānadhvajamālābhirgeyavādyādi maṅgalaiḥ ||
dodhūyamānaś camaraiḥ śivāya vinivedayet || 12.160 ||
yāvat tadromasaṃkhyānaṃ tatprasūti kuleṣu ca ||
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate || 12.161 ||
na ca mānuṣyakaṃ lokamāgacchetpunaradhruvaṃ ||
jñānayogaṃ samasādya tatraiva sa vimucyate || 12.162 ||
evaṃ vidhaṃ yo vṛṣabhaṃ gopatiṅgrāhaṇakṣamaṃ ||
vatsikājananaprāyaṃ bahukṣīrāvahaṅgamaṃ || 12.163 ||
nānābharaṇasaṃyuktaṃ pūrvaśobhāsamanvitam ||
gomātaraṃ ca sampūjya visṛjecchivagokule || 12.164 ||
evaṃ yaḥ sampradyāt tu vṛṣṣendraṃ śivagokulaṃ ||
sa pūrvoktaṃ labhet puṇyaṃ yatsandhyāvṛṣadānataḥ || 12.165 ||
nivedya sadguṇopetamanaḍvāhaṃ śivāśrame ||
daśa dhenupradānasya phalaṃ śobhanamāpnuyāt || 12.166 ||
utpādya sasyāni tṛṇaś caranti tadevabhūyaḥ savalaṃ vahanti ||
na bhārakhinnāḥ pravadanti kiñcidaho vṛṣairddhāryati jīvalokaḥ || 12.167 ||
vṛṣāṇāmpṛṣṭhamārūḍhā ye gacchanti narādhamāḥ ||
te mahāpralayaṃ yāvat pacyante narakāgniṣu || 12.168 ||
vṛṣapṛṣṭhena gacchantaṃ jñānaṃ jñātvā yadā nṛpaḥ ||
na vārayedupekṣeta pāpaṃ tasyāpi tatsamaṃ || 12.169 ||
ye vṛṣāḥ sādhubhir muktās triśūlāṅkāḥ śivapriyāḥ ||
tān vāhayanti ye mūḍhāḥ pāpācārānarādhamāḥ || 12.170 ||
te mahāpralayaṃ yāvadaśeṣanarakāgniṣu ||
prapadyante vadhai_rghoraiḥ patnī putrādisaṃyutāḥ || 12.171 ||
rājñaś ca viṣaye yasya jānataś ca narādhamaiḥ ||
vṛṣā vāhyanti pāpiṣṭhaiḥ pāpantasyāpi tatsamaṃ || 12.172 ||

tasmān nivārayed rājā vāhyamānān khalairvṛṣān ||
anyathā cāti ghoreṣu narakeṣu patet svayaṃ || 12.173 ||
vāhyamānān vṛṣān vārya nṛpatiḥ svargamāpnuyāt ||
ihārogyaṃ dhanaṃ saukhyamāyuḥ kīrtiṃ śriyaṃ sutān || 12.174 ||
yaś ca pāpaviśuddhyarthaṃ prāyaścittaṃ samīhate ||
savṛṣaikādaśīṃ datvā varṣaṃ rakṣec ca mātaraṃ || 12.175 ||
ekaikarakṣaṇaṃ kuryād gorūpāṇāṃ śataṃ śataṃ ||
gāvaḥ sukhenabarddhante caranti ca ramanti ca || 12.176 ||
govraṇāṃ pravilāyante nandante taravastathā ||
tasmāt praviralā gāstu cārayet pāyayīta ca || 12.177 ||
gobhirnnaikatra rakṣāḥ syurddanyānaḍvāhapadrahaḥ ||
api dravanti gāvastā vinaśyanti ca te’pi ca || 12.178 ||
śaradgrīṣme ca madhyānhe chāyāyāṃ viniveśayet ||
chāyāsu ghanavṛkṣāṇāṃ punarutthāya cārayet || 12.179 ||
ya evaṃ viralā gāś ca sadākṛtvā’nupālayet ||
samuktaḥ pātakaiḥ sarvaiḥ śivalokamavāpnuyāt || 12.180 ||
ye ’rccayanti śivaṃ bhaktyāṃ sadvidhāna vivarjjitaḥ ||
te vindanti mahābhogānnarāḥ śivapure ciraṃ || 12.181 ||
ye śivāśramatīrthāni śraddhayā yānti mānavāḥ ||
te krīḍanti mahābhogairdivyaiḥ śivapure narāḥ || 12.182 ||
na śivaḥ paripūrṇatvāt kañcidarthaṃ samīhate ||
kintu tannāmamātreṇa dattambhevatī cākṣayaṃ || 12.183 ||
dānenānena bhagavān prīyatāṃ me sadā śivaḥ ||
ityuktvā deyamarthibhyastattasmādakṣayaṃ phalaṃ || 12.184 ||
yastūlapūrṇavistīrṇam uccamañ camapūrakaṃ ||
mṛducarmakṛtaṃ vāpi sitavastrāvaguṇṭhitaṃ || 12.185 ||
kṛṣṇājinoparicchannaṃ dhūpapuṣpādhivāsitaṃ ||
śivadhyānābhiyuktāya śraddhayāvinivedayet || 12.186 ||
tattūlavastratantunāṃ romṇāṃ saṃkhyā ca yāvatī ||
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate || 12.187 ||
tadante sarvalokeṣu bhuktvā bhogānanukramāt ||
tataḥ kṣitiṃ samāsādya saṃhāsanapatirbhavet || 12.188 ||
tṛṇabalkalaparṇotthaṃ śayāpravaraṇādikaṃ ||
datvā tadarthine bhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate || 12.189 ||
śimuddiśya nirvāpaṃ yaḥ pradadyāttadarthine ||
śākamūlaphalādyaṃ vā tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu || 12.190 ||
yāvatsyāttaṇḍulādīnāṃ saṃkhyā patra phaleṣu ca ||
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate || 12.191 ||

bhikṣāṃ savyajñanāṃ datvā śiva bhaktāya bhaktitaḥ || 
varṣalakṣaṃ mahābhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate || 12.192 ||
dadhyannabhakṣyapūrṇaṃ vā bhikṣāpātraṃ suśobhanaṃ ||
dadyādyaḥ śivabhaktāya tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu || 12.193 ||
varṣakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ mahābhogasamanvitaḥ ||
sthitvā śivapure dehī tasyānte sa mahīpatiḥ || 12.194 ||
suśītalena toyena śivabhaktaṃ pipāsitaṃ ||
tarpayitvā śiveloke varṣalakṣaṃ pramodate || 12.195 ||
kalaśaṃ karkkarīyuktaṃ bastraputānupūritaṃ ||
dadyādyaḥ śivabhaktāya tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu || 12.196 ||
śuddhasphaṭika saṅkāśaṃ vimānaṃ sārvakāmikaṃ ||
samprāpya sa śive loke varṣaṃ koṭiṃ pramodate || 12.197 ||
palāśapadmapatrairvā yaḥ kṛtvā puṭakāni tu ||
pradadyācchivayogibhyastāmrapātraphalaṃ labhet || 12.198 ||
yastāmrapātraṃ sukṛtaṃ pradadyācchivayogine ||
suvarṇapātradānasya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ || 12.199 ||
raupyaṃ suvarṇapātraṃ vā nivedya śivayogine ||
koṭikoṭiṃ sa kalpānāṃ śivaloke pramodate || 12.200 ||
apyekaṃ śivamuddiśya yoginaṃ śivadhārmikaṃ ||
bhojayanti yathā śakti te ramanti śive pure || 12.201 ||
śivāpravrajitāṃ śāntāṃ śaktyā bhaktyā ca bhojayet ||
yaḥsa divyairmahābhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate || 12.202 ||
triśūlapāṇiryaḥ śaktyā vahate śivaguggulaṃ ||
tambhojayitvā yatnena śivaloke mahīyate || 12.203 ||
bhojayecchradvayā bhaktyā yaḥ śivabrahmacāriṇīṃ ||
sa go gaiḥ krīḍate divyaiḥ śivaloke vyavasthitaḥ || 12.204 ||
yaḥ śivāśramadharmasthaṃ gṛhasthaṃ bhojayed budhaḥ ||
vipulaiḥ sa mahābhogaiḥ krīḍan śivapure baset || 12.205 ||
śivāśramavanasthaṃ yaḥ kandamūlādibhiryajet ||
sa divyān prāpnuyād bhogānīśvarasya pure sthitaḥ || 12.206 ||
ekaṃ pāśupataṃ bhaktyā bhojayitvā praṇamya ca ||
nānāvidhairmahābhogaiḥśivaloke pramodate || 12.207 ||
mahāvratadharāyaikāṃ bhikṣāṃ yaḥ pratipādayet ||
sa divyaiḥ sumahābhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate || 12.208 ||
apyantajanamācāra śiva bhaktiratannaraṃ ||
bhojayitvā yathāśakti śivaloke mahīyate || 12.209 ||
jñānayogaṃ bahirdhā ye lokasāmānyakarmabhiḥ ||
pūjayanti śivaṃ bhaktyā śivalokaṃ vrajanti te || 12.210 ||

ebhyaḥ parādivyatamātra pūjā loke bhaved gograhaghātino’sya ||
sarve’pi tiṣṭhanti mahāntakālambhaveyurante pṛthivīśvarāś ca || 12.211 ||
nānāśakenāpi karīṣavanhau na ca pradānair na tapobhir ugraiḥ ||
gatiṃ prayāntisma na yajñasaṅkhairnnaivāpi yāṅgacchati gogaheṣu || 12.212 ||
dvaveva loke puruṣṭaumahāntau yau gacchataḥ sūryasabhāḥ vibhidya ||
eko munir yogaratas tathānyaḥ prāṇān priyānyasyajate gavārthe || 12.213 ||
jñānayogena ye śāntā yajanti paramaṃ śivaṃ ||
te sarve duḥkha nirmuktā bhavanti sukhinaḥ sadā || 12.214 ||
ityetacchivalokasya mahābhāgyamudāhṛtaṃ ||
golokasya prasaṅgena tadbhaktānāṃ samāsataḥ || 12.215 ||
śivalokādvahirjñeyamaṇḍasyāvaraṇāṣṭakaṃ ||
pañca bhūtānyahaṅkārāḥ khyātiḥ prakṛtiraṣṭamī || 12.216 ||
īdṛśānāṃ bhuvāṇḍānāṃ koṭyo jñeyāḥ sahasraśaḥ || 
sarve satvāḥ pradhānasya tiryaggūrdhvamadhaḥ sthitāḥ || 12.217 ||
aṇḍādūrdhvaṃ punarjñeyaṃ prakṛterdharmataḥ sthitaṃ ||
brahmaṇaḥ paramasthānaṃ padmarāgasamaprabhaṃ || 12.218 ||
brahmalokātparaṃ jñeyaṃ viṣṇoḥ sthānaṃ sanātanaṃ ||
indra nīlapratīkāśaṃ mahābhogairalaṅkṛtaṃ || 12.219 ||
viṣṇulokātparaṃ sthānaṃ kumārasya mahātmanaḥ ||
svacchamauktikasaṅkāśaṃ varabhogasamanvitaṃ || 12.220 ||
skandasthānāt paraṃ sthānamumādevyāḥ prakīrtitaṃ ||
taptacāmīkaraprakhyamaśeṣaguṇasaṃyutaṃ || 12.221 ||
umāsthānāc ca parataḥ sthānamādyamumāpateḥ ||
dinakṛtkoṭisaṅkāśaṃ sarvakāmasamanvitaṃ || 12.222 ||
aprameyaguṇaṃ śuddhamanaupamyaṃ sanātanaṃ ||
sarvopakārakair bhogair vividhaiḥ samalaṅkṛtaṃ || 12.223 ||
mahāprabhāvasaṃyuktaiḥ sūryāyutasamaprabhaiḥ ||
gaṇairadhyuṣitaṃ sthānamasaṃkhyairyāgatatparaiḥ || 12.224 ||
harihiraṇyagarbhādyairvasurudradivākaraiḥ ||
stūyate bhagavānnityaṃ tatsthānaprāptikāṃkṣibhiḥ || 12.225 ||
jñānadhyānarataiḥ śāntaibhir kṣāhārair jitendriyaiḥ ||
prāpyate tatpadaṃ divyaṃ yogibhirddagdhakilviṣaiḥ || 12.226 ||
samprāpya tatpadaṃ siddhāḥ samastalkeśavarjjitāḥ ||
sarvajñāḥ sarvagāḥ śuddhāḥ paripūrṇā bhavanti ca || 12.227 ||
viśuddhakāyakaraṇāḥ paramaiśvaryasaṃyutāḥ ||
sadehāś ca videhāś ca bhavantyātmetchayā punaḥ || 12.228 ||
iti nityaviśuddhaṃ ca sthānamādyamumāpateḥ ||
divyaṃ śrīkaṇṭhanāthasya jagadbhartuḥsamucchritaṃ || 12.229 ||
sthānapañcakamityetad viśuddhaṃ parikīrtitaṃ ||
paramāṣṭaguṇaiśvaryasaṃyuktaṃ nityamakṣayaṃ || 12.230 ||
svadevatāpraṇītena jñānayogena ye narāḥ ||
dhyāyanti devatāṃ nityaṃ te siddhā yānti tatpuraṃ || 12.231 ||
tatprāptāstadguṇairyuktā devatārūpadhāriṇaḥ ||
bhavanti ca śivāḥ siddhāḥ svabhogā nāma īśvarāḥ || 12.232 ||
abhyasya yaḥ śivaṃ jñānaṃ kiñcitkālaṃ tyajetpunaḥ ||
kāmatṛṣṇābhibhūtatvāt tasyāpīdaṃ mahatphalaṃ || 12.233 ||
apyekadivase pannaḥ śivadhyānaparāyaṇaḥ ||
śivadharma paraḥ sūkṣmastasyānto naiva vidyate || 12.234 ||
yogadharmaḥ susāratvādabhedyaḥ pāpamudgaraiḥ ||
vajrataṇḍulabajjñeyastasmāttasya mahatphalaṃ || 12.235 ||
dehānte tena dharmeṇa sthānamaumamavāpnuyāt ||
tatrāste vipulairbhogaiḥkrīḍan kalpāyutannaraḥ || 12.236 ||
tataḥ kalpāyutasyānte sthāne kaumāramāpnuyāt ||
tatrārddhasammitaṅkālaṃ krīḍamānaḥsukhaṃ vaset || 12.237 ||
tadante viṣṇulokaṃ ca samprāpya samate punaḥ ||
brahmalokantataś cānte prāpyabhogai ramed budhaḥ || 12.238 ||
brahmalokātparibhraṣṭaṣṭhecchiva pure sukhī ||
tatastān viṣṇubrahmādyāllokānāpnotyanukramāt || 12.239 ||
ityetatsarvalokeṣu bhuktvā bhogānaśeṣataḥ ||
manuṣyalokāmāsādya śivayogī bhavetpunaḥ || 12.240 ||
tataḥsa yogavidhanā punardhyāyati śaṅkaraṃ ||
prāptayogatanuntyaktvā śivasthānaṃ paraṃ brajet || 12.241 ||
naitattapobhiratyugrairnna ca sarvairmahāmakhaiḥ ||
samprāpya paramaṃ sthānaṃ śivayogādvasennaraḥ || 12.242 ||
tasmādantarbahiś cintāṃ paribhājya vicakṣaṇaḥ ||
sarvaduḥkha prahāṇārthaṃ śivayogaṃ samabhyaset || 12.243 ||
atha yogaṃ vināpyetat sthānamekena labhyate ||
śivapriyeṇa vidhinā nānyairvidhiśatairapi || 12.244 ||
śivaṃ sampūjya vidhivad ghṛtasnānādivistaraiḥ ||
sahasraṃ śiva bhaktānāṃ bhojayīta daśottaraṃ || 12.245 ||
tataḥ sahasra dogdhrīṇāṅgavāṃ śvetaṃ śitaṃ tathā ||
garbhiṇyarddhena sammiśraṃ vṛṣabhair daśabhir yutaṃ || 12.246 ||
pūjitaṃgandhapuṣpādyaiś cailakaṇṭhamalaṅkṛtaṃ ||
pradakṣiṇāmupāvṛtya mantreṇānena bhaktitaḥ || 12.247 ||
gāvo mamāgrato nityaṃ gāvo nityaṃ pratiṣṭhitāḥ ||
hṛdaye tu sadā gāvo gavāṃ madhye basāmy ahaṃ || 12.248 ||
gavāṃ mantraṃ samuccārya japettāsāṃ puraḥ sthitaḥ ||
gandhapuṣpākṣatonmiśrāṃ gṛhītvā tāmrakarkkarīṃ || 12.249 ||
śṛṅge pucchaṃ pradhānāyā goś ca snāpyatadambhasā ||
raupyapātre tu tattoyaṃ pratigṛhaṇa nayettataḥ || 12.250 ||
tairevasārdhdaṃ viprendrairmahatā tumulena ca ||
bhṛtyaputrakalatrādyairyuktaḥsvajanabandhubhiḥ || 12.251 ||
ānayed dhūpapuṣpādyam ekaikaṃ śrāvakaḥ kramāt || 12.252 ||
sarvasādhujanārthāya jñānamatra prado’pi vā ||
ācāryebhyaḥ kare dadyād vācakaḥ kusumatrayaṃ || 12.253 ||
te’pi tair ādimadhyānte kutyuḥ pūjāntu pustake ||
iti śaktayā ca bhaktayā ca kṛtvā pūjāṃ pradakṣiṇaṃ || 12.254 ||
pravartayati yaḥ kaś cicchivapustakavācanaṃ ||
sarvalokopakārārthamātmanaś ca vimuktaye || 12.255 ||
tasya puṇyaphalaṃ vakṣye śrotṛṇāṃ vācakasya ca ||
dhanamāyuḥ prajāḥ kīrtiṃ prajñāṃ buddhiṃ śriyaṃ sukhaṃ || 12.256 ||
iha samprāpya vipulaṃ dehānte śāntimāpnuyāt ||
asampūjya śivajñānaṃ pradeśe cāpyasaṃskṛte || 12.257 ||
vācayannarakaṃ yāti tasmātsatkṛtya vācayet ||
vācanānte jagacchāntimavadhārya dine dine || 12.258 ||
gaccheyuḥ kuśapuṣpārthaṃ śivārccādhyānatatparāḥ ||
tataḥ śāstrasamāptyante pūjāṃ kṛtvā viśeṣataḥ || 12.259 ||
śivavidyāgurūṇāṃ ca bhatyā ca śivayoginām ||
bhojanaṃ kalpayec caiṣāndīnāndhānāṃ ca sarvataḥ || 12.260 ||
mitrasvajanabandhūnāmante bhṛtyajanasya ca ||
gurave dakṣiṇāndadyācchavetaṅgomithunaṃ śubham || 12.261 ||
bastrayugmāṅgulīyaṃ ca ghṛpūrṇaṃ ca bhājanaṃ ||
vācakāya pradātavyā dakṣiṇā pūrvabhāṣitā || 12.262 ||
abhāṣite’sya dātavyā guror ardhena dakṣiṇā ||
śeṣāṇāṃ ca yathāśakti dakṣiṇā śivayogināṃ || 12.263 ||
dadyād vibodhayetpaś cātpradīpāṣṭaśataṃ budhaḥ ||
nivedayecchivāyaitadaśeṣaṃ puṣpavāriṇā || 12.264 ||
jñānapuṇyaṃ mahāśāntaṃ tattasmādakṣayaṃ phalaṃ ||
evamudyāpa kṛtvā śivajñānasya bhaktitaḥ || 12.265 ||
aśeṣapāpanirmuktaḥ śṛṇuyatphalamāptuyāt ||
kulatriṃśakamuddhṛtya bhāryāputrādisaṃyutaḥ || 12.266 ||
bandubhiḥ svajanaiḥ snigdhair bhṛtyaiḥ dāsaiḥ samāśritaiḥ ||
ity etaiḥ sahitaḥ sarvaiḥ śrīmac chivapure vaset || 12.267 ||
mahāvimānairārūḍhaḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaḥ ||
tatra bhuṅkte mahābhogānicchayā śivavadvaśī || 12.268 ||
dātā hartā ca kartā ca yāvatsamplāva mahat ||
pralayānte tataḥ prāpya jñānayogamanuttamaṃ || 12.269 ||
parameśaprasādena mucyate nātrasaṃśayaḥ ||
yasmād evam ataḥ kuryāc chivapustakavācanaṃ || 12.270 ||
bhogāpavargaphaladaṃ śivabhakto dine dine ||
na mārī na cadurbhikṣaṃ na rakṣāṃsi na cetayaḥ || 12.271 ||
nākālomriyate rājā pīḍyate na ca śatrubhiḥ ||
śṛṇoti yatra satataṃ śivadharmannarādhipaḥ || 12.272 ||
tatra deśe bhaven nityaṃ sarveṣaṃ dehināṃ śivaṃ || 12.273 ||

iti śrīśivadharmottare dvādaśo’dhyāyaḥ ||
|| śivāya namaḥ ||













	

